{
  "id": "7139407341696544246",
  "subject": {
    "id": "7139407341696544246",
    "text": {
      "text": "Updating Stakeholder Details: Name, Email, Address, etc. - Company Admin"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-4485025290834492907",
    "text": {
      "text": "TheStakeholder ledger allows companies to view and modify information for a stakeholder that holds one or multiple securities across the company, such as names, entity type, contact email, relationships, and physical addresses.",
      "originalText": "The Stakeholder ledger allows companies to view and modify information for a stakeholder that holds one or multiple securities across the company, such as names, entity type, contact email, relationships, and physical addresses.<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-7309781109247845649",
    "text": {
      "text": "If the stakeholder has already accepted securities, the company will only be able to update theContact email. ThePortfolio email will be linked to the user’s account and can be used to track the ownership of the securities.",
      "originalText": "If the stakeholder has already accepted securities, the company will only be able to update the Contact email. The Portfolio email will be linked to the user’s account and can be used to track the ownership of the securities.&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-3279852295341638709",
    "list": {
      "item": [{
        "text": "Learn more about Contact email and Portfolio email.",
        "originalText": "<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/stakeholder-email-designations\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a> about&nbsp;Contact email&nbsp;and&nbsp;Portfolio email."
      }, {
        "text": "Learn more about bulk updating stakeholder details.",
        "originalText": "<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/bulk-update-stakeholder-details\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a> about bulk updating stakeholder details."
      }, {
        "text": "Learn more about merging duplicate stakeholders.",
        "originalText": "<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/merging-duplicate-stakeholders\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>&nbsp;about&nbsp;merging duplicate stakeholders."
      }, {
        "text": "Learn more about the stakeholder ledger page.",
        "originalText": "<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/stakeholder-ledger\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a> about the stakeholder ledger page."
      }]
    }
  }, {
    "id": "8908616968651660732",
    "text": {
      "text": "1. Navigate toStakeholders >All Stakeholders. carta/public/11/images/2577492813570145989_rtaImage NOTE: the number of stakeholders in this list includes holders of canceled and/or expired securities. The number of stakeholders listed is different than the number used for billing. See this article on how stakeholders are counted for billing purposes.",
      "originalText": "1. Navigate to Stakeholders &gt; All Stakeholders.<br><img src=\"carta/public/11/images/2577492813570145989_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 468px;height: 231px;\"><br>NOTE: the number of stakeholders in this list includes holders of canceled and/or expired securities. The number of stakeholders listed is different than the number used for billing. See this article on <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/what-is-a-stakeholder\" target=\"_blank\">how stakeholders are counted for billing purposes</a>.",
      "associatedImage": {
        "url": "carta/public/11/images/2577492813570145989_rtaImage"
      }
    }
  }, {
    "id": "8587346397688266764",
    "text": {
      "text": "2. If you need to correct the name or email address connected to the stakeholder, click theV drop-down menu and selectEdit stakeholder. carta/public/11/images/4547285999434706535_rtaImage  Make the changes to the stakeholder as needed. carta/public/11/images/3055753272279864198_rtaImage",
      "originalText": "2. If you need to correct the name or email address connected to the stakeholder, click the V drop-down menu and select Edit stakeholder.<br><img src=\"carta/public/11/images/4547285999434706535_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 468px;height: 79px;\"><br><br>Make the changes to the stakeholder as needed.<br><img src=\"carta/public/11/images/3055753272279864198_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 468px;height: 375px;\"><br>&nbsp;",
      "associatedImage": {
        "url": "carta/public/11/images/3055753272279864198_rtaImage"
      }
    }
  }]
}

{
  "id": "5122223761391739557",
  "subject": {
    "id": "5122223761391739557",
    "text": {
      "text": "Purchase Board Approved RSAs"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "7701902330769668274",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "Navigate to Securities > Equity Awards.",
        "originalText": "Navigate to Securities &gt; Equity Awards.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Click on the RSAs tab.  carta/public/11/images/7297569249148896537_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Click on the RSAs tab.<br> <img alt=\"Screenshot 2021-06-14 154049.png\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7297569249148896537_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 1028px;height: 366px;\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/7297569249148896537_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click on Purchase RSA on the V drop-down menu to the right of the relevant RSA.  carta/public/11/images/5369584326690254601_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Click on Purchase RSA on the V drop-down menu to the right of the relevant RSA.<br> <img alt=\"Screenshot 2021-06-14 154158.png\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5369584326690254601_rtaImage\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/5369584326690254601_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Enter an issue date and click Next: review RSA Purchase.  NOTE: The issue date must be on or after the board approval date.  carta/public/11/images/5975973075872440967_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Enter an issue date and click Next: review RSA Purchase.<br> NOTE: The issue date must be on or after the board approval date.<br> <img alt=\"Screenshot 2021-06-14 154322.png\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5975973075872440967_rtaImage\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/5975973075872440967_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click Purchase RSA.  carta/public/11/images/8017998755210624088_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Click Purchase RSA.<br> <img alt=\"Screenshot 2021-06-14 154355.png\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8017998755210624088_rtaImage\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/8017998755210624088_rtaImage"
        }
      }]
    }
  }]
}

{
  "id": "-6583767860051127239",
  "subject": {
    "id": "-6583767860051127239",
    "text": {
      "text": "How to Execute a Cash Exercise - Public Market Optionholders"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "1604968953306198650",
    "text": {
      "text": "This article is for admins and optionholders of Carta’s Public Market companies. Your public options can be exercised in three distinct ways:",
      "originalText": "This article is for admins and optionholders of Carta’s Public Market companies. Your public options can be exercised in three distinct ways:"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-7623332146655443550",
    "list": {
      "item": [{
        "text": "Cash exercise",
        "originalText": "Cash exercise"
      }, {
        "text": "Cashless exercise and hold",
        "originalText": "<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/cashless-hold-exercise\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Cashless exercise and hold</a>"
      }, {
        "text": "Cashless exercise and sell",
        "originalText": "<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/cashless-sell-exercise\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Cashless exercise and sell</a>"
      }]
    }
  }, {
    "id": "2226584362531194304",
    "text": {
      "text": "In a cash exercise, you will exercise your options at the strike price, or exercise price, and pay for them out-of-pocket, with your own cash. The total amount owed when exercising your options consists of the cost of the options being exercised, plus any taxes owed at the moment of the exercise.  NOTE: It is recommended that you consult your personal financial advisor or tax professional to make sure exercising is right for you.",
      "originalText": "In a cash exercise, you will exercise your options at the strike price, or exercise price, and pay for them out-of-pocket, with your own cash. The total amount owed when exercising your options consists of the cost of the options being exercised, plus any taxes owed at the moment of the exercise.&nbsp;<br><br>NOTE: It is recommended that you consult your personal financial advisor or tax professional to make sure exercising is right for you."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-5378066935953208551",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "Navigating your portfolio. After logging into your Carta account, click into the Portfolio page on the upper left navigation bar.  If you have holdings in multiple companies, select the issuing company.",
        "originalText": "Navigating your portfolio. After logging into your Carta account, click into the Portfolio page on the upper left navigation bar.<br> If you have holdings in multiple companies, select the issuing company.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Initiating the exercise workflow: Under the Holdings tab, review the list of options available. To the right of the option grant you wish to exercise, click the V dropdown and select Cash Exercise.  carta/public/11/images/6657740468839453637_VG-qz53e3TXPRmZSlTATVyoeFKhaH22ri2589k9paQQ8DMpdNJKuLY9vjMmG_2AkJG6S08aCS2nfrNWDk86a3tzv9_AfHTLdyy5FTKL1ScszOGYGjuIvTpCWwXL1qrKqbkitb_gd",
        "originalText": "Initiating the exercise workflow: Under the Holdings tab, review the list of options available. To the right of the option grant you wish to exercise, click the V dropdown and select Cash Exercise.<br> <img height=\"387\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6657740468839453637_VG-qz53e3TXPRmZSlTATVyoeFKhaH22ri2589k9paQQ8DMpdNJKuLY9vjMmG_2AkJG6S08aCS2nfrNWDk86a3tzv9_AfHTLdyy5FTKL1ScszOGYGjuIvTpCWwXL1qrKqbkitb_gd\" width=\"481\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/6657740468839453637_VG-qz53e3TXPRmZSlTATVyoeFKhaH22ri2589k9paQQ8DMpdNJKuLY9vjMmG_2AkJG6S08aCS2nfrNWDk86a3tzv9_AfHTLdyy5FTKL1ScszOGYGjuIvTpCWwXL1qrKqbkitb_gd"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Confirm you can exercise: Confirm your residence and ensure that your account information is up to date and accurate.  NOTE: If the issuing company does not have your legal residence on file, you will need to enter in the fields to continue. If the issuing company does have your address on file, the address will be pre-populated and you can contact the issuer if it needs to be updated.  carta/public/11/images/3027069544586742595_RscIzxX53BbtgDcttyVXOmlQVqOY3Y737MiN5OAtqXDEqx0bIshGRmXzTZNw-XzaQ88t7kwORjBrgo00BB0DR9KXWSlw0gZWfzH5_855eQ9vCZvaDclMT55RWe9YJtl3k_tg5jye",
        "originalText": "Confirm you can exercise: Confirm your residence and ensure that your account information is up to date and accurate.<br> NOTE: If the issuing company does not have your legal residence on file, you will need to enter in the fields to continue. If the issuing company does have your address on file, the address will be pre-populated and you can contact the issuer if it needs to be updated.<br> <img height=\"444\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3027069544586742595_RscIzxX53BbtgDcttyVXOmlQVqOY3Y737MiN5OAtqXDEqx0bIshGRmXzTZNw-XzaQ88t7kwORjBrgo00BB0DR9KXWSlw0gZWfzH5_855eQ9vCZvaDclMT55RWe9YJtl3k_tg5jye\" width=\"624\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/3027069544586742595_RscIzxX53BbtgDcttyVXOmlQVqOY3Y737MiN5OAtqXDEqx0bIshGRmXzTZNw-XzaQ88t7kwORjBrgo00BB0DR9KXWSlw0gZWfzH5_855eQ9vCZvaDclMT55RWe9YJtl3k_tg5jye"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Select option grant: You will be given a list of option grants (ISO, NSO, or ISO/NSO grant types) that are available to be exercised. Any option grants that have expired, been canceled, or have a pending exercise will not be available to be exercised.  NOTE: You can only initiate an exercise request one grant at a time. If you want to exercise multiple grants, submit another request after completing this workflow.  carta/public/11/images/5046882854936590816_OX0Rgb9rxU57oEhUuFmw0QMBeGshS0B6yHUySzr3svWjMIUffaalnCE9traAtL2NkLtN3dxdJ5TfAVvDSpOD8bw2H5zZcFnovAMf5mA1qlSWHtEbOIyVxK8WB3daaLgIhOEdW35Z",
        "originalText": "Select option grant: You will be given a list of option grants (ISO, NSO, or ISO/NSO grant types) that are available to be exercised. Any option grants that have expired, been canceled, or have a pending exercise will not be available to be exercised.<br> NOTE: You can only initiate an exercise request one grant at a time. If you want to exercise multiple grants, submit another request after completing this workflow.<br> <img height=\"544\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5046882854936590816_OX0Rgb9rxU57oEhUuFmw0QMBeGshS0B6yHUySzr3svWjMIUffaalnCE9traAtL2NkLtN3dxdJ5TfAVvDSpOD8bw2H5zZcFnovAMf5mA1qlSWHtEbOIyVxK8WB3daaLgIhOEdW35Z\" width=\"524\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/5046882854936590816_OX0Rgb9rxU57oEhUuFmw0QMBeGshS0B6yHUySzr3svWjMIUffaalnCE9traAtL2NkLtN3dxdJ5TfAVvDSpOD8bw2H5zZcFnovAMf5mA1qlSWHtEbOIyVxK8WB3daaLgIhOEdW35Z"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Select quantity of shares: Review the quantity of options that are available for you to exercise and enter it into the Amount to exercise box, or select Exercise all to fill the field with the maximum exercisable quantity.  carta/public/11/images/9088733461056957350_6F87B4TdWhWAItdEKZ_-zuJwgegsoPRs31nuo-6i1wMlvOCHntNp7Q9Z1JK50Mnl1CkRdi_Wru2vp5kj6vh6xDOfjquMdp3i8DmqTZvbbBYWdnqAaz2TQ75vr1XrnDEwqsNw3YRN    The schedules that follow for Fair Market Value, Exercise Price, Exercise gain/loss, and Subtotal price will populate with calculations based on the number of shares entered in the field.  When you are ready, click Next.  carta/public/11/images/1546648969199918606_cNfNKxfYr99keo5egEu49MSNCefXc5huHsuR2KHxHiGAMaWs3KtT0dNMszchnFCuQI7N-4e4JJF7H4CLNaNynsz29AScHxOt5wbRebmCiqTS6_I9asdD5OtQlV_VZwqcIS8uj9mf",
        "originalText": "Select quantity of shares: Review the quantity of options that are available for you to exercise and enter it into the Amount to exercise box, or select Exercise all to fill the field with the maximum exercisable quantity.<br> <img height=\"407\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/9088733461056957350_6F87B4TdWhWAItdEKZ_-zuJwgegsoPRs31nuo-6i1wMlvOCHntNp7Q9Z1JK50Mnl1CkRdi_Wru2vp5kj6vh6xDOfjquMdp3i8DmqTZvbbBYWdnqAaz2TQ75vr1XrnDEwqsNw3YRN\" width=\"534\"><br> <br> The schedules that follow for Fair Market Value, Exercise Price, Exercise gain/loss, and Subtotal price will populate with calculations based on the number of shares entered in the field.<br> When you are ready, click Next.<br> <img height=\"406\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1546648969199918606_cNfNKxfYr99keo5egEu49MSNCefXc5huHsuR2KHxHiGAMaWs3KtT0dNMszchnFCuQI7N-4e4JJF7H4CLNaNynsz29AScHxOt5wbRebmCiqTS6_I9asdD5OtQlV_VZwqcIS8uj9mf\" width=\"523\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/1546648969199918606_cNfNKxfYr99keo5egEu49MSNCefXc5huHsuR2KHxHiGAMaWs3KtT0dNMszchnFCuQI7N-4e4JJF7H4CLNaNynsz29AScHxOt5wbRebmCiqTS6_I9asdD5OtQlV_VZwqcIS8uj9mf"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Review today’s taxes: Based on the grant type (ISO or NSO), you may or may not have taxes obligations due at the time of exercise.  If you are exercising NSOs and are a U.S. employee of the issuing company during the time frame, you are likely to be subject to tax withholdings. Based on your residential address (city and state), the platform will assist in calculating the tax withholdings based on the maximum percentage for each area. These can be adjusted by the company’s exercise approver before they approve the exercise.    After reviewing the Taxes owed today, click Next.  carta/public/11/images/5796686809198441065_-e4Yjg4rdWWWjvMoOgBq4T56RAl7puo0RRv3kqRIPPYyTtnER6_TsrOrWISpYzB-efhMCqPxeH7MScDz_N8ad0T6pEsKcVidcUfV0Iy1ZVVHRbwFxoayNx5foqpoCXifqaBVz2LG",
        "originalText": "Review today’s taxes: Based on the grant type (ISO or NSO), you may or may not have taxes obligations due at the time of exercise.<br> If you are exercising NSOs and are a U.S. employee of the issuing company during the time frame, you are likely to be subject to tax withholdings. Based on your residential address (city and state), the platform will assist in calculating the tax withholdings based on the maximum percentage for each area. These can be adjusted by the company’s exercise approver before they approve the exercise.<br> <br> After reviewing the Taxes owed today, click Next.<br> <img height=\"424\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5796686809198441065_-e4Yjg4rdWWWjvMoOgBq4T56RAl7puo0RRv3kqRIPPYyTtnER6_TsrOrWISpYzB-efhMCqPxeH7MScDz_N8ad0T6pEsKcVidcUfV0Iy1ZVVHRbwFxoayNx5foqpoCXifqaBVz2LG\" width=\"527\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/5796686809198441065_-e4Yjg4rdWWWjvMoOgBq4T56RAl7puo0RRv3kqRIPPYyTtnER6_TsrOrWISpYzB-efhMCqPxeH7MScDz_N8ad0T6pEsKcVidcUfV0Iy1ZVVHRbwFxoayNx5foqpoCXifqaBVz2LG"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Your end of year taxes: Based on the grant type (ISO or NSO), you may or may not have taxes obligations due at the end of the year for the exercise.  If you are exercising NSOs, you will not pay any additional taxes for the exercise unless you sell your shares.    Review end of year taxes and click I understand.  carta/public/11/images/2188367453533496425_yWH20WqS3NxxC6yQc9jrsJTaa0ruiaJyOO7CTTCh9BFsMyRquMc9XdKWKDLznqZlqAzcciAvHixRwgp4jR-CuAb5xrFWIiSd0HOtNdJVORp_cOESrAH_VVf5MyVFHLpJmPAESIz9",
        "originalText": "Your end of year taxes: Based on the grant type (ISO or NSO), you may or may not have taxes obligations due at the end of the year for the exercise.<br> If you are exercising NSOs, you will not pay any additional taxes for the exercise unless you sell your shares.<br> <br> Review end of year taxes and click I understand.<br> <img height=\"404\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/2188367453533496425_yWH20WqS3NxxC6yQc9jrsJTaa0ruiaJyOO7CTTCh9BFsMyRquMc9XdKWKDLznqZlqAzcciAvHixRwgp4jR-CuAb5xrFWIiSd0HOtNdJVORp_cOESrAH_VVf5MyVFHLpJmPAESIz9\" width=\"530\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/2188367453533496425_yWH20WqS3NxxC6yQc9jrsJTaa0ruiaJyOO7CTTCh9BFsMyRquMc9XdKWKDLznqZlqAzcciAvHixRwgp4jR-CuAb5xrFWIiSd0HOtNdJVORp_cOESrAH_VVf5MyVFHLpJmPAESIz9"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Review exercise: Review the details of your exercise request, including the Total amount payable, and ensure that all the information on this page is accurate.  Ensure that your payment account selected is correct under the Payment Method section. If you wish to use a different account for payment, click Change account and make the necessary changes.  Finally, click the checkboxes below to agree to the withdrawal of funds from your account and to Carta’s Payment Terms and Conditions.  Click Sign and submit exercise request to proceed.  carta/public/11/images/2453416886582843583_RBLJ4xLUEdI0C8TFIHeZbzZ2PUZWXQc03En_HNefps_5xQXyKcVMpq8Hueltexd_sxE8sr7L4KhprpNkIRtHBHgggMXvwBSYPqgM5PYNMC9tyoFF1XyvRlDfEj_15WRizqzXBNRB",
        "originalText": "Review exercise: Review the details of your exercise request, including the Total amount payable, and ensure that all the information on this page is accurate.<br> Ensure that your payment account selected is correct under the Payment Method section. If you wish to use a different account for payment, click Change account and make the necessary changes.<br> Finally, click the checkboxes below to agree to the withdrawal of funds from your account and to Carta’s Payment Terms and Conditions.<br> Click Sign and submit exercise request to proceed.<br> <img height=\"774\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/2453416886582843583_RBLJ4xLUEdI0C8TFIHeZbzZ2PUZWXQc03En_HNefps_5xQXyKcVMpq8Hueltexd_sxE8sr7L4KhprpNkIRtHBHgggMXvwBSYPqgM5PYNMC9tyoFF1XyvRlDfEj_15WRizqzXBNRB\" width=\"529\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/2453416886582843583_RBLJ4xLUEdI0C8TFIHeZbzZ2PUZWXQc03En_HNefps_5xQXyKcVMpq8Hueltexd_sxE8sr7L4KhprpNkIRtHBHgggMXvwBSYPqgM5PYNMC9tyoFF1XyvRlDfEj_15WRizqzXBNRB"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Sign and submit exercise request: You will need to check off the boxes for the documents attached to your option grant and type your name to electronically sign. When you are ready to submit your exercise, click Submit.  carta/public/11/images/2765500033851040353_o9qudKrTCdYeYE3W9aF_GxnOa58t0uOR5HsIJjoNdm30iF_MWA1TmhBZIm8CO3YYprUUjG8ljuq6bSV2Iyb8L4ZVyomyAc9pMGtqrIG0VLRlmHi8pqAwIzyRyki8fsMoFceXU-Vf",
        "originalText": "Sign and submit exercise request: You will need to check off the boxes for the documents attached to your option grant and type your name to electronically sign. When you are ready to submit your exercise, click Submit.<br> <img height=\"390\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/2765500033851040353_o9qudKrTCdYeYE3W9aF_GxnOa58t0uOR5HsIJjoNdm30iF_MWA1TmhBZIm8CO3YYprUUjG8ljuq6bSV2Iyb8L4ZVyomyAc9pMGtqrIG0VLRlmHi8pqAwIzyRyki8fsMoFceXU-Vf\" width=\"431\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/2765500033851040353_o9qudKrTCdYeYE3W9aF_GxnOa58t0uOR5HsIJjoNdm30iF_MWA1TmhBZIm8CO3YYprUUjG8ljuq6bSV2Iyb8L4ZVyomyAc9pMGtqrIG0VLRlmHi8pqAwIzyRyki8fsMoFceXU-Vf"
        }
