    "text": {
      "text": "International option holders of private US companies can exercise through Carta via wire transfer. This is an old flow that will be deprecated soon. Refer to this workflow for non-US optionholders to exercise their options.",
      "originalText": "International option holders of private US companies can exercise through Carta via wire transfer. This is an old flow that will be deprecated soon. <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/enabling-online-transactions-non-us\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Refer to this workflow</u></a> for non-US optionholders to exercise their options.<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "580967905839055284",
