        "originalText": "Select a repurchase reason from the dropdown and enter a date for the repurchase.<br> <img height=\"105\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1096283092172284042_nun5EjtLAcQzPorcrjiHvBTY_gwcIOqlaee2-LGvHoow6VYLKF5pjlpQ2-6IY9FJVc9ehsRAW9MO9FEs_v0OBGCcSr1gAgpXD_dynBTYCfk28-uvyJn7o9S9yOx1aIU5Jc-EsQHk\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"442\"><br> NOTE:  The selected certificate for repurchase will be shown on the left-hand side throughout the workflow. Tagging repurchases with specific reasons will provide structure to your data and allow for more accurate reporting. If reflecting a historical repurchase, provide the date on which the repurchase occurred.  <br> &nbsp;",
