        "originalText": "Attach a repurchase agreement and provide the transaction value and select whether or not to transfer funds through Carta using ACH.<br> <img height=\"225\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5693967399900335473_7TB-phed7wtYwJzttX965zIjauscjO4tXTerlekGfdn7WkUQcGEZkngqOLbUcpKDQQqYNxX4Hvp6o7NJpaBPdWdkLxtWIktmhWqbZOCitQz4b44IKmnolBbQwWC2NxmQwC49jdac\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"432\"><br> NOTE:  If you would not like to transfer funds through Carta and would like to proceed with the transaction offline, select No for the Transfer funds via ACH? question. The Transfer funds via ACH? question will only appear if both the company and the stakeholder involved in the repurchase have connected their bank accounts in Carta.  <br> &nbsp;",
