        "originalText": "If Yes is selected for the Transfer funds via ACH? question, an additional table with bank account information will appear. Check off I agree to the withdrawal… and click Next to proceed.<br> If No is selected, simply click Next to proceed.<br> <img height=\"236\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6111625027410719507_1jDoWaPlRkzrS4sPxXQVM_PkEayYx0-FvgtmA8-HHsqVti7EaKS0xQcjsTL12q4-NWFUIlPchRONyTrMNodwPjZLNDMcpt6f94OnoQ5FGZGOgLUYBdJHgTZBxUASSK1xMykY8tRZ\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"433\"><br> &nbsp;",
