      "text": "Before turning on online transactions, a user withCompany Editor orLegal Administrator permissions must set up the company’s bank account on Carta. ACH transactions only work for bank accounts based in the United States (and may not work for brokerage accounts). Only Checkings accounts are supported. The bank account(s) added can be used for online transactions and subscription billing purposes. Learn more about viewing your subscription.  In this video demo, you will review how to add a bank account, designate it for subscription payments, and enable ACH transactions.\n Video: ",
