        "originalText": "In the Payment Information tab, click + Add payment method to add payment methods. If needed, multiple bank accounts can be added.<br> <img height=\"187\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8552902780977088687_vnPyug3JhepE_zzyINRSecZPMI5VucE5qzIBNJtbVzky-exDfCDmkl2LJzFEbHSsW_TTBtfIKkyALBqimdUgxZSULFrSzNBQxZ4mfyPAljtdavYrtfO7K3Sy8faDTOfjBC1EOEyr\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"430\"><br> <img height=\"216\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7276638570919569902_tzenpkRb4sEmkLlJqU--6AAFIfD171wMJk93QI6wOtem9CM7qW71B9UYQT1y-JAG_BlXnNW8J_da_178dD2w39uJD_3jPh5Ysg1HVNJ_sdysk1nr-X4MWCW_X3MukCZGdJ91TND2\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"433\">",
