      "text": "After accepting your security, you can log into Carta and view it at any time. If you have any questions, submit a case via Carta's Help Center after you create your Carta account. Learn more about Carta's Help Center.",
      "originalText": "After accepting your security, you can log into Carta and view it at any time. If you have any questions, submit a case via <a href=\"https://app.carta.com/profiles/update?help=true\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Carta's Help Center</u></a> after you create your Carta account. <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/carta-help-center\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Learn more about Carta's Help Center</u></a>."
