{
  "id": "-6980203829946703058",
  "subject": {
    "id": "-6980203829946703058",
    "text": {
      "text": "Accepting Securities into New or Existing Portfolios"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "1435256148862065459",
    "text": {
      "text": "Issuing companies may use different names when issuing securities to users. To avoid creating multiple portfolios within Carta, users can choose which portfolio they would like to use for securities that are issued to names not associated with their existing Carta account. For example, Tagg Palmer may have securities to accept under “Taggert E Palmer” and “Tagg Palmer”.",
      "originalText": "Issuing companies may use different names when issuing securities to users. To avoid creating multiple portfolios within Carta, users can choose which portfolio they would like to use for securities that are issued to names not associated with their existing Carta account.<br>For example, Tagg Palmer may have securities to accept under “Taggert E Palmer” and “Tagg Palmer”."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "5118788086367480787",
    "text": {
      "text": "If you receive a security issued to a name that does not already have a corresponding portfolio, you will be presented with the option to choose an existing portfolio or create a new portfolio under that name. carta/public/11/images/3697571934268463468_ZNvlzUUCH7zrVtqc9FPgykwSCaPvDsI6nd30KJwI0qzJEGLdnQm_ZmF-dx51LduJb-eIGGvSsvO-sJsEaqpK7AingZh63wHI1MqnSsfYK4I5h10NjJDrCb9-O9eTR_Ekyh52K95i",
      "originalText": "If you receive a security issued to a name that does not already have a corresponding portfolio, you will be presented with the option to choose an existing portfolio or create a new portfolio under that name.<br><img height=\"403\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3697571934268463468_ZNvlzUUCH7zrVtqc9FPgykwSCaPvDsI6nd30KJwI0qzJEGLdnQm_ZmF-dx51LduJb-eIGGvSsvO-sJsEaqpK7AingZh63wHI1MqnSsfYK4I5h10NjJDrCb9-O9eTR_Ekyh52K95i\" width=\"624\">",
      "associatedImage": {
        "url": "carta/public/11/images/3697571934268463468_ZNvlzUUCH7zrVtqc9FPgykwSCaPvDsI6nd30KJwI0qzJEGLdnQm_ZmF-dx51LduJb-eIGGvSsvO-sJsEaqpK7AingZh63wHI1MqnSsfYK4I5h10NjJDrCb9-O9eTR_Ekyh52K95i"
      }
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-1401976996376616676",
    "text": {
      "text": "If you select an existing portfolio, your security will appear in that portfolio. The name on that security and the issuing company’s cap table will remain the name of the issued security (i.e.“Taggert E Palmer”).  If you choose to create a new portfolio, the portfolio will take on the name that the security was issued to and will now appear in theAccounts drop down in the upper left of your Carta account.",
      "originalText": "If you select an existing portfolio, your security will appear in that portfolio. The name on that security and the issuing company’s cap table will remain the name of the issued security (i.e.“Taggert E Palmer”).<br><br>If you choose to create a new portfolio, the portfolio will take on the name that the security was issued to and will now appear in the Accounts drop down in the upper left of your Carta account.<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "7174871918159311118",
    "text": {
      "text": "NOTE: If you are accepting a security on behalf of a trust, it is recommend to create a new portfolio with the trust name. If your security is transferring to a trust, contact the issuer.",
      "originalText": "NOTE: If you are accepting a security on behalf of a trust, it is recommend to create a new portfolio with the trust name. If your security is transferring to a trust, <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/contacting-the-issuer\" target=\"_blank\"><u>contact the issuer.</u></a> &nbsp;"
    }
  }]
}

