{
  "id": "1993586502622581401",
  "subject": {
    "id": "1993586502622581401",
    "text": {
      "text": "Where can I find and download an 83(b) election form?",
      "originalText": "Where can I find and download&nbsp;an 83(b) election form?"
    },
    "signals": [{
      "valueL": "2"
    }]
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-62743855426517328",
    "text": {
      "text": "If you have early exercised an option grant via Carta's workflow, a pre-filled 83(b) form will be generated for you at the end of the workflow for you to download, sign, then mail to the IRS. NOTE: 83(b) elections are not generated in relation to RSAs on Carta.",
      "originalText": "If you have early exercised an option grant via Carta's workflow, a pre-filled 83(b) form will be generated for you at the end of the workflow for you to download, sign, then mail to the IRS.<br>NOTE:&nbsp;83(b) elections are not generated in relation to RSAs on Carta."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "8663766511732020484",
    "text": {
      "text": "After early exercising, the 83(b) election can be found on the83(b) elections tab of the exercised option grant. It is strongly recommended to submit a copy of your signed 83(b) election form to the issuing company. Within the83(b) election tab of the exercised option grant, a scanned copy of the form can be uploaded for the issuing company. carta/public/11/images/4023355369945536089_4lpyBRbaFhHUjbxpYv9GJ97RySap7m8dN9JFhRnBKwdXXtTn1RFSKFxvtyq6qrp-G8I8dNmtwjiW8_An7CdjrfoeBkNK6YUbcwe2druaj6S_lgFXd-5HsvWRzkuSfoYqTideAN6e  Choose the file to upload, enter the date that you mailed the form to the IRS, and selectSave this 83(b) election. Now, the issuing company will have access to a copy of the executed document. carta/public/11/images/6675169419960109098_uZZmU3qid3z8kSPH_YJ11JzaB7uspRYok5kUGX5M94sLuWK3AI30F4WF-b954IkF8hbbSXVuzZFo2j0SxPIIc99RPYqi0UOIJ8g9ScFxqId-TD-wYO9yshmCW8odwZqzL6HiZbpH  Alternatively, you can notify the issuing company that an 83(b) election for this option exercise will not be made by checking off the boxI do not wish to make 83(b) elections for this option exercise. carta/public/11/images/8522242189007062329_jecQw4fF7NIzSbHsUqlWEd0VTsril9z6Lx83rn08A0IzcsQTCqTHtouHvZmhRyYwB34k61ldT_yTwCME0pw6Xsyuz0ox4O2zKNOyPiVT76g-A88WzS6UzLPMQDUuODx_cfq5Oq4P  If needed, you can download Carta’s templated IRS Section 83(b) Election Form which includes information on where to send your form. Before mailing the completed 83(b) election form, review and consult with your tax advisor to ensure accurate information. 83(b) Election Form (blank template)",
      "originalText": "After early exercising, the 83(b) election can be found on the 83(b) elections tab of the exercised option grant. It is strongly recommended to submit a copy of your signed 83(b) election form to the issuing company. Within the 83(b) election tab of the exercised option grant, a scanned copy of the form can be uploaded for the issuing company.<br><img height=\"419\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/4023355369945536089_4lpyBRbaFhHUjbxpYv9GJ97RySap7m8dN9JFhRnBKwdXXtTn1RFSKFxvtyq6qrp-G8I8dNmtwjiW8_An7CdjrfoeBkNK6YUbcwe2druaj6S_lgFXd-5HsvWRzkuSfoYqTideAN6e\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"624.0000000000001\"><br><br>Choose the file to upload, enter the date that you mailed the form to the IRS, and select Save this 83(b) election. Now, the issuing company will have access to a copy of the executed document.<br><img height=\"443\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6675169419960109098_uZZmU3qid3z8kSPH_YJ11JzaB7uspRYok5kUGX5M94sLuWK3AI30F4WF-b954IkF8hbbSXVuzZFo2j0SxPIIc99RPYqi0UOIJ8g9ScFxqId-TD-wYO9yshmCW8odwZqzL6HiZbpH\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"624\"><br><br>Alternatively, you can notify the issuing company that an 83(b) election for this option exercise will not be made by checking off the box I do not wish to make 83(b) elections for this option exercise.<br><img height=\"420\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8522242189007062329_jecQw4fF7NIzSbHsUqlWEd0VTsril9z6Lx83rn08A0IzcsQTCqTHtouHvZmhRyYwB34k61ldT_yTwCME0pw6Xsyuz0ox4O2zKNOyPiVT76g-A88WzS6UzLPMQDUuODx_cfq5Oq4P\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"624\"><br><br>If needed, you can download Carta’s templated IRS Section 83(b) Election Form which includes information on where to send your form. Before mailing the completed 83(b) election form, review and consult with your tax advisor to ensure accurate information.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://carta.my.salesforce.com/sfc/p/f4000000nrKS/a/0H000000Xm1Z/H0r8oAMKO54MeOPha6Y2ej8zlCnIrPzVyQsFP5XdboU\" target=\"_blank\">83(b) Election Form (blank template)</a><br>&nbsp;",
      "associatedImage": {
        "url": "carta/public/11/images/8522242189007062329_jecQw4fF7NIzSbHsUqlWEd0VTsril9z6Lx83rn08A0IzcsQTCqTHtouHvZmhRyYwB34k61ldT_yTwCME0pw6Xsyuz0ox4O2zKNOyPiVT76g-A88WzS6UzLPMQDUuODx_cfq5Oq4P"
      }
    }
  }]
}

