        "text": "If you have trouble downloading the files, check your browser permissions to allow pop-ups and redirects from app.carta.com.  carta/public/11/images/6502117796852321867_CM2phuluK0FjTKQV4tITjms3Ag6UwsoL31al-Tp0zEnmYShN5eJaNtM5231b1YMadT7b7hoiiYoOA3Fkp1uYXOGbDCyr294RKgMiWPn_sgYZCbKhEsTaoyIAAIbAuVJGvvTt38VS",
        "originalText": "If you have trouble downloading the files, check your browser permissions to allow pop-ups and redirects from app.carta.com.<br> <img height=\"259\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6502117796852321867_CM2phuluK0FjTKQV4tITjms3Ag6UwsoL31al-Tp0zEnmYShN5eJaNtM5231b1YMadT7b7hoiiYoOA3Fkp1uYXOGbDCyr294RKgMiWPn_sgYZCbKhEsTaoyIAAIbAuVJGvvTt38VS\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"325\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/6502117796852321867_CM2phuluK0FjTKQV4tITjms3Ag6UwsoL31al-Tp0zEnmYShN5eJaNtM5231b1YMadT7b7hoiiYoOA3Fkp1uYXOGbDCyr294RKgMiWPn_sgYZCbKhEsTaoyIAAIbAuVJGvvTt38VS"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "For ISO/NSO split option grants, two separate 83(b) election forms will be generated. For most browser settings, this will open in two new tabs.",
        "originalText": "For ISO/NSO split option grants, two separate 83(b) election forms will be generated. For most browser settings, this will open in two new tabs."
      }, {
        "text": "For ISO/NSO split option grants, where exercised ISOs are vested, exercised NSOs are unvested, the first 83(b) form for the vested quantity will not be needed. In this case, consult your tax advisor to confirm the best way to file your 83(b) election for your early exercised ISO/NSO split option grant.  carta/public/11/images/8501661333562202109_PSrUl8FCTz5cGXvUAZBK35kVnRwTkb5AfF6Gl0y4Ijl0T87OFUMLrsw4jj5nZ1CBMXGQdSMMCa0fcLyhnAev9_JuB7H0IzYokWIT50qqh3XjuDk-8vcuHKnjSm4uhzN7952jS-E_",
        "originalText": "For ISO/NSO split option grants, where exercised ISOs are vested, exercised NSOs are unvested, the first 83(b) form for the vested quantity will not be needed. In this case, consult your tax advisor to confirm the best way to file your 83(b) election for your early exercised ISO/NSO split option grant.<br> <img height=\"368\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8501661333562202109_PSrUl8FCTz5cGXvUAZBK35kVnRwTkb5AfF6Gl0y4Ijl0T87OFUMLrsw4jj5nZ1CBMXGQdSMMCa0fcLyhnAev9_JuB7H0IzYokWIT50qqh3XjuDk-8vcuHKnjSm4uhzN7952jS-E_\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"624\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/8501661333562202109_PSrUl8FCTz5cGXvUAZBK35kVnRwTkb5AfF6Gl0y4Ijl0T87OFUMLrsw4jj5nZ1CBMXGQdSMMCa0fcLyhnAev9_JuB7H0IzYokWIT50qqh3XjuDk-8vcuHKnjSm4uhzN7952jS-E_"
        }
      }]
    }
  }, {
    "id": "7807253616079651476",
