      "text": "On thePortfolio details page, on theHoldings tab, you will see anExercise button if you have options available to exercise. Click theExercise button to begin an exercise request. carta/public/11/images/3525159676060470164_4-Q_IVd2vMPapv2CrFho97tlgGer5W6nuLoodAOn2F3nHN8lEwO2q_vyI_3tgE_1SA-15PLR3fd_gD2uRS-c0v5LdUEarbdrSOHRT0eVKA_7fbFkmwqGG8vt34CEDXDY56oKsC8R",
