    "id": "8619188648956807447",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "Confirm you can exercise: It is recommended that you read Carta’s Equity 101 FAQs and consult your personal financial advisor or tax professional to make sure exercising is right for you.  The first step is to confirm that your residence information is up to date and accurate.  NOTE: If the issuing company does not have your legal residence on file, you will need to enter in the fields to continue. If the issuing company does have your address on file, the address will be pre-populated and you can contact the issuer if it needs to be updated. carta/public/11/images/228875266336863331_TgEqZuJAs2a20UF0t5cqrUyD1jFx4DZhdYqM93-N64u7oxUC_5zPzAVwVeTSk7HZPqlVEnzZJHwfKyCe8CDxy2ynXbXo2N_MeRjMY8ajBWD4dpI_033dOEKbG0X_m331BctNfciX",
        "originalText": " Confirm you can exercise: It is recommended that you read Carta’s Equity 101 FAQs and consult your personal financial advisor or tax professional to make sure exercising is right for you.<br> <br> The first step is to confirm that your residence information is up to date and accurate.<br> NOTE: If the issuing company does not have your legal residence on file, you will need to enter in the fields to continue. If the issuing company does have your address on file, the address will be pre-populated and you can <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/contacting-the-issuer\" target=\"_blank\"><u>contact the issuer</u></a> if it needs to be updated.<br> <img height=\"483\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/228875266336863331_TgEqZuJAs2a20UF0t5cqrUyD1jFx4DZhdYqM93-N64u7oxUC_5zPzAVwVeTSk7HZPqlVEnzZJHwfKyCe8CDxy2ynXbXo2N_MeRjMY8ajBWD4dpI_033dOEKbG0X_m331BctNfciX\" width=\"720\"> ",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/228875266336863331_TgEqZuJAs2a20UF0t5cqrUyD1jFx4DZhdYqM93-N64u7oxUC_5zPzAVwVeTSk7HZPqlVEnzZJHwfKyCe8CDxy2ynXbXo2N_MeRjMY8ajBWD4dpI_033dOEKbG0X_m331BctNfciX"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Select option grant: You will be given a list of option grants that are available to be exercised. Any option grants that have expired, been canceled, or have a pending exercise will not be available to be exercised. carta/public/11/images/6238634972331904476_8qmh4DG_9SZhV8Jy8vYp2vdUx3k59zzwubfY2eqGqsUKaxdVxA_m_x4eDvUJ6-2no5_YwuuMj6J_hHAi1UOLTeGJMi7r2lt0dOQkbrqN1O66GRRc97mPD0GJuD9mtTYxedOO-53v",
        "originalText": " Select option grant: You will be given a list of option grants that are available to be exercised. Any option grants that have expired, been canceled, or have a pending exercise&nbsp;will not be available to be exercised.<br> <br> <img height=\"456.502756339581\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6238634972331904476_8qmh4DG_9SZhV8Jy8vYp2vdUx3k59zzwubfY2eqGqsUKaxdVxA_m_x4eDvUJ6-2no5_YwuuMj6J_hHAi1UOLTeGJMi7r2lt0dOQkbrqN1O66GRRc97mPD0GJuD9mtTYxedOO-53v\" width=\"720\"><br> &nbsp; ",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/6238634972331904476_8qmh4DG_9SZhV8Jy8vYp2vdUx3k59zzwubfY2eqGqsUKaxdVxA_m_x4eDvUJ6-2no5_YwuuMj6J_hHAi1UOLTeGJMi7r2lt0dOQkbrqN1O66GRRc97mPD0GJuD9mtTYxedOO-53v"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Select shares: Review the quantity of options that are available for you to exercise and enter it into theAmount to exercise box. The total pre-tax cost will automatically be calculated below. When you are ready, clickNext. carta/public/11/images/7435761359803174787_2WWQ7bDnOZqA5_K68GPRAEE2aRU5_rhCXxs5_hPTHDWRWbdAEAb3ZedZL72tkFOhM60nP0ebOWDLZnQpJ_77HZ3Kgi-ZSn4M5Ki85gp8fux0CZkL1tM7yyd5P-blzlC_HZ4NgEUi",
        "originalText": " Select shares: Review the quantity of options that are available for you to exercise and enter it into the Amount to exercise&nbsp;box. The total pre-tax cost will automatically be calculated below. When you are ready, click Next.<br> <img height=\"405\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7435761359803174787_2WWQ7bDnOZqA5_K68GPRAEE2aRU5_rhCXxs5_hPTHDWRWbdAEAb3ZedZL72tkFOhM60nP0ebOWDLZnQpJ_77HZ3Kgi-ZSn4M5Ki85gp8fux0CZkL1tM7yyd5P-blzlC_HZ4NgEUi\" width=\"720\"><br> &nbsp; ",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/7435761359803174787_2WWQ7bDnOZqA5_K68GPRAEE2aRU5_rhCXxs5_hPTHDWRWbdAEAb3ZedZL72tkFOhM60nP0ebOWDLZnQpJ_77HZ3Kgi-ZSn4M5Ki85gp8fux0CZkL1tM7yyd5P-blzlC_HZ4NgEUi"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Review your taxes today: Based on the grant type (ISO or NSO), you may or may not have taxes obligations due at exercise.4a.If you are exercising ISOs, you may not have taxes owed at the time of exercise, but you may be subject to AMT taxes which will be estimated in the next step. carta/public/11/images/3500316670493041849_VBZI_N_uWGCQblOayhDYMuMseZF90b74-Iqway3kCCrEw6qGzgIW48SM0Ocf9F0DJpT0Zp4aItlJymZjJP06n3YOjXvKMggI3hWKcuc1d2R0_28uViZkDHdLDXcsZeB06vJsDBLp4b.If you are exercising NSOs and were a U.S. employee of the issuing company during the time frame, you are likely to be subject to tax withholdings. Based on your address, the platform will assist in calculating the tax withholdings based on the maximum percentage for each area. These can be adjusted by the Company’s exercise approver before they approve the exercise. carta/public/11/images/5461828387921402481_iIBv8SN2LxUEz_WinFwOke1x9TIGHAZjAU8cqDQZLEW69kzvmpUQcHqoSQvpOhKJN06gr8X_5UIkbMkuwDMTcqzNPcWCgCIXqIMGSJvMQ7jTmd-4tdzuwKmaghic1wyoGmBrI579",
        "originalText": " Review your taxes today: Based on the grant type (ISO or NSO), you may or may not have taxes obligations due at exercise.<br> <br> 4a. If you are exercising ISOs, you may not have taxes owed at the time of exercise, but you may be subject to AMT taxes which will be estimated in the next step.<br> <img height=\"301\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3500316670493041849_VBZI_N_uWGCQblOayhDYMuMseZF90b74-Iqway3kCCrEw6qGzgIW48SM0Ocf9F0DJpT0Zp4aItlJymZjJP06n3YOjXvKMggI3hWKcuc1d2R0_28uViZkDHdLDXcsZeB06vJsDBLp\" width=\"624\"><br> <br> 4b. &nbsp;If you are exercising NSOs and were a U.S. employee of the issuing company during the time frame, you are likely to be subject to tax withholdings. Based on your address, the platform will assist in calculating the tax withholdings based on the maximum percentage for each area. These can be adjusted by the Company’s exercise approver before they approve the exercise.<br> <img height=\"487\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5461828387921402481_iIBv8SN2LxUEz_WinFwOke1x9TIGHAZjAU8cqDQZLEW69kzvmpUQcHqoSQvpOhKJN06gr8X_5UIkbMkuwDMTcqzNPcWCgCIXqIMGSJvMQ7jTmd-4tdzuwKmaghic1wyoGmBrI579\" width=\"720\"><br> &nbsp; ",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/5461828387921402481_iIBv8SN2LxUEz_WinFwOke1x9TIGHAZjAU8cqDQZLEW69kzvmpUQcHqoSQvpOhKJN06gr8X_5UIkbMkuwDMTcqzNPcWCgCIXqIMGSJvMQ7jTmd-4tdzuwKmaghic1wyoGmBrI579"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Your end of year taxes: Based on the grant type (ISO or NSO), you may or may not have taxes obligations due at the end of the year for the exercise.5a.If you are exercising ISOs, the platform will estimate AMT taxes based on the option spread from current fair market value to the exercise price. carta/public/11/images/1442373177848935813_0jlSLH1LzDuf6a7vZ-Xx1sX1D8n2mwAsUzpVAWzrVtg8Ljd2yJeUmXk-NzkNx24nRg7tSCEz4_9gbLfCjNVmeoZxQdt5j6FBCxqRzzO7ezduarxgCXwopRU-D4Q6iK0IW-kTyF6t5b.If you are exercising NSOs, you are likely to not owe additional taxes upon exercise, unless you sell your shares at a later time. carta/public/11/images/6037485532608892177_fTQPk-A_ZJKD-wn8QqPyeLNbHU0SGxr7HY_C4HvlXfGFdy5T9d1nGF9JX50c8Kc3LVoSxuYUXdagazWbjw5SQnsQO_AJgWBZJC1LEC2Ygh5H2nKefRfYJQYv_fMoz0R2FZuIsLn8",
        "originalText": " Your end of year taxes: Based on the grant type (ISO or NSO), you may or may not have taxes obligations due at the end of the year for the exercise.<br> <br> 5a.&nbsp; If you are exercising ISOs, the platform will estimate AMT taxes based on the option spread from current fair market value to the exercise price.<br> <img height=\"401\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1442373177848935813_0jlSLH1LzDuf6a7vZ-Xx1sX1D8n2mwAsUzpVAWzrVtg8Ljd2yJeUmXk-NzkNx24nRg7tSCEz4_9gbLfCjNVmeoZxQdt5j6FBCxqRzzO7ezduarxgCXwopRU-D4Q6iK0IW-kTyF6t\" width=\"624\"><br> <br> 5b. If you are exercising NSOs, you are likely to not owe additional taxes upon exercise, unless you sell your shares at a later time.<br> <img height=\"343\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6037485532608892177_fTQPk-A_ZJKD-wn8QqPyeLNbHU0SGxr7HY_C4HvlXfGFdy5T9d1nGF9JX50c8Kc3LVoSxuYUXdagazWbjw5SQnsQO_AJgWBZJC1LEC2Ygh5H2nKefRfYJQYv_fMoz0R2FZuIsLn8\" width=\"720\"><br> &nbsp; ",
