        "text": "Tranche information: The primary content of the report is the tranche information organized into eight columns (i.e. Columns A through H)  carta/public/11/images/3968529198615410309_lAzbvpr3LyHIcbvB83P0YA8BfwY8I1GMFlkVdx3JrsnsTqXuA50-p3_k6VwMqnv2fQkkXG3NucNlVCZasEmJiBabZ1yMYUYm3BdfF2YTRTDVyfoPC24fafYtwVZyOVrp4LsJgJN7Exercisable date - the date on which a particular tranche becomes exercisable. Usually the same as the vesting date for a tranche unless the option grant is early exercisable. If a grant is early exercisable (like in the example screenshot above), the exercisable date of every tranche will be the issue date of the grant.Vesting date - the date on which a particular tranche vests or becomes earned by the stakeholder.ISO shares - the quantity of ISO shares in a given tranche.NSO shares - the quantity of NSO shares in a given tranche.ISO value - the US dollar value of the ISO shares in a given tranche.NSO value - the US dollar value of the NSO shares in a given tranche.Total shares - the total quantity of ISO and NSO shares in a given tranche.Total value - the total US dollar value of the ISO and NSO shares in a given tranche.",
        "originalText": "Tranche information: The primary content of the report is the tranche information organized into eight columns (i.e. Columns A through H)<br> <img height=\"287\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3968529198615410309_lAzbvpr3LyHIcbvB83P0YA8BfwY8I1GMFlkVdx3JrsnsTqXuA50-p3_k6VwMqnv2fQkkXG3NucNlVCZasEmJiBabZ1yMYUYm3BdfF2YTRTDVyfoPC24fafYtwVZyOVrp4LsJgJN7\" width=\"476\"><br> &nbsp;  Exercisable date - the date on which a particular tranche becomes exercisable. Usually the same as the vesting date for a tranche unless the option grant is early exercisable. If a grant is early exercisable (like in the example screenshot above), the exercisable date of every tranche will be the issue date of the grant. Vesting date - the date on which a particular tranche vests or becomes earned by the stakeholder. ISO shares - the quantity of ISO shares in a given tranche. NSO shares - the quantity of NSO shares in a given tranche. ISO value - the US dollar value of the ISO shares in a given tranche. NSO value - the US dollar value of the NSO shares in a given tranche. Total shares - the total quantity of ISO and NSO shares in a given tranche. Total value - the total US dollar value of the ISO and NSO shares in a given tranche.<br> &nbsp;  ",
        "associatedImage": {
