    "text": {
      "text": "The grant editor is a powerful tool that gives legal administrators the ability to override the Carta-estimated distribution of ISO shares versus NSO shares within a vesting tranche for an ISO/NSO split option grant. Our customers and their legal teams need this flexibility and customization as there are instances in which the interpretation and the scope of application of the ISO 100K rules differ between Carta’s ISO 100K calculator and an issuing company’s legal counsel.",
