        "originalText": "Employee information: Basic employee identification information can be found at the top of the screen, including employee name, email address, and their current relationship with the company.<br> <img height=\"233\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/4297227128433538826_kUcRHgyVjg4wDUhTzOYY-DKBS6TixlP4ZJsXgB4c9Cld-x5kMNRoGirlqxCpNuvFu0ra1tHBCC-4RXQxSaqpPQNTwhQw_OrWoL15PIKWKhG1XT17stQ2Qs_soLJyo_xlbYyjHOuN\" width=\"184\">",
        "associatedImage": {
