        }
      }, {
        "text": "Grant switcher: If multiple grants for a particular stakeholder need to be overridden, use the grant switcher to quickly switch between individual ISO/NSO split option grants for the selected stakeholder. You can edit a grant and subsequently switch to and edit additional grants before clicking Finish editing and save to save all edits across all grants in one action.  carta/public/11/images/3013145238431885001_W8T8RFptYUpgHWSsr6wmT_IVLcWpVEZp3TQ8sE6rqe4T1FUn1Av5t1cxfE8266qZ9XHPT8xC6WZPIFWkYbPGcnSPnMD8RmEh0RNtmmhK6HswViGq7K9MR6GQjKqqu6U-QbN4m7oR",
        "originalText": "Grant switcher: If multiple grants for a particular stakeholder need to be overridden, use the grant switcher to quickly switch between individual ISO/NSO split option grants for the selected stakeholder. You can edit a grant and subsequently switch to and edit additional grants before clicking Finish editing and save to save all edits across all grants in one action.<br> <img height=\"521\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3013145238431885001_W8T8RFptYUpgHWSsr6wmT_IVLcWpVEZp3TQ8sE6rqe4T1FUn1Av5t1cxfE8266qZ9XHPT8xC6WZPIFWkYbPGcnSPnMD8RmEh0RNtmmhK6HswViGq7K9MR6GQjKqqu6U-QbN4m7oR\" width=\"205\">",
