    "id": "-3075329961001664759",
    "text": {
      "text": "Once the grant editor is used on a stakeholder’s grant, Carta will notify legal administrators in two different ways if a modification is made to the stakeholder’s ISO or ISO/NSO split grants.",
      "originalText": "Once the grant editor is used on a stakeholder’s grant, Carta will notify legal administrators in two different ways if a modification is made to the stakeholder’s ISO or ISO/NSO split grants."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "4783767085171604879",
    "text": {
      "text": "In the modification workflow (grant cancellation for this example), the legal administrator will be shown an orange banner indicating that Carta’s automatic ISO 100K calculator is not running for the stakeholder and their ISO and ISO/NSO split option grants should be reviewed by the company and their legal counsel to ensure compliance under the ISO 100K limit: carta/public/11/images/7333437185394749509_jm9yJZerpZwgMCw7FnlvacSmoOzv_8RbH9Xsa3gTh5ot4kUcWoSFARjE7TbNvHgo4sFoG1MVVCc4IvT3DAK47rWfdJ0VIp6gVKFZcrOqOBck1kAZ7nd-LvVWkozqjlIdeD7fwQC5",
      "originalText": "In the modification workflow (grant cancellation for this example), the legal administrator will be shown an orange banner indicating that Carta’s automatic ISO 100K calculator is not running for the stakeholder and their ISO and ISO/NSO split option grants should be reviewed by the company and their legal counsel to ensure compliance under the ISO 100K limit:<br><img height=\"319\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7333437185394749509_jm9yJZerpZwgMCw7FnlvacSmoOzv_8RbH9Xsa3gTh5ot4kUcWoSFARjE7TbNvHgo4sFoG1MVVCc4IvT3DAK47rWfdJ0VIp6gVKFZcrOqOBck1kAZ7nd-LvVWkozqjlIdeD7fwQC5\" width=\"332\">",
