      }
    }
  }, {
    "id": "5106689380224438263",
    "text": {
      "text": "Completing a modification workflow in Carta will also trigger an email notification to all legal administrators in the company reminding them that a given stakeholder has been excluded from Carta’s automatic ISO 100K calculator - note that the subject line of the email will be the same as the large bolded text shown in the example email below “Review the ISO/NSO status for {stakeholder name}’s grants”: carta/public/11/images/6005308621235059152_tc8xLXdmafHBMwfSNt-0rr-fRz8EZDFwLNFASIgy3Qe1kuGBb0jQPa8xbSTrlZpnJm_7-ZZMn8FSe2cFToMObkBAVq1C_duKTYeSmkEfLRrRvJzny05RybfM3uz3pX459W0H2ewK",
      "originalText": "Completing a modification workflow in Carta will also trigger an email notification to all legal administrators in the company reminding them that a given stakeholder has been excluded from Carta’s automatic ISO 100K calculator - note that the subject line of the email will be the same as the large bolded text shown in the example email below “Review the ISO/NSO status for {stakeholder name}’s grants”:<br><img height=\"337\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6005308621235059152_tc8xLXdmafHBMwfSNt-0rr-fRz8EZDFwLNFASIgy3Qe1kuGBb0jQPa8xbSTrlZpnJm_7-ZZMn8FSe2cFToMObkBAVq1C_duKTYeSmkEfLRrRvJzny05RybfM3uz3pX459W0H2ewK\" width=\"358\">",
      "associatedImage": {
        "url": "carta/public/11/images/6005308621235059152_tc8xLXdmafHBMwfSNt-0rr-fRz8EZDFwLNFASIgy3Qe1kuGBb0jQPa8xbSTrlZpnJm_7-ZZMn8FSe2cFToMObkBAVq1C_duKTYeSmkEfLRrRvJzny05RybfM3uz3pX459W0H2ewK"
      }
    }
  }, {
    "id": "6017108345769774410",
    "text": {
      "text": "If a legal administrator clicks on theReview button from the email, they’ll be taken to the ISO 100K Dashboard in Carta where they can apply a filter in the stakeholder search panel to find all stakeholders that have been excluded from the automatic calculator: carta/public/11/images/2841623413060243383_2prJOOiJn4YUatH1YoXOUw128X0o_owe2ODWGzS0V1aZIMptVk-ffl-pAciKwcqh0IIIgU6mp69jabnPhnTFy1jq-fE_it53BpTJ9Ukiwr4VdlmmFXhnFGdI3MsXezd0riQZ03Jv",
      "originalText": "If a legal administrator clicks on the Review button from the email, they’ll be taken to the ISO 100K Dashboard in Carta where they can apply a filter in the stakeholder search panel to find all stakeholders that have been excluded from the automatic calculator:<br><img height=\"361\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/2841623413060243383_2prJOOiJn4YUatH1YoXOUw128X0o_owe2ODWGzS0V1aZIMptVk-ffl-pAciKwcqh0IIIgU6mp69jabnPhnTFy1jq-fE_it53BpTJ9Ukiwr4VdlmmFXhnFGdI3MsXezd0riQZ03Jv\" width=\"455\">",
