        "text": "No access: Only individual securities and personal details are visible to stakeholders with accepted securities. Company cap table information is not visible.   carta/public/11/images/833264568640222909_rtaImage    The user can access the details of their own securities  carta/public/11/images/7125475294608480498_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "No access: Only individual securities and personal details are visible to stakeholders with accepted securities. Company cap table information is not visible.&nbsp;<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/833264568640222909_rtaImage\" width=\"80%\"><br> <br> The user can access the details of their own securities<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7125475294608480498_rtaImage\" width=\"80%\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
