        "text": "Individual access: Stakeholders with view are not able to see detailed information about any other shareholder or share class level data.    Users with personal portfolios can view a detailed summary of their own holdings and their ownership percentage in your company.  carta/public/11/images/8699123670084408187_rtaImage    Users with Investment Firms can view the personal portfolio's view. In addition, the balance of the fully diluted shares aggregated as a single line item will be displayed.    carta/public/11/images/3159435156796663586_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Individual access: Stakeholders with view are not able to see detailed information about any other shareholder or share class level data.<br> <br> Users with personal portfolios can view a detailed summary of their own holdings and their ownership percentage in your company.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8699123670084408187_rtaImage\" width=\"80%\"><br> <br> Users with Investment Firms can view the personal portfolio's view. In addition, the balance of the fully diluted shares aggregated as a single line item will be displayed.<br> <br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3159435156796663586_rtaImage\" width=\"80%\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
