        "originalText": "Summary access: Summary access allows investors to see detailed information about their own holdings, but only share class level information for any other holdings. Investors can download a basic cap table report and access the company's Financing History page.<br> <br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7556113086863212071_rtaImage\" width=\"80%\"><br> <br> Under the Financing History tab, the user will be able to access the following details about each investment round.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6920374933045979147_rtaImage\" width=\"80%\"><br> <br> The user will be able to download Summary cap table reports under the Reports tab.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5419815157340331763_rtaImage\" width=\"80%\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/5419815157340331763_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Intermediate access: Intermediate access grants detailed ownership data for preferred stakeholders and share class level data for non-preferred stakeholders. Common stock and options are grouped into one line item each, at a basic level, so investors do not have the ability to view stakeholder details for these classes of stock.  NOTE: For stakeholders with only Convertibles, the stakeholder must hold an investor type security (preferred/convertible/warrant) and have an outstanding amount that contributes to the fully diluted to appear.  carta/public/11/images/2229521189456582027_rtaImage    The user will be able to download Summary cap table reports and Intermediate reports under the Reports tab.  carta/public/11/images/4899649367110165386_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Intermediate access: Intermediate access grants detailed ownership data for preferred stakeholders and share class level data for non-preferred stakeholders. Common stock and options are grouped into one line item each, at a basic level, so investors do not have the ability to view stakeholder details for these classes of stock.<br> NOTE: For stakeholders with only Convertibles, the stakeholder must hold an&nbsp;investor type security (preferred/convertible/warrant) and have an outstanding amount that contributes to the fully diluted to appear.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/2229521189456582027_rtaImage\" width=\"80%\"><br> <br> The user will be able to download Summary cap table reports and Intermediate reports under the Reports tab.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/4899649367110165386_rtaImage\" width=\"80%\"><br> &nbsp;",
