        "originalText": "Detailed access: Detailed access grants detailed ownership data for all stakeholders and securities. They can view all holdings by stakeholder and are able to access the round modeling and waterfall analyses as well as the ability download reports that include your detailed cap table.<br> NOTE: For stakeholders with only Convertibles, the stakeholder must hold an investor type security (preferred/convertible/warrant) and have an outstanding amount that contributes to the fully diluted to appear.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3709058667999028891_rtaImage\" width=\"80%\"><br> <br> Common stock and options will now be detailed.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/4537418270393462271_rtaImage\" width=\"80%\"><br> <br> The user will be able to download Summary cap table, Intermediate, Detailed, and Security ledgers by type and class reports under the Reports tab.<br> <br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6455973434429866697_rtaImage\" width=\"80%\"><br> <br> The user will be able to access details for any securities.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8296595607173425963_rtaImage\" width=\"80%\">",
