    "id": "-2480635148864441034",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "Features requiring a stakeholder’s address that’s provided and managed by the stakeholder in their portfolio.For example, the distribution of Form 1099-B in Carta. Carta leverages the address provided directly by the stakeholder in theAccount settings for their portfolio to send Form 1099-B. carta/public/11/images/6027578096042792461_Co_JAintKUhhGBwvdUHBps0QX9uZQzUychMzZIJLK1eaOUnEtS_AclUlaDY9t5g77lbfjj52VCYOnTZuCqVbwsFlkqcQeHai68-wkbgU0FyU9XjPq6_xyD1hI6B_z7mFWkGtbUK1",
        "originalText": "Features requiring a stakeholder’s address that’s provided and managed by the stakeholder in their portfolio.  For example, the distribution of Form 1099-B in Carta. Carta leverages the address provided directly by the stakeholder in the Account settings for their portfolio to send Form 1099-B.<br> <img height=\"228\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6027578096042792461_Co_JAintKUhhGBwvdUHBps0QX9uZQzUychMzZIJLK1eaOUnEtS_AclUlaDY9t5g77lbfjj52VCYOnTZuCqVbwsFlkqcQeHai68-wkbgU0FyU9XjPq6_xyD1hI6B_z7mFWkGtbUK1\" width=\"431\">  &nbsp;",
