        }
      }, {
        "text": "Features requiring a stakeholder’s address that’s provided and managed by the company in the Stakeholderledger.For example, Carta’s tax system that estimates tax withholding amounts for option exercises. Tax withholding is the legal obligation for an issuer, so the company should be on the hook for maintaining accurate information like stakeholder addresses for tax and compliance purposes. Therefore, tax withholding estimates in Carta will use the stakeholder address provided and managed by the company in the Stakeholder ledger: carta/public/11/images/3541066944138704081_Un9WoLB1acHmaq6wAkrlhVEZyQXgxZlEDFb1UR_uAxf6hR8XI9frieAYQ_S57bebRBitZp2lVZxxSW2YB_OeEqOBLUEJDiOUflRcqXG8z-HLBNm52D3TBLxRqU_FYBRije_4RbBA",
