    "id": "7449489121217398950",
    "text": {
      "text": "Stakeholders from public companies can now more easily view their share and cost basis information. Stakeholder portfolios feature two new tabs,Share lot details andTransaction details that show detailed information for an employee’s common stock and cost basis information.",
      "originalText": "Stakeholders from public companies can now more easily view their share and cost basis information. Stakeholder portfolios feature two new tabs,&nbsp;Share lot details&nbsp;and&nbsp;Transaction details&nbsp;that show detailed information for an employee’s common stock and cost basis information."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-4769609150635186265",
    "text": {
      "text": "TheShare lot details tab shows the stakeholder’s share lots. Stakeholders can view their acquisition date and cost basis for all share lots, as well as the source of the shares. For share lots linked to ISO awards or employee stock purchase plans, this view shows a qualifying date capturing the earliest date that the share lot can be sold in a qualifying disposition. The FMV at acquisition is also captured in the table to facilitate tax analysis. carta/public/11/images/4158356087968065322_7X-RJLMLxI5yITGolr0vLLJgIVhFarSQh_Shm-wYLEwQXCUQAeyHbzvPngozOouSgEye817NdItvOGKv6D7NWOnmc6qprYlv4ME59mW-xlvoIqXVRf-1nzFB4y-TLWyUBmCFurov",
      "originalText": "The Share lot details tab shows the stakeholder’s share lots. Stakeholders can view their acquisition date and cost basis for all share lots, as well as the source of the shares. For share lots linked to ISO awards or employee stock purchase plans, this view shows a qualifying date capturing the earliest date that the share lot can be sold in a qualifying disposition. The FMV at acquisition is also captured in the table to facilitate tax analysis.<br><img height=\"361.4489355137303\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/4158356087968065322_7X-RJLMLxI5yITGolr0vLLJgIVhFarSQh_Shm-wYLEwQXCUQAeyHbzvPngozOouSgEye817NdItvOGKv6D7NWOnmc6qprYlv4ME59mW-xlvoIqXVRf-1nzFB4y-TLWyUBmCFurov\" width=\"513\">",
      "associatedImage": {
        "url": "carta/public/11/images/4158356087968065322_7X-RJLMLxI5yITGolr0vLLJgIVhFarSQh_Shm-wYLEwQXCUQAeyHbzvPngozOouSgEye817NdItvOGKv6D7NWOnmc6qprYlv4ME59mW-xlvoIqXVRf-1nzFB4y-TLWyUBmCFurov"
      }
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-1125902892628531284",
    "text": {
      "text": "The second tab featuresTransaction details for any sold lots. Stakeholders can view their sold share lots and their related cost basis and acquisition dates. This view also shows the disposition type if the share lot is linked to an ISO exercise or ESPP purchase. The view captures the proceeds for each liquidated share lot. carta/public/11/images/4806536964088907352_EECx3aeCiaiDaMrhxpOf3WmDWRiqcVpHYATKMLHl0crU4xi7IVnOcWT2ekzBvSih8HSnoVwz_Dx0ps0gUDnbP2pgtRO6smqYaPw9p5xR0qa0nASHKSsqMpsWGAH9qn-ZABgoAcue",
      "originalText": "The second tab features Transaction details for any sold lots. Stakeholders can view their sold share lots and their related cost basis and acquisition dates. This view also shows the disposition type if the share lot is linked to an ISO exercise or ESPP purchase. The view captures the proceeds for each liquidated share lot.<br><img height=\"397\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/4806536964088907352_EECx3aeCiaiDaMrhxpOf3WmDWRiqcVpHYATKMLHl0crU4xi7IVnOcWT2ekzBvSih8HSnoVwz_Dx0ps0gUDnbP2pgtRO6smqYaPw9p5xR0qa0nASHKSsqMpsWGAH9qn-ZABgoAcue\" width=\"524\">",
      "associatedImage": {
        "url": "carta/public/11/images/4806536964088907352_EECx3aeCiaiDaMrhxpOf3WmDWRiqcVpHYATKMLHl0crU4xi7IVnOcWT2ekzBvSih8HSnoVwz_Dx0ps0gUDnbP2pgtRO6smqYaPw9p5xR0qa0nASHKSsqMpsWGAH9qn-ZABgoAcue"
