      "originalText": "The Portfolio email is the email address associated with the holder's portfolio which holds their accepted securities.<br><img height=\"208.00000000000003\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/4369143736515084554_TdCjupgGjxPDgIE3HxmEPwGG_wI5cIx_ibdzQeO-Gz3mDQ18YJXTN7a4CR4uctf04ATzvqS0wvZqOBKqGYb9voHtG2EMm8nbA2WNq1vUcZsR4EcDUzVupMoLBdfX9oAzJ6I0iMSw\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"624\">",
