      }
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-3511979687986627412",
    "list": {
      "item": [{
        "text": "For new stakeholders who have yet to accept a security from the issuing company, there will be a “Pending” label for individuals and “Investor Portfolio” for non-individuals (law firms, investment firms).  carta/public/11/images/4782850642104024267_IFpNbeTpCUhKcTP0drtvJLlQzjA7GJPInEWupIrdQQVs7cKK3ENMyTtsG-nkBtWMvyOgdCoo68E8MBTSAGJFDr2RzpzG09IokqoP3vyCVv5vk8rXUI_b8MLITZI91tmGf3vi1xjr",
        "originalText": "For new stakeholders who have yet to accept a security from the issuing company, there will be a “Pending” label for individuals and “Investor Portfolio” for non-individuals (law firms, investment firms).<br> <img height=\"113\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/4782850642104024267_IFpNbeTpCUhKcTP0drtvJLlQzjA7GJPInEWupIrdQQVs7cKK3ENMyTtsG-nkBtWMvyOgdCoo68E8MBTSAGJFDr2RzpzG09IokqoP3vyCVv5vk8rXUI_b8MLITZI91tmGf3vi1xjr\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"624\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/4782850642104024267_IFpNbeTpCUhKcTP0drtvJLlQzjA7GJPInEWupIrdQQVs7cKK3ENMyTtsG-nkBtWMvyOgdCoo68E8MBTSAGJFDr2RzpzG09IokqoP3vyCVv5vk8rXUI_b8MLITZI91tmGf3vi1xjr"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "This email is used by the holder to log into their Carta account to accept and view their securities.",
        "originalText": "This email is used by the holder to log into their Carta account to accept and view their securities."
      }, {
        "text": "When the holder needs to change their Portfolio email, by following these steps, the change will then be updated on the company’s All Stakeholders page.",
        "originalText": "When the holder needs to change their Portfolio email, <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/update-stakeholder-details\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">by following these steps</a>, the change will then be updated on the company’s All Stakeholders page."
      }, {
        "text": "Future securities issued from the company will need to be accepted by the account associated with the Portfolio email.",
        "originalText": "Future securities issued&nbsp; from the company will need to be accepted by the account associated with the Portfolio email."
      }]
    }
  }, {
    "id": "36676217585348224",
    "text": {
      "text": "NOTE: If securities are sent to a stakeholder with a setPortfolio email, but differentContact email, the notification will be sent to theContact email, but the task to accept the securities will be held in the Carta account associated with thePortfolio email. So users can have issues trying to accept their securities with theirContact email, instead of their previously usedPortfolio email listed. carta/public/11/images/3892118701865833964_N3JjnBF6s3UE1sCUweB2JI7GidF0nhfUcMrdiNyo3cqFGdxREtdKhVgIts9taoloVjKS_lu5dKYNih1lO-QBa_1iyGmChT0HPGVJ8LtORxANyLu8MgCCe2saHhG_dtuOUJ62Th9W",
      "originalText": "NOTE: If securities are sent to a stakeholder with a set Portfolio email, but different Contact email, the notification will be sent to the Contact email, but the task to accept the securities will be held in the Carta account associated with the Portfolio email. So users can have issues trying to accept their securities with their Contact email, instead of their previously used Portfolio email listed.<br><img height=\"148\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3892118701865833964_N3JjnBF6s3UE1sCUweB2JI7GidF0nhfUcMrdiNyo3cqFGdxREtdKhVgIts9taoloVjKS_lu5dKYNih1lO-QBa_1iyGmChT0HPGVJ8LtORxANyLu8MgCCe2saHhG_dtuOUJ62Th9W\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"624\">",
