{
  "id": "-7051590479063172191",
  "subject": {
    "id": "-7051590479063172191",
    "text": {
      "text": "Viewing your Carta 409a Valuation status"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-943248022997779479",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "Navigate to Compliance > 409A.  carta/public/11/images/6255349686647570368_WH8Rj9u7coNT5AILWcVhpikSO6rb2EajQqtwkwIDdp16KAkEycOQ0F5lT1ppkvOKvLIAycTO2lQ4YsqN9j8vfG89WiRJ-Wa8KOUhlnsWOvW3KGnvhPtSwZz-l80S_ZdS0U0wFqKo",
        "originalText": "Navigate to Compliance &gt; 409A.<br> <img height=\"126\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6255349686647570368_WH8Rj9u7coNT5AILWcVhpikSO6rb2EajQqtwkwIDdp16KAkEycOQ0F5lT1ppkvOKvLIAycTO2lQ4YsqN9j8vfG89WiRJ-Wa8KOUhlnsWOvW3KGnvhPtSwZz-l80S_ZdS0U0wFqKo\" width=\"429\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/6255349686647570368_WH8Rj9u7coNT5AILWcVhpikSO6rb2EajQqtwkwIDdp16KAkEycOQ0F5lT1ppkvOKvLIAycTO2lQ4YsqN9j8vfG89WiRJ-Wa8KOUhlnsWOvW3KGnvhPtSwZz-l80S_ZdS0U0wFqKo"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "The most recent completed valuation or current pending valuation will be listed at the top. Under the Status column, a completed valuation will have a green dot and a pending valuation will have a yellow dot.  carta/public/11/images/1560148790531781233_1q0cdnMQs_8ROx-y3-L8oQHo17FbhBnI_fqIVkt8dtrdiTfuArtTkHcFfjid5Bkf5bo_7CygyWAp8yAc6JAmN1Y_AKBsFm0uxydX4UfNblSXSp0-IQtluOzrX-EtkUfheSgV2jYj",
        "originalText": "The most recent completed valuation or current pending valuation will be listed at the top. Under the Status column, a completed valuation will have a green dot and a pending valuation will have a yellow dot.<br> <img height=\"293\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1560148790531781233_1q0cdnMQs_8ROx-y3-L8oQHo17FbhBnI_fqIVkt8dtrdiTfuArtTkHcFfjid5Bkf5bo_7CygyWAp8yAc6JAmN1Y_AKBsFm0uxydX4UfNblSXSp0-IQtluOzrX-EtkUfheSgV2jYj\" width=\"476\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/1560148790531781233_1q0cdnMQs_8ROx-y3-L8oQHo17FbhBnI_fqIVkt8dtrdiTfuArtTkHcFfjid5Bkf5bo_7CygyWAp8yAc6JAmN1Y_AKBsFm0uxydX4UfNblSXSp0-IQtluOzrX-EtkUfheSgV2jYj"
        }
      }]
    }
  }, {
    "id": "5319848118838647191",
    "text": {
      "text": "Below are different statuses that a report can be in and a description of what to expect in each:",
      "originalText": "Below are different statuses that a report can be in and a description of what to expect in each:<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-6191646396800886940",
    "list": {
      "item": [{
        "text": "Data validation: The 409A Team has received the submission and a Valuation Specialist is reviewing the information for accuracy. The review process is about two business days from 409A request submission.",
        "originalText": "Data validation: The 409A Team has received the submission and a Valuation Specialist is reviewing the information for accuracy. The review process is about two business days from 409A request submission.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Valuation on hold: The admin will receive an email from the Carta Valuations Team indicating a problem or inconsistency from the information provided on the 409A request form. The issues will need to be resolved before moving forward in the valuation process.",
        "originalText": "Valuation on hold: The admin will receive an email from the Carta Valuations Team indicating a problem or inconsistency from the information provided on the 409A request form. The issues will need to be resolved before moving forward in the valuation process.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "More information needed: The admin will receive an email from the Carta Valuations Team with questions or clarifications needed to proceed with the valuation. Admins should respond to this in a timely manner to ensure the valuation stays on track.",
        "originalText": "More information needed: The admin will receive an email from the Carta Valuations Team with questions or clarifications needed to proceed with the valuation. Admins should respond to this in a timely manner to ensure the valuation stays on track.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Awaiting assignment: The valuation is in the process of being assigned to an analyst. This will typically take about four business days, depending on the complexity of the Valuation and the team’s request volume.",
        "originalText": "Awaiting assignment: The valuation is in the process of being assigned to an analyst. This will typically take about four business days, depending on the complexity of the Valuation and the team’s request volume.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Analyst reviewing: A dedicated analyst is working on the Valuation. The typical time until delivery is three to seven business days, depending on the size and complexity of the company.",
        "originalText": "Analyst reviewing: A dedicated analyst is working on the Valuation. The typical time until delivery is three to seven business days, depending on the size and complexity of the company.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Draft delivered: A draft report has been delivered. The point of contact on the Valuation should have received an email when the draft was delivered. The draft can be viewed by going to Compliance > 409A. Contact 409A@carta.com with any questions and concerns about the valuation.",
        "originalText": "Draft delivered: A draft report has been delivered. The point of contact on the Valuation should have received an email when the draft was delivered. The draft can be viewed by going to Compliance &gt; 409A. Contact <a href=\"mailto:409a@carta.com\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">409A@carta.com</a> with any questions and concerns about the valuation.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Complete: The report has been accepted. The FMV and report have been added to the option ledger automatically and the Company can begin granting options and allowing exercises.",
        "originalText": "Complete: The report has been accepted. The FMV and report have been added to the option ledger automatically and the Company can begin granting options and allowing exercises."
      }]
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-2673207420115827177",
    "text": {
      "text": "If there are any questions or concerns about the valuation report, contact the Carta Valuation team’s post-delivery support team at 409A@carta.com to schedule a call to discuss the Valuation and make any revisions as needed.",
      "originalText": "If there are any questions or concerns about the valuation report, contact the Carta Valuation team’s post-delivery support team at <a href=\"mailto:409A@carta.com\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">409A@carta.com</a> to schedule a call to discuss the Valuation and make any revisions as needed."
    }
  }]
}

