    "text": {
      "text": "Connecting your QuickBooks account"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-6564149928916855481",
    "text": {
      "text": "Connecting the company financials can assist in completing the 409A valuation request quicker. If you are not the owner of the QuickBooks account that you wish to connect, you will need to ask the owner of the QuickBooks account to add you to their account.",
      "originalText": "Connecting the company financials can assist in completing the 409A valuation request quicker. If you are not the owner of the QuickBooks account that you wish to connect, you will need to ask the owner of the QuickBooks account to add you to their account.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-7950433404837806863",
    "text": {
      "text": "NOTE: Carta will fetch last three months of data everyday except Sunday at 12:00 AM PST. On Sunday, Carta will fetch the last twelve months of data at 12:00 AM PST.",
      "originalText": "NOTE: Carta will fetch last three months of data everyday except Sunday at 12:00 AM PST.<br>On Sunday, Carta will fetch the last twelve months of data at 12:00 AM PST.<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "3574945767545895095",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "To connect your QuickBooks account to Carta, navigate to Company > Settings > Financials and HR.  carta/public/11/images/1364008141525101220_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "To connect your QuickBooks account to Carta, navigate to Company &gt; Settings &gt; Financials and HR.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1364008141525101220_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/1364008141525101220_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click Connect and you will be prompted to sign into your QuickBooks account.  https://s3.amazonaws.com/helpscout.net/docs/assets/558b2474e4b01a224b42e68e/images/590a69c12c7d3a057f88c6f1/file-cehHT4bQ7k.png",
        "originalText": "Click Connect and you will be prompted to sign into your QuickBooks account.<br> <img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/helpscout.net/docs/assets/558b2474e4b01a224b42e68e/images/590a69c12c7d3a057f88c6f1/file-cehHT4bQ7k.png\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/helpscout.net/docs/assets/558b2474e4b01a224b42e68e/images/590a69c12c7d3a057f88c6f1/file-cehHT4bQ7k.png"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Once you have connected to QuickBooks, you can use these to complete a 409A valuation request quicker.",
        "originalText": "Once you have connected to QuickBooks, you can use these to complete a 409A valuation request quicker."
      }]
    }
