      "originalText": "To export the company's Rule 701 analysis, navigate to Capitalization &gt; Reporting.<br><img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7604569635467731980_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 813px;height: 190px;\"><br><br>The Rule 701 analysis report can be found under the Standard reports&nbsp;section.<br><img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5982665643167162379_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 804px;height: 369px;\"><br>&nbsp;",
