        "text": "Row 13 (Common shares issued under Rule 701): Includes common stock issued under Rule 701 with the following criteria:(a) RSAs that were both (i) issued during the report period and (ii) remain outstanding at the end of the report period;(b) Exercise of option grants or warrants that were both (i) granted and (ii) exercised within the report period;(c) Settlement of RSUs that were both (i) granted and (ii) settled within the report period. This method allows us to (1) make the awards whole for purposes of Test 1 and (2) exclude shares issued under Rule 701 from the aggregate values of outstanding stock for Tests 2 and 3. Carta only includes the stock that was originally issued under Rule 701. Transferred and balance stock certificates are excluded.",
        "originalText": "Row 13 (Common shares issued under Rule 701): &nbsp;Includes common stock issued under Rule 701 with the following criteria:  (a) RSAs that were both (i) issued during the report period and (ii) remain outstanding at the end of the report period;&nbsp; (b) Exercise of option grants or warrants that were both (i) granted and (ii) exercised within the report period; (c) Settlement of RSUs that were both (i) granted and (ii) settled within the report period.<br> &nbsp;  This method allows us to (1) make the awards whole for purposes of Test 1 and (2) exclude shares issued under Rule 701 from the aggregate values of outstanding stock for Tests 2 and 3.&nbsp; Carta only includes the stock that was originally issued under Rule 701. Transferred and balance stock certificates are excluded.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Repeat for Row 14 - 16 with preferred shares.",
        "originalText": "Repeat for Row 14 - 16 with&nbsp;preferred shares.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Row 19 - 26 represents the issued and outstanding stock as converted, as of the report end date. We exclude the shares issued under Rule 701 during the report period for purposes of Tests 2 and 3, pursuant to Rule 701(d)(3)(iii).",
        "originalText": "Row&nbsp;19 - 26 represents the issued and outstanding stock as converted, as of the report end date. &nbsp;We exclude the shares issued under Rule 701 during the report period for purposes of Tests 2 and 3, pursuant to Rule 701(d)(3)(iii).<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Row 24 (Options issued): Outstanding stock as of report end date = (Issued and Outstanding as of the report end date) - (securities issued under Rule 701)",
        "originalText": "Row 24 (Options issued):&nbsp;Outstanding stock as of report end date = (Issued and Outstanding as of the report end date) - (securities issued under Rule 701)<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Row 29 (Aggregate dollar value of Rule 701 shares < $1M): Test 1= Aggregate dollar value of Rule 701 shares = the sum of the exercise price of outstanding options plus the aggregate dollar amount of sales made in reliance of Rule 701 during the report (lookback) period. For options, Carta defines the “sales price” as the aggregate exercise price to be paid for such options as of the grant date. Canceled, terminated and expired grants are not included in Carta's calculation.",
        "originalText": "Row 29 (Aggregate dollar value of Rule 701 shares &lt; $1M): Test 1&nbsp;= Aggregate dollar value of Rule 701 shares = the sum of the exercise price of outstanding options plus the aggregate dollar amount of sales made in reliance of Rule 701 during the report (lookback) period. &nbsp;For options, Carta defines the “sales price” as the aggregate exercise price to be paid for such options as of the grant date. &nbsp;Canceled, terminated and expired grants are not included in Carta's calculation.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
