        "originalText": "Row 30&nbsp;(Aggregate Rule 701 shares &lt; 15% of outstanding shares):&nbsp;Test 2 = Aggregate Rule 701 shares issued during the report period is less than 15% of issued and outstanding shares (as converted, excluding shares issued under Rule 701) per Rule 701(d)(3)(iii).<br> &nbsp;"
