{
  "id": "3709075471432377854",
  "subject": {
    "id": "3709075471432377854",
    "text": {
      "text": "How to Amend the Option Plan Size"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "6127750717283636804",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "If you would like to amend an active option/equity plan to increase or decrease the number of shares in the pool, navigate to Securities > Equity Awards.   carta/public/11/images/85763395164699454_GA8CEJkhrJky8UZQ7eDDdPB1CLBpPci925M_gIY6lPBlLNOM9vDmrGxF-BKFepMgJeMR0_AE6weFhDAdneO2Zp2LtZFG6kathVuApv-yFdfvjGZO5xCEXkv2UxiA6sxU6Rb7f_hb    Alternately, navigate to Capitalization > Equity plans, then skip to Step 3.  carta/public/11/images/7712395116470248894_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "If you would like to amend an active option/equity plan to increase or decrease the number of shares in the pool, navigate to Securities &gt; Equity Awards.&nbsp;<br> <img height=\"202\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/85763395164699454_GA8CEJkhrJky8UZQ7eDDdPB1CLBpPci925M_gIY6lPBlLNOM9vDmrGxF-BKFepMgJeMR0_AE6weFhDAdneO2Zp2LtZFG6kathVuApv-yFdfvjGZO5xCEXkv2UxiA6sxU6Rb7f_hb\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"432\"><br> <br> Alternately, navigate to Capitalization &gt; Equity plans, then skip to Step 3.<br> <img alt=\"image.png\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7712395116470248894_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 227px;height: 212px;\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/7712395116470248894_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "In the upper right, click the V dropdown and select Manage equity plans.  carta/public/11/images/1061282970362824566_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "In the upper right, click the V&nbsp;dropdown and select Manage&nbsp;equity plans.<br> <img alt=\"image.png\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1061282970362824566_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 453px;height: 207px;\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/1061282970362824566_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click the V dropdown and select Amend plan size next to the option plan that will be amended.  carta/public/11/images/6752029100920136871_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Click the&nbsp;V&nbsp;dropdown and select&nbsp;Amend plan size next to the option plan that will be amended.<br> <img alt=\"Screenshot 2021-02-22 162816.png\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6752029100920136871_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 495px;height: 112px;\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/6752029100920136871_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click Add new amendment button. If an existing amendment needs to be corrected, click Edit to the right of the appropriate amendment.  carta/public/11/images/974498000847934458_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Click Add new amendment button. If an existing amendment needs to be corrected, click Edit to the right of the appropriate amendment.<br> <img alt=\"image.png\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/974498000847934458_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 548px;height: 272px;\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/974498000847934458_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Add the amendment information (e.g. the new plan size, board approval date) and click Next: review this amendment.  carta/public/11/images/4811533140143233072_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Add the amendment information (e.g. the new plan size, board approval date) and click Next: review this amendment.<br> <img alt=\"image.png\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/4811533140143233072_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 459px;height: 637px;\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/4811533140143233072_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Review the amendment details and click Save amendment. carta/public/11/images/1654516014849800447_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Review the amendment details and click Save amendment.<img alt=\"image.png\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1654516014849800447_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 467px;height: 203px;\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/1654516014849800447_rtaImage"
        }
      }]
    }
  }]
}

{
