        "originalText": "SAFEs must be issued out of a SAFEs Convertibles term set.<br> If there is an existing SAFEs term set to be used, skip to step 3.<br> &nbsp;  If not, click Manage convertible terms and select Create convertible terms.<br> <img height=\"178\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/4262836764017923123_dGIZ6l8v2i3rwPkWgecdrfOolvbVbarnuHVy2LkGZRvi-1gsZ2PuapLm-D5_aQZRedDaaE2Wg9qDtNzxiDMQc0spF6CpeUmV9hSYT9GXrxDJJ-EhtVm898M_NfL1CnNzQP823jnb\" width=\"382\"><br> &nbsp; Select SAFE for Convertible type. <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/create-note-block\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Review the term set creation steps here</a>.<br> <img height=\"159\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/9113549820639136619_QX84H-buQ5DpzcJ6K_SgB2tIdr9kXvMlwbWcAedhTXmiQtuFQWe1toZ9nH3SeW-8m8rAKWpeP2ePEZjr4I-ogQY4nxixLfanNaBuyOTNUpH2Fw1qr-RWxkpM_YfPfWSk24gLJURq\" width=\"377\"><br> &nbsp;  ",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/9113549820639136619_QX84H-buQ5DpzcJ6K_SgB2tIdr9kXvMlwbWcAedhTXmiQtuFQWe1toZ9nH3SeW-8m8rAKWpeP2ePEZjr4I-ogQY4nxixLfanNaBuyOTNUpH2Fw1qr-RWxkpM_YfPfWSk24gLJURq"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click Draft convertibles.  carta/public/11/images/5112098326624439622_Hw8ldaH8fm__zn5vy2gvhVIQocNbULkoanqNfXrECoNDK6wHPtyFi4PEj1qDEpaNb7KU58V55tPI8UW5g_b2nuf_uWVH4akvL4j-gzuqXzTZZLL4NBtC8lVj6S4ig_He-KsWEP3k",
        "originalText": "Click Draft convertibles.<br> <img height=\"213\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5112098326624439622_Hw8ldaH8fm__zn5vy2gvhVIQocNbULkoanqNfXrECoNDK6wHPtyFi4PEj1qDEpaNb7KU58V55tPI8UW5g_b2nuf_uWVH4akvL4j-gzuqXzTZZLL4NBtC8lVj6S4ig_He-KsWEP3k\" width=\"428\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/5112098326624439622_Hw8ldaH8fm__zn5vy2gvhVIQocNbULkoanqNfXrECoNDK6wHPtyFi4PEj1qDEpaNb7KU58V55tPI8UW5g_b2nuf_uWVH4akvL4j-gzuqXzTZZLL4NBtC8lVj6S4ig_He-KsWEP3k"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "From the upper right, click the name of the SAFEs term set to issue the drafts from that set.  carta/public/11/images/7531982289648785246_Lxhjh4t0O_sSXZk8cUFZc7xbP_6MAA-GssIT0_3v6cRdDQUXkuuHjugw0ox0akzoCu4Z-3z4iLe12A6o-VldUQv_v_JLhF1aLE5Mr8JYFxBp95WGqL3CXDy3eJF3m2ygUghYt0_P",
        "originalText": "From the upper right, click the name of the SAFEs term set to issue the drafts from that set.<br> <img height=\"136\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7531982289648785246_Lxhjh4t0O_sSXZk8cUFZc7xbP_6MAA-GssIT0_3v6cRdDQUXkuuHjugw0ox0akzoCu4Z-3z4iLe12A6o-VldUQv_v_JLhF1aLE5Mr8JYFxBp95WGqL3CXDy3eJF3m2ygUghYt0_P\" width=\"476\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/7531982289648785246_Lxhjh4t0O_sSXZk8cUFZc7xbP_6MAA-GssIT0_3v6cRdDQUXkuuHjugw0ox0akzoCu4Z-3z4iLe12A6o-VldUQv_v_JLhF1aLE5Mr8JYFxBp95WGqL3CXDy3eJF3m2ygUghYt0_P"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click Add convertible notes to create a convertible draft. Drafts can be added individually or in bulk using a spreadsheet template.  carta/public/11/images/4266463953110148994_2PkI1-TnlVaP-oDIGm_NfoByu5uGCaq1Ev4mRBX9ScoRrnmnCF_dK7hBAm47hU2ZrNQQVkHbtouhrhfgJpYQoaxDdiYEcGoRyvEWshN1smBaGPmPKl_w00hEb6kJlL9iTVLeaCWm",
        "originalText": "Click Add convertible notes to create a convertible draft. Drafts can be added individually or in bulk using a spreadsheet template.<br> <img height=\"101\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/4266463953110148994_2PkI1-TnlVaP-oDIGm_NfoByu5uGCaq1Ev4mRBX9ScoRrnmnCF_dK7hBAm47hU2ZrNQQVkHbtouhrhfgJpYQoaxDdiYEcGoRyvEWshN1smBaGPmPKl_w00hEb6kJlL9iTVLeaCWm\" width=\"473\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/4266463953110148994_2PkI1-TnlVaP-oDIGm_NfoByu5uGCaq1Ev4mRBX9ScoRrnmnCF_dK7hBAm47hU2ZrNQQVkHbtouhrhfgJpYQoaxDdiYEcGoRyvEWshN1smBaGPmPKl_w00hEb6kJlL9iTVLeaCWm"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "After importing a template or adding a convertible, click on the individual row SAFE draft to edit the details on the right-hand side. Each change is saved automatically.  carta/public/11/images/3905077907388234092_IHCx0sPU7zozJQRj8lY0AbXDDVHvlgZNIhbGHAujMc0Tu38P36YC0a7y03pjLaoK-hu4fUa7zcs8xujf_CDWx02azDiRVha00WJPzBuEEpsy3Xx2v3Ivu7h0OJhsDHdT2qt54DM9",
        "originalText": "After importing a template or adding a convertible, click on the individual row SAFE draft to edit the details on the right-hand side. Each change is saved automatically.<br> <img height=\"261\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3905077907388234092_IHCx0sPU7zozJQRj8lY0AbXDDVHvlgZNIhbGHAujMc0Tu38P36YC0a7y03pjLaoK-hu4fUa7zcs8xujf_CDWx02azDiRVha00WJPzBuEEpsy3Xx2v3Ivu7h0OJhsDHdT2qt54DM9\" width=\"479\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/3905077907388234092_IHCx0sPU7zozJQRj8lY0AbXDDVHvlgZNIhbGHAujMc0Tu38P36YC0a7y03pjLaoK-hu4fUa7zcs8xujf_CDWx02azDiRVha00WJPzBuEEpsy3Xx2v3Ivu7h0OJhsDHdT2qt54DM9"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Once the SAFE drafts are ready for issuance, check off the box (of one draft or the header box to select all), and click Send.  carta/public/11/images/4315655591627023708_TGu5XmMIHFiYLiJoVkjApkiIDpMArt2XKVic5Wxw_3T5GXlDFO13qyv7vubkPlI8LA1JhCti143lxmXZF6mbnohuuh_DUVKF6CzG7iOIatsuhsE0wCfB2-WhPI4fYP7giY8g0SsR",
        "originalText": "Once the SAFE drafts are ready for issuance, check off the box (of one draft or the header box to select all), and click Send.<br> <img height=\"103\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/4315655591627023708_TGu5XmMIHFiYLiJoVkjApkiIDpMArt2XKVic5Wxw_3T5GXlDFO13qyv7vubkPlI8LA1JhCti143lxmXZF6mbnohuuh_DUVKF6CzG7iOIatsuhsE0wCfB2-WhPI4fYP7giY8g0SsR\" width=\"484\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
