        }
      }, {
        "text": "Review the details, then click Send these convertibles.  carta/public/11/images/7460120399796703748_qwFMZpuvrwu40QaNZVmt98JJSLzegvudsNwW3zwthpT1K8-nqJ6L0rb9BHtM9hFJoVDiBL25QAzgBrlncwYzvYn9cEmrX2Wiidr4gsCco3dAqDwP0RbsUEsG53JMYr3pwjGXyRWh",
