{
  "id": "-3234328390716002171",
  "subject": {
    "id": "-3234328390716002171",
    "text": {
      "text": "How to request a 2FA reset"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-1984027052409465360",
    "text": {
      "text": "If you have lost access to your two factor authentication (2FA) device or are facing difficulties receiving the 2FA code, you can still use your backup codes to log in.  If you do not have your backup codes, read the instructions below to raise a 2FA reset request with Carta Support team.",
      "originalText": "If you have lost access to your two factor authentication (2FA) device or are facing difficulties receiving the 2FA code, you can still use your backup codes to log in.<br><br>If you do not have your backup codes, read the instructions below to raise a 2FA reset request with Carta Support team."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "8712279905289893600",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "Navigate to carta.com/accounts/login and log in using your credentials.  carta/public/11/images/957422959422298820_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Navigate to <a href=\"http://carta.com/accounts/login\" target=\"_blank\">carta.com/accounts/login</a> and log in using your credentials.<br> <img alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-02-19 at 13.35.38.png\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/957422959422298820_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 697.986px;height: 705px;\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/957422959422298820_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click Recovery options from the Authentication Code screen.  carta/public/11/images/1447296292330981818_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Click Recovery options from the Authentication Code screen.<br> <img alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-02-19 at 13.36.08.png\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1447296292330981818_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 702.969px;height: 680px;\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/1447296292330981818_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "If you have your backup codes, enter one of them on the following screen. If you do not, click Request 2FA reset to raise a request with Carta Support to have them approve of disabling 2FA on your account.  carta/public/11/images/3566033608810944127_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "If you have your backup codes, enter one of them on the following screen. If you do not, click Request 2FA reset to raise a request with Carta Support to have them approve of disabling 2FA on your account.<br> <img alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-02-19 at 13.36.35.png\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3566033608810944127_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 699.983px;height: 615.99px;\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/3566033608810944127_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Fill out the request form with the required information.    Note: Temporarily, please drag and drop the image file of your ID on the attachment button or the form will refresh.  carta/public/11/images/3013520386342574738_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Fill out the request form with the required information.<br> <br> Note: Temporarily, please drag and drop the image file of your ID on the attachment button or the form will refresh.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3013520386342574738_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/3013520386342574738_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Check your email and click Complete reset request to confirm the request.  carta/public/11/images/9141193297197289447_L8Pbj-i5p5j2FLWHwbjRpfaO9e0uCDl2NhJuPEektppW7dsBNQnCfqL4LuNFu11nAvYKKAt0MyYMOmkOBw09julExq_Q3yUbw-_eSmLMlpiIWClE9iPyjUF0h6FYsiilcrEq_5aq",
        "originalText": "Check your email and click Complete reset request to confirm the request.<br> <img height=\"388\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/9141193297197289447_L8Pbj-i5p5j2FLWHwbjRpfaO9e0uCDl2NhJuPEektppW7dsBNQnCfqL4LuNFu11nAvYKKAt0MyYMOmkOBw09julExq_Q3yUbw-_eSmLMlpiIWClE9iPyjUF0h6FYsiilcrEq_5aq\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;width: 703.976px;height: 696.997px;\" width=\"390\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/9141193297197289447_L8Pbj-i5p5j2FLWHwbjRpfaO9e0uCDl2NhJuPEektppW7dsBNQnCfqL4LuNFu11nAvYKKAt0MyYMOmkOBw09julExq_Q3yUbw-_eSmLMlpiIWClE9iPyjUF0h6FYsiilcrEq_5aq"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "You are all set! Our team will review the information provided and compare with the data that we have on file. You will be contacted within 24 business hours with next steps.",
        "originalText": "You are all set!&nbsp;Our team will review the information provided and compare with the data that we have on file. You will be contacted within 24 business hours with next steps."
      }]
    }
  }]
