{
  "id": "-2061710687027213138",
  "subject": {
    "id": "-2061710687027213138",
    "text": {
      "text": "Tender Offer FAQ"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "5265588710415925307",
    "text": {
      "text": "Review these frequently asked questions about Tender Offers facilitated on Carta.",
      "originalText": "Review these frequently asked questions about <a href=\"https://carta.com/private-companies/liquidity/\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Tender Offers facilitated on Carta</u></a>."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-6794407376508745751",
    "text": {
      "text": "What type of transactions can I execute through the Carta tender offer feature? Company Buyback and Secondary.",
      "originalText": "What type of transactions can I execute through the Carta <a href=\"https://blog.carta.com/tender-offer-faq/\" target=\"_blank\">tender offer</a> feature?<br>Company Buyback and Secondary."
    },
    "signals": [{
      "key": "FontBolded",
      "valueB": true
    }]
  }, {
    "id": "-8461084993247891630",
    "text": {
      "text": "How do I set up a tender offer in Carta? Request a demo and pricing with our Relationship Management team. Once a contract is signed, you will be assigned a Project Manager who will work with you to setup and launch the offer.",
      "originalText": "How do I set up a tender offer in Carta?<br>Request a demo and pricing with our Relationship Management team. Once a contract is signed, you will be assigned a Project Manager who will work with you to setup and launch the offer."
    },
    "signals": [{
      "key": "FontBolded",
      "valueB": true
    }]
  }, {
    "id": "-1478176276864176388",
    "text": {
      "text": "How much lead time do we need to set up the tender offer in Carta? Final seller table in Carta required format, offer to purchase, letter of transmittal, and disclosure documents should be provided to Cart at least two weeks prior to the first order date.",
      "originalText": "How much lead time do we need to set up the tender offer in Carta?<br>Final seller table in Carta required format, offer to purchase, letter of transmittal, and disclosure documents should be provided to Cart at least two weeks prior to the first order date."
    },
    "signals": [{
      "key": "FontBolded",
      "valueB": true
    }]
  }, {
    "id": "-1482961060387279168",
    "text": {
      "text": "What does the participant experience look like? Review this article for more information.",
      "originalText": "What does the participant experience look like?<br><a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/participate-tender-offer\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Review this article for more information</u></a>."
    },
    "signals": [{
      "key": "FontBolded",
      "valueB": true
    }]
  }, {
    "id": "3003351421322268560",
    "text": {
      "text": "Can participants execute a cashless exercise? Yes, our tender offer feature is designed for cashless exercise. Once the transaction is settled, we will automatically update the cap table with the exercise and cancellation of the stock certificate.",
      "originalText": "Can participants execute a cashless exercise?<br>Yes, our tender offer feature is designed for cashless exercise. Once the transaction is settled, we will automatically update the cap table with the exercise and cancellation of the stock certificate."
    },
    "signals": [{
      "key": "FontBolded",
      "valueB": true
    }]
  }, {
    "id": "2248155482367626744",
    "text": {
      "text": "How does it work if we don’t allow cashless exercise? Participants will exercise outside of the tender offer via ACH on Carta or manually with company admin. Once the certificate is created, we will add it to the tender offer so the employee can place their order.",
      "originalText": "How does it work if we don’t allow cashless exercise?<br>Participants will exercise outside of the tender offer via ACH on Carta or manually with company admin. Once the certificate is created, we will add it to the tender offer so the employee can place their order."
    },
    "signals": [{
      "key": "FontBolded",
      "valueB": true
    }]
  }, {
    "id": "-6212596879708832416",
    "text": {
      "text": "How many shares are eligible to sell during the Tender Offer? You can find the number of eligible shares to sell in theTransaction overview. Note that this number (see screenshot) in theTransaction Overview page is the total number of shares that you are eligible to sell across all your holdings. carta/public/11/images/5919393131023195261_KX3JTP50nq_xZd2ZamFmu5A8g6vEuI96V4m_-Tpe5KZSi-A1vDlhGNzxxNvujkqr5sbfTjj94tZDHWtg_WvpklWrYHKOQvEbmu5qwMJWS5-XAL5S7Hj9LjMVex9NqcQnDRhIVglj",
      "originalText": "How many shares are eligible to sell during the Tender Offer?<br>You can find the number of eligible shares to sell in the Transaction overview. Note that this number (see screenshot) in the Transaction Overview page is the total number of shares that you are eligible to sell across all your holdings.<br><img height=\"260\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5919393131023195261_KX3JTP50nq_xZd2ZamFmu5A8g6vEuI96V4m_-Tpe5KZSi-A1vDlhGNzxxNvujkqr5sbfTjj94tZDHWtg_WvpklWrYHKOQvEbmu5qwMJWS5-XAL5S7Hj9LjMVex9NqcQnDRhIVglj\" width=\"526\">",
      "associatedImage": {
        "url": "carta/public/11/images/5919393131023195261_KX3JTP50nq_xZd2ZamFmu5A8g6vEuI96V4m_-Tpe5KZSi-A1vDlhGNzxxNvujkqr5sbfTjj94tZDHWtg_WvpklWrYHKOQvEbmu5qwMJWS5-XAL5S7Hj9LjMVex9NqcQnDRhIVglj"
      }
    },
    "signals": [{
      "key": "FontBolded",
      "valueB": true
    }]
  }, {
    "id": "7243727723114301118",
    "text": {
      "text": "Each eligible option grant or certificate is allowed to sell up to the max eligible total (the cap), unless the option grant or the certificate has vested shares less than the cap. In this case, you can sell up to total shares vested per the option grant or certificate. However, you will not be able to request to sell more shares than the cap across your holdings.  For example, the max eligible total (the cap) here is 3000 shares. CS-44 is allowed to sell up to the cap 3000 shares, and ES-236 is also allowed to sell up to the cap 3000 shares. But the total shares requested to be sold cannot exceed 3000 shares. carta/public/11/images/6715742228562027004_I4OYqAS5x_qZGIu-R9AOfeYSBn45H--dP2u8vHuXP6tsWiohzGfOtt-8jg72PboFtqvoal7mzDAxGRTW8c_4OjIZdIfHTHO3lg_vapUJnk3zVNaQ6aGwFCrMEgzQCJB6RULqt_EJ  If the total shares requested to sell exceed the max eligible total (the cap), you will be prompted with an error to prevent you from moving forward. carta/public/11/images/1030308294520191419_ljQY84MiP8Q5ufeHY8hol6aexSYxDFnq5cBX1qUGFrsxH0OCwSngRjVcg0Vi61BvOkwZz90ul2_OWgxYKyLRU1fSG4dz_nG1nmwDpEokClMFxSSTJdxmjnJ5kGfv6-ThgDcds3Hf",
      "originalText": "Each eligible option grant or certificate is allowed to sell up to the max eligible total (the cap), unless the option grant or the certificate has vested shares less than the cap. In this case, you can sell up to total shares vested per the option grant or certificate. However, you will not be able to request to sell more shares than the cap across your holdings.<br><br>For example, the max eligible total (the cap) here is 3000 shares. CS-44 is allowed to sell up to the cap 3000 shares, and ES-236 is also allowed to sell up to the cap 3000 shares. But the total shares requested to be sold cannot exceed 3000 shares.<br><img height=\"289\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6715742228562027004_I4OYqAS5x_qZGIu-R9AOfeYSBn45H--dP2u8vHuXP6tsWiohzGfOtt-8jg72PboFtqvoal7mzDAxGRTW8c_4OjIZdIfHTHO3lg_vapUJnk3zVNaQ6aGwFCrMEgzQCJB6RULqt_EJ\" width=\"524\"><br><br>If the total shares requested to sell exceed the max eligible total (the cap), you will be prompted with an error to prevent you from moving forward.<br><img height=\"307\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1030308294520191419_ljQY84MiP8Q5ufeHY8hol6aexSYxDFnq5cBX1qUGFrsxH0OCwSngRjVcg0Vi61BvOkwZz90ul2_OWgxYKyLRU1fSG4dz_nG1nmwDpEokClMFxSSTJdxmjnJ5kGfv6-ThgDcds3Hf\" width=\"524\">",
      "associatedImage": {
        "url": "carta/public/11/images/1030308294520191419_ljQY84MiP8Q5ufeHY8hol6aexSYxDFnq5cBX1qUGFrsxH0OCwSngRjVcg0Vi61BvOkwZz90ul2_OWgxYKyLRU1fSG4dz_nG1nmwDpEokClMFxSSTJdxmjnJ5kGfv6-ThgDcds3Hf"
      }
    }
  }, {
    "id": "1974431594786079507",
    "text": {
      "text": "How many shares have I vested as ofToday and as ofRecord Date? This number of shares showing underVested in theTransaction overview page is the number of shares vested as ofToday (the day when you are looking at the platform), not the cutoff date (Record date) of the vested shares for counting your eligibility.  For example, if your company allows sellers to sell 10% of vested shares as of Jan 1, 2021, this number shows shares vested as of today, not as of Jan 1, 2021. carta/public/11/images/5221147803277997491_jSYCzGAQLr06MFBoGSuXByXwPm8_nQRAPyUpVDkm_HTl_c1RCDq0ysDNN_9-rdxxVn23aX0CJZrdPepXuAxPLweRKh2HxzGXg7ny_3A0rPQqbhhDbe8JZVuyQmeLT0glfOpd-43m  For shares vested as of theRecord Date, you would need to click into theVesting schedule tab of the security to see how many shares you have vested as of theRecord Date. Reach out to your company in regards to what theRecord Date is. carta/public/11/images/8754413432949569253_kwnVeiwDcrBulC8U28hvXw-TVbfoTeFKOvA_99sccnwQ-VRE-1Y8STL9WxTHmjfFoLvQUjoTiCx4t6STvjgvlzUCeOALCiEg5n9-GOEqu1I3Wp_u2W6TX80Okn9YnyLvcUcNm8Uk",
      "originalText": "How many shares have I vested as of Today and as of Record Date?<br>This number of shares showing under Vested in the Transaction overview page is the number of shares vested as of Today (the day when you are looking at the platform), not the cutoff date (Record date) of the vested shares for counting your eligibility.<br><br>For example, if your company allows sellers to sell 10% of vested shares as of Jan 1, 2021, this number shows shares vested as of today, not as of Jan 1, 2021.<br><img height=\"259\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5221147803277997491_jSYCzGAQLr06MFBoGSuXByXwPm8_nQRAPyUpVDkm_HTl_c1RCDq0ysDNN_9-rdxxVn23aX0CJZrdPepXuAxPLweRKh2HxzGXg7ny_3A0rPQqbhhDbe8JZVuyQmeLT0glfOpd-43m\" width=\"523\"><br><br>For shares vested as of the Record Date, you would need to click into the Vesting schedule tab of the security to see how many shares you have vested as of the Record Date. <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/contacting-the-issuer\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Reach out to your company</a> in regards to what the Record Date is.<br><img height=\"540\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8754413432949569253_kwnVeiwDcrBulC8U28hvXw-TVbfoTeFKOvA_99sccnwQ-VRE-1Y8STL9WxTHmjfFoLvQUjoTiCx4t6STvjgvlzUCeOALCiEg5n9-GOEqu1I3Wp_u2W6TX80Okn9YnyLvcUcNm8Uk\" width=\"530\">",
      "associatedImage": {
