    "signals": [{
      "key": "FontBolded",
      "valueB": true
    }]
  }, {
    "id": "6514646411122140755",
    "text": {
      "text": "What is the time zone of the times displayed on the tender workflow? All times displayed in the tender offer workflow are Pacific Standard Time (PST), UTC -8 regardless of where you are located. UTC -7 during daylight savings time (PDT). carta/public/11/images/5321497865002431636_nGOQHPGKY7ErEL-C-ouIA3IR42eFB09paSVts0VlqLr_fNV7Nog_RJesd3ylkQW5kvPtSV_pj7ykZOQ-AmThWI6NuTFjjDEbzsPm7g9iVJYntrdDCZ8EPgdzqNNQfGcwgkjNe76c",
      "originalText": "What is the time zone of the times displayed on the tender workflow?<br>All times displayed in the tender offer workflow are Pacific Standard Time (PST), UTC -8 regardless of where you are located.<br>UTC -7 during daylight savings time (PDT).<br><img height=\"267\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5321497865002431636_nGOQHPGKY7ErEL-C-ouIA3IR42eFB09paSVts0VlqLr_fNV7Nog_RJesd3ylkQW5kvPtSV_pj7ykZOQ-AmThWI6NuTFjjDEbzsPm7g9iVJYntrdDCZ8EPgdzqNNQfGcwgkjNe76c\" width=\"526\">",
