      "originalText": "How do I edit the Social Security Number or the Foreign tax ID on my tax form in the tender offer workflow?<br>The Social Security Number or the Foreign tax ID in the Tax documentation step is not editable on this page.<br><img height=\"68\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8305906641881053807_l8IrNv1lFje-7mEcbYJVxqk_pGyMd_cVCm8_k74VUG1ZCEpoluMLjuk2BRNNRdXBiaOeAVRBO58tpyIEAld56J1gnjdtD7rmknUYqss1ZG9NXvLEjkuc0DziaKjKPBCxfbHZ57tz\" width=\"527\"><br><img height=\"409\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/835052100559891315_FkaL_KDtq006Oz4dznScXztbPW1zqWqm_xDwZoPRUxLAatSIeMI3r1M-n1AvJs5ZV7ON0_4pYGKdEoQTxFT9aid0rvXqJR-obk0x4ThyG33w80W-7q-kipaqp8XH2qTLaktRXtGG\" width=\"523\">",
