    "id": "5651736615956204495",
    "text": {
      "text": "Why is the platform telling me to exercise before I can participate? ISO/NSO split grants. If you see anISO/NSO split tab on your security, that means your grant is subject to ISO/NSO split. Carta’s tender offer platform currently doesn’t allow this type of grants to participate. carta/public/11/images/7918907283661738101_OKxHMsRMfliTsPYBuyoZPCHggKh_DcvGHk_fkVPEdNQmJH3A8P83Ei61wK-5SHgqduyz7e3UvqROq37sf9awQ8lYRQbp9daBcwjoIpUL2HSBolxCh5gDAAMmxhlyptAddTuOzU1g  If you would like to tender those shares, reach out to liquidity@carta.com to split the grant. It takes 2-3 business days for the Carta team to complete the split for you to participate.  Here is an example of what you will see if attempting to sell with an ISO/NSO split grant: carta/public/11/images/8685967949651542684_00YMD1nykPZ8L_fgReH_RuBgSTaY3l7m8M1E1SdZV0GDrc_00pc8xEsL-zE9-ZeG4wA0aQ3cfPLJuNb_CQLems7PRvuK5PpqKLwmFNLy3XueIPbzn7nc2IA7947j8nM4wo6qzpbs",
      "originalText": "Why is the platform telling me to exercise before I can participate?<br>ISO/NSO split grants. If you see an ISO/NSO split tab on your security, that means your grant is subject to ISO/NSO split. Carta’s tender offer platform currently doesn’t allow this type of grants to participate.<br><img height=\"281\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7918907283661738101_OKxHMsRMfliTsPYBuyoZPCHggKh_DcvGHk_fkVPEdNQmJH3A8P83Ei61wK-5SHgqduyz7e3UvqROq37sf9awQ8lYRQbp9daBcwjoIpUL2HSBolxCh5gDAAMmxhlyptAddTuOzU1g\" width=\"527\"><br><br>If you would like to tender those shares, reach out to <a href=\"mailto:liquidity@carta.com\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">liquidity@carta.com</a> to split the grant. It takes 2-3 business days for the Carta team to complete the split for you to participate.<br><br>Here is an example of what you will see if attempting to sell with an ISO/NSO split grant:<br><img height=\"274\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8685967949651542684_00YMD1nykPZ8L_fgReH_RuBgSTaY3l7m8M1E1SdZV0GDrc_00pc8xEsL-zE9-ZeG4wA0aQ3cfPLJuNb_CQLems7PRvuK5PpqKLwmFNLy3XueIPbzn7nc2IA7947j8nM4wo6qzpbs\" width=\"526\">",
