{
  "id": "8272087620670446341",
  "subject": {
    "id": "8272087620670446341",
    "text": {
      "text": "How to Request a Capital Call"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-1237527566779751744",
    "text": {
      "text": "Carta fund administration customers can initiate a capital call using our request capital call form in the Carta app. Once you submit the details using the form your dedicated Carta fund administration team will prepare the capital call and send it back for your approval before sending the notices to LPs.",
      "originalText": "Carta fund administration customers can initiate a capital call using our request capital call form in the Carta app. Once you submit the details using the form your dedicated Carta fund administration team will prepare the capital call and send it back for your approval before sending the notices to LPs."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-7174564852393277718",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "Select the entity on the left sidebar that you would like to call capital from. carta/public/11/images/3448265758174331055_zHBYiBTgwdv9A89yOGFjadsiCTMCNcEFLC4gDKf3WaHsMT-3DQfOZteF92apr-QOpu93BXkJVvFAL0qPvc2Jnp6qGq8h_VwW708leQeJ3xwN3uuSMuqDR6bp7QUvyg2irCuB8ahu",
        "originalText": "Select the entity on the left sidebar that you would like to call capital from. &nbsp; <img height=\"324\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3448265758174331055_zHBYiBTgwdv9A89yOGFjadsiCTMCNcEFLC4gDKf3WaHsMT-3DQfOZteF92apr-QOpu93BXkJVvFAL0qPvc2Jnp6qGq8h_VwW708leQeJ3xwN3uuSMuqDR6bp7QUvyg2irCuB8ahu\" width=\"251\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/3448265758174331055_zHBYiBTgwdv9A89yOGFjadsiCTMCNcEFLC4gDKf3WaHsMT-3DQfOZteF92apr-QOpu93BXkJVvFAL0qPvc2Jnp6qGq8h_VwW708leQeJ3xwN3uuSMuqDR6bp7QUvyg2irCuB8ahu"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Select the Capital calls tab and then click the Request capital call button. carta/public/11/images/1497128610500703537_K4ry-fWnEVO6_zygGsPVJWX5fJb_siSVKe6GcrDUDFI6XD_Tkasrmx4LOwxdF-yt7RkzVcRO7w23vKpzp1TzxvDZvYN-QpGx3SK4QstXF_IURHp9erDtvtfUYnSyx2sK_kyLMUh5",
        "originalText": "Select the Capital calls tab and then click the Request capital call button. &nbsp; <img height=\"163\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1497128610500703537_K4ry-fWnEVO6_zygGsPVJWX5fJb_siSVKe6GcrDUDFI6XD_Tkasrmx4LOwxdF-yt7RkzVcRO7w23vKpzp1TzxvDZvYN-QpGx3SK4QstXF_IURHp9erDtvtfUYnSyx2sK_kyLMUh5\" width=\"796\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/1497128610500703537_K4ry-fWnEVO6_zygGsPVJWX5fJb_siSVKe6GcrDUDFI6XD_Tkasrmx4LOwxdF-yt7RkzVcRO7w23vKpzp1TzxvDZvYN-QpGx3SK4QstXF_IURHp9erDtvtfUYnSyx2sK_kyLMUh5"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Enter the below information that will show up on the capital call notice sent to LPs:Issue date: When LPs should be notified of this capital call.Due date: The date capital is due for LPs.Amount to call: Enter the total amount you would like to call. You can enter either a total dollar amount or call a percent of total commitments.Capital call purpose: Include a message to LPs to explain the reason for the capital call.Contacts to be CC'd: In addition to your Carta fund administration team, you can select other contacts at your fund to be cc'd on each of the email notices sent to LPs. This is optional. carta/public/11/images/198983815660672698_DCE3s2US3I14fgxwBWfdrt9R71WNogsfDov_wsNwtlNZ4gpk_ByD5wqgbLLkbI_i9LnE0HBMX7cKd98z8-JKZBXlBwnyn2XTS9JoOb4jeKUlBEYHxuLivbiMqCejPgVkS-WRX_oh",
        "originalText": "Enter the below information that will show up on the capital call notice sent to LPs:  Issue date: When LPs should be notified of this capital call. Due date: The date capital is due for LPs. Amount to call: Enter the total amount you would like to call. You can enter either a total dollar amount or call a percent of total commitments. Capital call purpose: Include a message to LPs to explain the reason for the capital call. Contacts to be CC'd: In addition to your Carta fund administration team, you can select other contacts at your fund to be cc'd on each of the email notices sent to LPs. This is optional. &nbsp; <img height=\"615\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/198983815660672698_DCE3s2US3I14fgxwBWfdrt9R71WNogsfDov_wsNwtlNZ4gpk_ByD5wqgbLLkbI_i9LnE0HBMX7cKd98z8-JKZBXlBwnyn2XTS9JoOb4jeKUlBEYHxuLivbiMqCejPgVkS-WRX_oh\" width=\"755\">  ",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/198983815660672698_DCE3s2US3I14fgxwBWfdrt9R71WNogsfDov_wsNwtlNZ4gpk_ByD5wqgbLLkbI_i9LnE0HBMX7cKd98z8-JKZBXlBwnyn2XTS9JoOb4jeKUlBEYHxuLivbiMqCejPgVkS-WRX_oh"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "When the capital call notices are sent to LPs they will be emailed a link to view their capital call notice. You can designate whether or not a LP must be logged in to their Carta account to view the capital call notice. carta/public/11/images/3558694595625460933_DfTEJFzfFYHznxMSgT2S3mV3qh7c3wp4SroFUE9dj0yJrNTs3ccHlVZ2xtUX-KPWETJBFuU_W5KU_pp888pNgSepbmi6gPOIP4Plv8wJoa4E_ALGS3wKiBOLUAkM35u_5O9YaVLT",
        "originalText": "When the capital call notices are sent to LPs they will be emailed a link to view their capital call notice. You can designate whether or not a LP must be logged in to their Carta account to view the capital call notice. &nbsp; <img height=\"199\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3558694595625460933_DfTEJFzfFYHznxMSgT2S3mV3qh7c3wp4SroFUE9dj0yJrNTs3ccHlVZ2xtUX-KPWETJBFuU_W5KU_pp888pNgSepbmi6gPOIP4Plv8wJoa4E_ALGS3wKiBOLUAkM35u_5O9YaVLT\" width=\"630\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/3558694595625460933_DfTEJFzfFYHznxMSgT2S3mV3qh7c3wp4SroFUE9dj0yJrNTs3ccHlVZ2xtUX-KPWETJBFuU_W5KU_pp888pNgSepbmi6gPOIP4Plv8wJoa4E_ALGS3wKiBOLUAkM35u_5O9YaVLT"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "If you have any other instructions that will help your fund administration team prepare the capital call notices you can enter them here. carta/public/11/images/7347940412475393538_w0_jCGDNADweiAPsCb_8CHntrcuF20a2uG_1kWV7GkEQpZsglT7ft-Hb19BZGPdt2MGFwDJLPOIByVOxKXw4GbFO2THcRaqbrkyFpWLfl4geqZCZ7W_2MW2sKdUMCLX8Fc1SqWHQ",
        "originalText": "If you have any other instructions that will help your fund administration team prepare the capital call notices you can enter them here. &nbsp; <img height=\"241\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7347940412475393538_w0_jCGDNADweiAPsCb_8CHntrcuF20a2uG_1kWV7GkEQpZsglT7ft-Hb19BZGPdt2MGFwDJLPOIByVOxKXw4GbFO2THcRaqbrkyFpWLfl4geqZCZ7W_2MW2sKdUMCLX8Fc1SqWHQ\" width=\"723\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/7347940412475393538_w0_jCGDNADweiAPsCb_8CHntrcuF20a2uG_1kWV7GkEQpZsglT7ft-Hb19BZGPdt2MGFwDJLPOIByVOxKXw4GbFO2THcRaqbrkyFpWLfl4geqZCZ7W_2MW2sKdUMCLX8Fc1SqWHQ"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Once you have completed filling in the form click the Submit request button. This will send a notification to your fund administration team who will prepare the capital call per your instructions. Before anything gets sent to LPs your team will have you approve the final details of the capital call notices.",
        "originalText": "Once you have completed filling in the form click the Submit request button. This will send a notification to your fund administration team who will prepare the capital call per your instructions. Before anything gets sent to LPs your team will have you approve the final details of the capital call notices."
      }]
    }
  }]
}

{
  "id": "8601494863569958860",
  "subject": {
    "id": "8601494863569958860",
    "text": {
      "text": "Renaming a Board Consent"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-5289906748172969774",
    "text": {
      "text": "Once a board consent is drafted or sent to the Board for approval, the Administrator can navigate back toBoard > Consents to rename the consents as needed. No notifications are sent when renaming a consent.",
      "originalText": "Once a board consent is drafted or sent to the Board for approval, the Administrator can navigate back to&nbsp;Board &gt; Consents&nbsp;to rename the consents as needed. No notifications are sent when renaming a consent."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-4153666616537193753",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "The board consent can be renamed from the consents ledger from the V dropdown and selecting Rename consent.  carta/public/11/images/4471842421713686563_rtaImage    The consent can also be renamed when viewing the consent from Actions > Rename consent.  carta/public/11/images/5663065694097657086_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "The board consent can be renamed from the consents ledger from the V dropdown and selecting Rename consent.<br> <img class=\"\" alt=\"Screenshot 2021-02-10 113734.png\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/4471842421713686563_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 626px;height: 275px;\"><br> <br> The consent can also be renamed when viewing the consent from Actions &gt; Rename consent.<br> <img alt=\"Screenshot 2021-02-10 114620.png\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5663065694097657086_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 644px;height: 246px;\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/5663065694097657086_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Enter in the updated name and click Save.  carta/public/11/images/1780808307773740378_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Enter in the updated name and click&nbsp;Save.<br> <img alt=\"image.png\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1780808307773740378_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 456px;height: 192px;\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/1780808307773740378_rtaImage"
        }
      }]
    }
  }]
}

