          "url": "carta/public/11/images/2145553235693249244_4qQf_TZxXfHGvkymctbZEPBzPfWHVnSUiTYoDyJ9zxnac2Kpq_9AeniQEYq3KGkqw-7U3qRdjvvuo6m89JhLuElsS6eI09wmz_mQJs7MFWgsvgWW_TEZCVWWUNrMi0cBuhMmrG49"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Select Address in the list of columns for the downloaded template and any other fields as needed. Click Download spreadsheet to download the template spreadsheet.  carta/public/11/images/2268559973942235052_aGES5PZl0pMsTZPTGmbO2fmT63bk0DN5e8S7L2JLIXvaMoKsNfpxUS4jN56w3ec_BMa_kQe8-rpdFPaGvwD8XB-avpIgLBowcaU4AAZj3w7oxMcIhjKEShd16ASmbIMktK5K5eJ1",
        "originalText": "Select Address in the list of columns for the downloaded template and any other fields as needed. Click Download spreadsheet to download the template spreadsheet.<br> <img height=\"293\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/2268559973942235052_aGES5PZl0pMsTZPTGmbO2fmT63bk0DN5e8S7L2JLIXvaMoKsNfpxUS4jN56w3ec_BMa_kQe8-rpdFPaGvwD8XB-avpIgLBowcaU4AAZj3w7oxMcIhjKEShd16ASmbIMktK5K5eJ1\" width=\"486\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/2268559973942235052_aGES5PZl0pMsTZPTGmbO2fmT63bk0DN5e8S7L2JLIXvaMoKsNfpxUS4jN56w3ec_BMa_kQe8-rpdFPaGvwD8XB-avpIgLBowcaU4AAZj3w7oxMcIhjKEShd16ASmbIMktK5K5eJ1"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "In the template, fill in the address information for all relevant stakeholders. For US-based stakeholders, make sure to use the 2-letter US state abbreviation when filling in the State column. For stakeholders based outside of the US, reference the Manage Stakeholder Addresses and Countries and Country Regions articles to find detailed information about how to look up and enter the country and country region codes accepted by Carta for the Country and State columns, respectively.    NOTE: Entering the correct country and country region codes is important because Carta’s tax system (which estimates option exercise tax withholding amounts) relies on these codes to determine tax jurisdictions.",
        "originalText": "In the template, fill in the address information for all relevant stakeholders. For US-based stakeholders, make sure to use the 2-letter US state abbreviation when filling in the State column. For stakeholders based outside of the US, reference the <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/managing-stakeholder-addresses#update-non-us\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Manage Stakeholder Addresses</u></a> and <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/countries-and-country-regions\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Countries and Country Regions</u></a> articles to find detailed information about how to look up and enter the country and country region codes accepted by Carta for the Country and State columns, respectively.<br> <br> NOTE: Entering the correct country and country region codes is important because Carta’s tax system (which estimates option exercise tax withholding amounts) relies on these codes to determine tax jurisdictions.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Save the template and re-import the file from the same screen as step 3. Resolve any reported validation errors in the imported file to ensure that the data is successfully saved in Carta.  carta/public/11/images/2348760491167602466_5omoZqcTlXteyqznFUjJM_6tpOrGbg4MqsQChq4qt5lEXd_gVYu9akXaCOBM7-mfmQZ_gata03CnNLkLAD4Ya63Ylr8xLFI68GdqiG_s_-g9qNiJWelcmXaY5VY7ecCKgOikQmu4    NOTE: The Manage Stakeholder Addresses article contains more information on how to update stakeholder addresses for companies tracking tax mobility. See the Tax mobility section in this article for an explanation of how tax mobility could affect your tax withholding obligations, and speak with a tax professional if you have further questions.",
        "originalText": "Save the template and re-import the file from the same screen as step 3. Resolve any reported validation errors in the imported file to ensure that the data is successfully saved in Carta.<br> <img height=\"137\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/2348760491167602466_5omoZqcTlXteyqznFUjJM_6tpOrGbg4MqsQChq4qt5lEXd_gVYu9akXaCOBM7-mfmQZ_gata03CnNLkLAD4Ya63Ylr8xLFI68GdqiG_s_-g9qNiJWelcmXaY5VY7ecCKgOikQmu4\" width=\"421\"><br> <br> NOTE: The <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/managing-stakeholder-addresses\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Manage Stakeholder Addresses</u></a> article contains more information on how to update stakeholder addresses for companies tracking tax mobility. See the Tax mobility section in this article for an explanation of how tax mobility could affect your tax withholding obligations, and speak with a tax professional if you have further questions.",
