{
  "id": "341120150550259556",
  "subject": {
    "id": "341120150550259556",
    "text": {
      "text": "Tax rules"
    },
    "signals": [{
      "valueL": "3"
    }]
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-4218449112918787453",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "Companies using our new tax functionality can take control over tax withholding calculations after navigating to Compliance > Tax rules.  carta/public/11/images/2117895333475894965_x5Pq_7Ws_1fE7KnhUBKa_KGCYwR2GLJBqELitK5_ncxptuMqcxfM_vsvcntEmWrS7ySwUTB15i1TTvD2oXpLCvRlERYQkVr9rWv_RLhZWLmUH8ZXkCL8SWTnI4e6Vr96f7O1bSX2",
        "originalText": "Companies using our new tax functionality can take control over tax withholding calculations after navigating to Compliance &gt; Tax rules.<br> <img height=\"92\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/2117895333475894965_x5Pq_7Ws_1fE7KnhUBKa_KGCYwR2GLJBqELitK5_ncxptuMqcxfM_vsvcntEmWrS7ySwUTB15i1TTvD2oXpLCvRlERYQkVr9rWv_RLhZWLmUH8ZXkCL8SWTnI4e6Vr96f7O1bSX2\" width=\"426\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/2117895333475894965_x5Pq_7Ws_1fE7KnhUBKa_KGCYwR2GLJBqELitK5_ncxptuMqcxfM_vsvcntEmWrS7ySwUTB15i1TTvD2oXpLCvRlERYQkVr9rWv_RLhZWLmUH8ZXkCL8SWTnI4e6Vr96f7O1bSX2"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "In the Tax jurisdictions and rates page, Administrators will be able to view and edit all tax rates and rules that apply to stakeholder tax withholdings. In addition, they can see the full list of jurisdictions and rates and filter to only show jurisdictions applicable to one or more of the company’s stakeholders if needed.  carta/public/11/images/1317415361657668573_vVvzYgxkXVwgvCxfen5-CieXpeJYMLbW7iphYk1M48LLFWjoaX3GEwOlZ2U1VK_3dySmOEy3XTrtiaGL4t0YHDb7YnIq_brwg-V39zPOOX3pVupdhlhEjECamgUvCTMUbYOqPhCb",
        "originalText": "In the Tax jurisdictions and rates page, Administrators will be able to view and edit all tax rates and rules that apply to stakeholder tax withholdings. In addition, they can see the full list of jurisdictions and rates and filter to only show jurisdictions applicable to one or more of the company’s stakeholders if needed.<br> <img height=\"166\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1317415361657668573_vVvzYgxkXVwgvCxfen5-CieXpeJYMLbW7iphYk1M48LLFWjoaX3GEwOlZ2U1VK_3dySmOEy3XTrtiaGL4t0YHDb7YnIq_brwg-V39zPOOX3pVupdhlhEjECamgUvCTMUbYOqPhCb\" width=\"431\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/1317415361657668573_vVvzYgxkXVwgvCxfen5-CieXpeJYMLbW7iphYk1M48LLFWjoaX3GEwOlZ2U1VK_3dySmOEy3XTrtiaGL4t0YHDb7YnIq_brwg-V39zPOOX3pVupdhlhEjECamgUvCTMUbYOqPhCb"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click on a row for a jurisdiction to reveal the rates and rules applicable to stakeholders with corresponding addresses based on the tax jurisdiction. Tax rates can be set on a flat or progressive level based on year-to-date income amounts. No payroll or fallback rates can be set for stakeholders that do not have any payroll year-to-date compensation information uploaded.  carta/public/11/images/6879142090751982807_vMx7R1EpWiIRZjDWvhi4h4kt4Hg8lVJeU_qmIPEY4KGdvV0dTnTp4qYgBQVq0otcm2PoRCbkrCB-_cb-3fUk-13FP1XGPcrVd7Mjl8XOM_ZO8vsCV9r9hnDHBnAyULZEzJ2_mpGt",
        "originalText": "Click on a row for a jurisdiction to reveal the rates and rules applicable to stakeholders with corresponding addresses based on the tax jurisdiction. Tax rates can be set on a flat or progressive level based on year-to-date income amounts. No payroll or fallback rates can be set for stakeholders that do not have any payroll year-to-date compensation information uploaded.<br> <img height=\"194\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6879142090751982807_vMx7R1EpWiIRZjDWvhi4h4kt4Hg8lVJeU_qmIPEY4KGdvV0dTnTp4qYgBQVq0otcm2PoRCbkrCB-_cb-3fUk-13FP1XGPcrVd7Mjl8XOM_ZO8vsCV9r9hnDHBnAyULZEzJ2_mpGt\" width=\"431\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/6879142090751982807_vMx7R1EpWiIRZjDWvhi4h4kt4Hg8lVJeU_qmIPEY4KGdvV0dTnTp4qYgBQVq0otcm2PoRCbkrCB-_cb-3fUk-13FP1XGPcrVd7Mjl8XOM_ZO8vsCV9r9hnDHBnAyULZEzJ2_mpGt"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Carta provides out-of-the-box tax rates for all US states and some international jurisdictions. Click the V drop down and select Edit jurisdiction rules to override the withholding events under which the tax rule applies.  carta/public/11/images/2972211644241447043_g7Qu8GHz0i3vCkkYVhiQXzhjQC1vnxrGEU-_h_Ku3kUm9T88Wch2nHNjnsDJeQRGmJLHGGWl0rSy90mUDyh0VTEhKGJrr2YzKHAJr55iJw8E3-K9zA4QykIi4tcPzMhBitr7cjp-",
        "originalText": "Carta provides out-of-the-box tax rates for all US states and some international jurisdictions. Click the V drop down and select Edit jurisdiction rules to override the withholding events under which the tax rule applies.<br> <img height=\"185\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/2972211644241447043_g7Qu8GHz0i3vCkkYVhiQXzhjQC1vnxrGEU-_h_Ku3kUm9T88Wch2nHNjnsDJeQRGmJLHGGWl0rSy90mUDyh0VTEhKGJrr2YzKHAJr55iJw8E3-K9zA4QykIi4tcPzMhBitr7cjp-\" width=\"434\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/2972211644241447043_g7Qu8GHz0i3vCkkYVhiQXzhjQC1vnxrGEU-_h_Ku3kUm9T88Wch2nHNjnsDJeQRGmJLHGGWl0rSy90mUDyh0VTEhKGJrr2YzKHAJr55iJw8E3-K9zA4QykIi4tcPzMhBitr7cjp-"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "When editing a jurisdiction, administrators can update which events trigger tax withholding. For companies tracking employee movement via our mobility taxation feature, companies can set the maximum number of days (i.e. Grace period) a stakeholder can remain in a jurisdiction before triggering tax calculation for that jurisdiction.  carta/public/11/images/7575077285289507742_8kPqaSPAe_7P8_tuqCSs4RWiuKV4ijMhGiS_t1vvhKNsZUOkyTyyn-z4CMKlfVcjecbpjXFRWVnXyN5vsQdbmlmxjNqdkMH2UgAw7lyLLFyzfhlZj5P3Wbc1zVKxoPytsWf2Yqja",
        "originalText": "When editing a jurisdiction, administrators can update which events trigger tax withholding. For companies tracking employee movement via our mobility taxation feature, companies can set the maximum number of days (i.e. Grace period) a stakeholder can remain in a jurisdiction before triggering tax calculation for that jurisdiction.<br> <img height=\"164\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7575077285289507742_8kPqaSPAe_7P8_tuqCSs4RWiuKV4ijMhGiS_t1vvhKNsZUOkyTyyn-z4CMKlfVcjecbpjXFRWVnXyN5vsQdbmlmxjNqdkMH2UgAw7lyLLFyzfhlZj5P3Wbc1zVKxoPytsWf2Yqja\" width=\"433\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/7575077285289507742_8kPqaSPAe_7P8_tuqCSs4RWiuKV4ijMhGiS_t1vvhKNsZUOkyTyyn-z4CMKlfVcjecbpjXFRWVnXyN5vsQdbmlmxjNqdkMH2UgAw7lyLLFyzfhlZj5P3Wbc1zVKxoPytsWf2Yqja"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "If an administrator overrides the rates or rules for a given jurisdiction, a checkmark will appear in the Customcolumn to indicate this override.  carta/public/11/images/4328444369015893453_h1vG4e9E1dWhkKMoNsctxUe2FO29LJ0kEdGnkEFVSO8PfLvqFDhX2pRr-7jKbm2j4lFawB5B7NXzhoJfRIqTQbYKDuKI2uB6WtQsvYWVCJ3ROq9Dcp0rkv0oh0mKcmthc8g3scvm",
        "originalText": "If an administrator overrides the rates or rules for a given jurisdiction, a checkmark will appear in the Custom column to indicate this override.<br> <img height=\"170\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/4328444369015893453_h1vG4e9E1dWhkKMoNsctxUe2FO29LJ0kEdGnkEFVSO8PfLvqFDhX2pRr-7jKbm2j4lFawB5B7NXzhoJfRIqTQbYKDuKI2uB6WtQsvYWVCJ3ROq9Dcp0rkv0oh0mKcmthc8g3scvm\" width=\"434\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/4328444369015893453_h1vG4e9E1dWhkKMoNsctxUe2FO29LJ0kEdGnkEFVSO8PfLvqFDhX2pRr-7jKbm2j4lFawB5B7NXzhoJfRIqTQbYKDuKI2uB6WtQsvYWVCJ3ROq9Dcp0rkv0oh0mKcmthc8g3scvm"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Administrators can also restore a jurisdiction to the Carta default by clicking the V drop down and selecting Restore jurisdiction.  carta/public/11/images/7737808959033067797_tcwY-rnQGDOTgaglzqOHZ8H_Ey780BFklavXVRaRHW6QLB_WZso53UFPVCJEavY-mjniWoe0yrdEuSAmlztEmVgAxYQYIJaEzBMR8Pxy4Iw_htY2R7JoiefQBemUPy_NI72lfx8O    NOTE: Carta periodically updates its default tax rates. If an administrator has overridden the default rates or rules for a jurisdiction, the updated default tax rates will not appear in Carta until the default rates are explicitly restored.  carta/public/11/images/1474915782966780811_GyiZUYhus_2gw9kAeJ9ndINZFsnee1xnyI-y10G4yI_9907GZ4Q1j_7TlWfursxyujCAgmZEZJ0vk8_J6uMgtSxci6crAPukT1iJsT8M9KE5XX9QeX7DIIS5S_wZvoNNFiHuO9Mm",
        "originalText": "Administrators can also restore a jurisdiction to the Carta default by clicking the V drop down and selecting Restore jurisdiction.<br> <img height=\"189\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7737808959033067797_tcwY-rnQGDOTgaglzqOHZ8H_Ey780BFklavXVRaRHW6QLB_WZso53UFPVCJEavY-mjniWoe0yrdEuSAmlztEmVgAxYQYIJaEzBMR8Pxy4Iw_htY2R7JoiefQBemUPy_NI72lfx8O\" width=\"430\"><br> <br> NOTE: Carta periodically updates its default tax rates. If an administrator has overridden the default rates or rules for a jurisdiction, the updated default tax rates will not appear in Carta until the default rates are explicitly restored.<br> <img height=\"165\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1474915782966780811_GyiZUYhus_2gw9kAeJ9ndINZFsnee1xnyI-y10G4yI_9907GZ4Q1j_7TlWfursxyujCAgmZEZJ0vk8_J6uMgtSxci6crAPukT1iJsT8M9KE5XX9QeX7DIIS5S_wZvoNNFiHuO9Mm\" width=\"430\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/1474915782966780811_GyiZUYhus_2gw9kAeJ9ndINZFsnee1xnyI-y10G4yI_9907GZ4Q1j_7TlWfursxyujCAgmZEZJ0vk8_J6uMgtSxci6crAPukT1iJsT8M9KE5XX9QeX7DIIS5S_wZvoNNFiHuO9Mm"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Tax jurisdictions can be added at the country, state/province, or local level, along with associated rates and rules. The jurisdictions and corresponding rates and rules will apply to stakeholders with matching address information. Review Updating stakeholder information for more information on how to properly track stakeholder addresses that drive tax withholding estimates.",
        "originalText": "Tax jurisdictions can be added at the country, state/province, or local level, along with associated rates and rules. The jurisdictions and corresponding rates and rules will apply to stakeholders with matching address information.&nbsp; Review <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/update-stakeholder-details\" target=\"_blank\">Updating stakeholder information</a> for more information on how to properly track stakeholder addresses that drive tax withholding estimates.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Issuers can add new tax rates at the jurisdiction level by selecting Add tax rates and selecting the calculation method and rate(s).  carta/public/11/images/525997822153128925_kVVn3gP8U12dUDB1oi6R_Pb_Sgwgwr109tFiNqNSDA-U4cZiZFJ-219eMxCSnWaTKxyfUfFaM7cx7XBQdtVXCZg-AIeAE9-6u-rMwpN0f7N52aTaoaRAA4wG1MUZV9DYq46Rd6cp",
        "originalText": "Issuers can add new tax rates at the jurisdiction level by selecting Add tax rates and selecting the calculation method and rate(s).<br> <img height=\"156\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/525997822153128925_kVVn3gP8U12dUDB1oi6R_Pb_Sgwgwr109tFiNqNSDA-U4cZiZFJ-219eMxCSnWaTKxyfUfFaM7cx7XBQdtVXCZg-AIeAE9-6u-rMwpN0f7N52aTaoaRAA4wG1MUZV9DYq46Rd6cp\" width=\"428\">",
        "associatedImage": {
