        }
      }, {
        "text": "Companies can edit existing tax rates by clicking the V drop down and selecting Edit tax rate.  carta/public/11/images/3502297752250405593_uNmEEwxZY0ZrLXO39zcn2RkwSOaEURN5u-Kqog3D1fPAV6xS5-F27RsHoaRMWQDLO4bX2KnS1rg4_EmX5cdApWlgwhqhuNtcesjOJ0vOR5Zrno8yuvyMUF-X8k_pajtLvZ7g9u_8",
