        "originalText": "From here, the rate calculation method and rate(s) can be edited. In this example, the administrator has changed California’s supplemental flat rate from 10.23% to 11%.<br> <img height=\"134\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1629058520639085076_68ZmUbfW98fMfSnlbRucccy22J0zpArZXEVMdLFtYoT1xKnGL2ueHW-lLxBnC2_4LRWqP12S6mgMw51Z5yAZU4rd8AA1dJaoRdlxSEzrQE8S2HcEOo8mM8ahBmaMOqykIzg3JM6c\" width=\"431\"><br> &nbsp;",
