{
  "id": "3867661898596164526",
  "subject": {
    "id": "3867661898596164526",
    "text": {
      "text": "Procedure",
      "originalText": "Procedure"
    },
    "signals": [{
      "valueL": "1"
    }]
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-4022540060679907423",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "Make sure Employee IDs match. The Carta + Workday integration is based on the Employee ID field. Ensure that your stakeholders have matching Employee IDs in Carta and Workday. Employee IDs in Carta can be bulk updated from the Stakeholders > All stakeholders page. Click Manage and select Update stakeholders.",
        "originalText": "Make sure Employee IDs match. The Carta + Workday integration is based on the Employee ID field. Ensure that your stakeholders have matching Employee IDs in Carta and Workday. Employee IDs in Carta can be bulk updated from the Stakeholders &gt; All stakeholders page. Click Manage and select Update stakeholders."
      }, {
        "text": "Find your Workday WSDL URL.Search for “Public Web Services” from your Workday dashboard to find the list of Workday web services available.Within the list of web services, find the Human Resources endpoint. Click on it and selectView WSDL.Scroll to the bottom of the page to find the WSDL URL, which will look something like:  https://wd2-impl-services1.workday.com/ccx/service/mycompany/Human_Resources/v36.0  There are two key pieces of information needed from the URL, the Domain and the Tenant. The URL is always structured as https://{{domain}}/ccx/service/{{tenant}}/Human_Resources/{{version}}, so in the case of our example, these are the fields you need. Copy and save a copy of these fields, as they will be needed later in the process.  Example domain = wd2-impl-services1.workday.com  Example tenant = mycompany  NOTE: the domain and tenant fields are case sensitive.",
        "originalText": "Find your Workday WSDL URL.  Search for “Public Web Services” from your Workday dashboard to find the list of Workday web services available.<br> &nbsp; Within the list of web services, find the Human Resources endpoint. Click on it and select View WSDL.<br> &nbsp; Scroll to the bottom of the page to find the WSDL URL, which will look something like:<br> https://wd2-impl-services1.workday.com/ccx/service/mycompany/Human_Resources/v36.0&nbsp;<br> <br> There are two key pieces of information needed from the URL, the Domain and the Tenant. The URL is always structured as https://{{domain}}/ccx/service/{{tenant}}/Human_Resources/{{version}}, so in the case of our example, these are the fields you need. Copy and save a copy of these fields, as they will be needed later in the process.<br> <br> Example domain = wd2-impl-services1.workday.com<br> Example tenant = mycompany<br> <br> NOTE: the domain and tenant fields are case sensitive.  "
      }, {
        "text": "Create a Workday Integration System User. The Integration System User is the Workday user that the Carta integration will use to connect. Save the user’s username and password, as these access credentials will be needed later in the process.",
        "originalText": "Create a Workday Integration System User. The Integration System User is the Workday user that the Carta integration will use to connect. Save the user’s username and password, as these access credentials will be needed later in the process.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Work with your company’s Workday administrator to create and configure an Integration System User for Carta. The user should have the following permissions configured:OperationDomain Security PolicyDomain Security Policies Inheriting PermissionFunctional AreasGet OnlyPerson Data: Home AddressContact InformationGet OnlyPerson Data: Home EmailContact InformationGet OnlyPerson Data: Legal NameContact InformationGet OnlyPerson Data: Home Contact InformationPerson Data: Home PhoneContact InformationGet OnlyPerson Data: Work EmailContact InformationGet OnlyWorker Data: TerminationsStaffingGet OnlyWorker Data: Current Staffing InformationStaffingGet OnlyPerson Data: Date of BirthPersonal DataGet OnlyWorker Data: Worker IDPersonal DataGet OnlyPerson Data: Government IDsPersonal DataGet OnlyWorker Data: Active EmployeesStaffingGet OnlyWorker Data: All PositionsStaffingGet OnlyWorker Data: Public Worker ReportsStaffing",
        "originalText": "Work with your company’s Workday administrator to create and configure an Integration System User for Carta. The user should have the following permissions configured:  &nbsp;                    Operation   Domain Security Policy   Domain Security Policies Inheriting Permission   Functional Areas    Get Only Person Data: Home Address &nbsp; Contact Information   Get Only Person Data: Home Email &nbsp; Contact Information   Get Only Person Data: Legal Name &nbsp; Contact Information   Get Only Person Data: Home Contact Information Person Data: Home Phone Contact Information   Get Only Person Data: Work Email &nbsp; Contact Information   Get Only Worker Data: Terminations &nbsp; Staffing   Get Only Worker Data: Current Staffing Information &nbsp; Staffing   Get Only Person Data: Date of Birth &nbsp; Personal Data   Get Only Worker Data: Worker ID &nbsp; Personal Data   Get Only Person Data: Government IDs &nbsp; Personal Data   Get Only Worker Data: Active Employees &nbsp; Staffing   Get Only Worker Data: All Positions &nbsp; Staffing   Get Only Worker Data: Public Worker Reports &nbsp; Staffing    <br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Create the Workday Integration in Carta. In Carta, navigate to Company > Settings > Integrations, and select Workday as the provider.  carta/public/11/images/5808049405630496456_2V8GSiFnzLXqenAZwV6nHBDXl84zbyPE-iqU6rDavC_t3GQj_9zb-xv-U85crzaUzPN9_5w_dg1XY87NcPmyjTHN1OaaIM_HVGmCFgEL_bruoO4yimDSaW3McR7WufeROHKSTTOa",
        "originalText": "Create the Workday Integration in Carta. In Carta, navigate to Company &gt; Settings &gt; Integrations, and select Workday as the provider.<br> <img height=\"262\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5808049405630496456_2V8GSiFnzLXqenAZwV6nHBDXl84zbyPE-iqU6rDavC_t3GQj_9zb-xv-U85crzaUzPN9_5w_dg1XY87NcPmyjTHN1OaaIM_HVGmCFgEL_bruoO4yimDSaW3McR7WufeROHKSTTOa\" width=\"429\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/5808049405630496456_2V8GSiFnzLXqenAZwV6nHBDXl84zbyPE-iqU6rDavC_t3GQj_9zb-xv-U85crzaUzPN9_5w_dg1XY87NcPmyjTHN1OaaIM_HVGmCFgEL_bruoO4yimDSaW3McR7WufeROHKSTTOa"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Set the Integration Name. Set a name that you will use to refer to this integration,  Then click Next: authorize access.  carta/public/11/images/202209119258158695_LS93fQ6b_Vn8h4_YsUNavRp5M9dCBmNuw-P8BdflaY4Ot_dDKUJMZGA4jx_Rwu2qCPZ7b-1CJrTP0d_5wXhDFWqbtzBOyZ7zYw1LnQvCDGxeLhjKy9hHgerLcCA_DySFs1QTon9B",
        "originalText": "Set the Integration Name. Set a name that you will use to refer to this integration,<br> Then click Next: authorize access.<br> <img height=\"171\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/202209119258158695_LS93fQ6b_Vn8h4_YsUNavRp5M9dCBmNuw-P8BdflaY4Ot_dDKUJMZGA4jx_Rwu2qCPZ7b-1CJrTP0d_5wXhDFWqbtzBOyZ7zYw1LnQvCDGxeLhjKy9hHgerLcCA_DySFs1QTon9B\" width=\"429\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/202209119258158695_LS93fQ6b_Vn8h4_YsUNavRp5M9dCBmNuw-P8BdflaY4Ot_dDKUJMZGA4jx_Rwu2qCPZ7b-1CJrTP0d_5wXhDFWqbtzBOyZ7zYw1LnQvCDGxeLhjKy9hHgerLcCA_DySFs1QTon9B"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Fill in the Access Credentials. Fill the access fields using the values from previous steps (Steps 2 and 3):Your Workday domain (e.g. wd2-impl-services1.workday.com)Your Workday tenant (e.g. mycompany)Your Workday username (e.g. ISU_Carta)Your Workday password (e.g. Carta123!)   Then click Next: test connection.  carta/public/11/images/1070853878664701669_qmjN3Wo_9Y0-xrdv-2ssDddEC8uU2nkDkfgSC-2BtbNMRLoELlNfv4VeYFtAivlwoF1ZoMpGlm9DaHFHGq5wWA7AX0mgH5NpCE4_kQqQhfSj9rhkUMTMtDXBBHbjZ5WLvMwvxkmz",
        "originalText": "Fill in the Access Credentials. Fill the access fields using the values from previous steps (Steps 2 and 3):  Your Workday domain (e.g. wd2-impl-services1.workday.com) Your Workday tenant (e.g. mycompany) Your Workday username (e.g. ISU_Carta) Your Workday password (e.g. Carta123!)  <br> Then click Next: test connection.<br> <img height=\"233\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1070853878664701669_qmjN3Wo_9Y0-xrdv-2ssDddEC8uU2nkDkfgSC-2BtbNMRLoELlNfv4VeYFtAivlwoF1ZoMpGlm9DaHFHGq5wWA7AX0mgH5NpCE4_kQqQhfSj9rhkUMTMtDXBBHbjZ5WLvMwvxkmz\" width=\"430\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/1070853878664701669_qmjN3Wo_9Y0-xrdv-2ssDddEC8uU2nkDkfgSC-2BtbNMRLoELlNfv4VeYFtAivlwoF1ZoMpGlm9DaHFHGq5wWA7AX0mgH5NpCE4_kQqQhfSj9rhkUMTMtDXBBHbjZ5WLvMwvxkmz"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Test the Connection. Click on Test connection to ensure that your credentials are valid.  carta/public/11/images/5375784088797627816_XY9qJa1UVxJiVdatxZmA-oRZw4hGeZQBuKeLaMxTxYBdiYlQq4fV1iCGHjMIsCrS_ufmI3e0r_Hix21AmM9a0suVCH5_HLDZBf7mm631KqfcW2_DyTMkemxvXMz2UlhbwdfpwLWW",
        "originalText": "Test the Connection. Click on Test connection to ensure that your credentials are valid.<br> <img height=\"168\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5375784088797627816_XY9qJa1UVxJiVdatxZmA-oRZw4hGeZQBuKeLaMxTxYBdiYlQq4fV1iCGHjMIsCrS_ufmI3e0r_Hix21AmM9a0suVCH5_HLDZBf7mm631KqfcW2_DyTMkemxvXMz2UlhbwdfpwLWW\" width=\"431\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/5375784088797627816_XY9qJa1UVxJiVdatxZmA-oRZw4hGeZQBuKeLaMxTxYBdiYlQq4fV1iCGHjMIsCrS_ufmI3e0r_Hix21AmM9a0suVCH5_HLDZBf7mm631KqfcW2_DyTMkemxvXMz2UlhbwdfpwLWW"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "If the integration is able to connect successfully, the screen will show the test was completed, then click Next: import employees ids which will match Employee IDs between Workday and Carta.  carta/public/11/images/2273138679793215787_SpN5fP9Dr9g7wvgzzlz8VONhjqSJOfQQCmEAuRj_tSPFgaDGs7xt_M63Q2wzY9sBaKAYKM6Wqs7pl0WwAj4Pgyj3X9seRaVeIyKJLFOziZDNvtXnDjQwolKyC0lR604Ghnpo-gLF",
        "originalText": "If the integration is able to connect successfully, the screen will show the test was completed, then click Next: import employees ids which will match Employee IDs between Workday and Carta.<br> <img height=\"144\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/2273138679793215787_SpN5fP9Dr9g7wvgzzlz8VONhjqSJOfQQCmEAuRj_tSPFgaDGs7xt_M63Q2wzY9sBaKAYKM6Wqs7pl0WwAj4Pgyj3X9seRaVeIyKJLFOziZDNvtXnDjQwolKyC0lR604Ghnpo-gLF\" width=\"433\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/2273138679793215787_SpN5fP9Dr9g7wvgzzlz8VONhjqSJOfQQCmEAuRj_tSPFgaDGs7xt_M63Q2wzY9sBaKAYKM6Wqs7pl0WwAj4Pgyj3X9seRaVeIyKJLFOziZDNvtXnDjQwolKyC0lR604Ghnpo-gLF"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Agree to the Terms and Conditions by checking the box, then click Submit and activate integration.  carta/public/11/images/6184567923864724044_4kka9nthPOq6Eow-EzgbXx_-G-1dwn0QDYgJuDfM_FDZee8r2Sy4ft5xJgWYqzcYOurGcExVFJOUGfm0g3CGPSp-cLh74-XiIJKrUOb3ZYFglam0ir_m-mfmKMfdnVJqtCBYtak8",
        "originalText": "Agree to the Terms and Conditions by checking the box, then click Submit and activate integration.<br> <img height=\"224\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6184567923864724044_4kka9nthPOq6Eow-EzgbXx_-G-1dwn0QDYgJuDfM_FDZee8r2Sy4ft5xJgWYqzcYOurGcExVFJOUGfm0g3CGPSp-cLh74-XiIJKrUOb3ZYFglam0ir_m-mfmKMfdnVJqtCBYtak8\" width=\"430\"><br> &nbsp;",
