{
  "id": "5997804716036389373",
  "subject": {
    "id": "5997804716036389373",
    "text": {
      "text": "Enabling Online Transactions (US companies) - Beta"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-7458084941658994751",
    "text": {
      "text": "This article details the instructions for enabling online transactions and controlling option exercising settings with a feature that is currently being rolled out. All US customers will have access to this feature by February 26, 2021.",
      "originalText": "This article details the instructions for enabling online transactions and controlling option exercising settings with a feature that is currently being rolled out. All US customers will have access to this feature by February &nbsp;26, 2021.&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-6799918755804576876",
    "text": {
      "text": "If you do not currently have this view, review the instructions for the old method.  US private companies can enable online transactions to allow option exercise, repurchases, and other transactions to be executed online.  For option exercising, this enables optionholders to submit exercise requests online. After admin approval, Carta Payments collects funds from optionholders using ACH (US optionholders) or wire transfer (non-US optionholders). After receiving the funds in full, the collected funds are deposited via ACH into the company’s preferred deposit bank account. Shares are then issued to shareholders and their certificates will appear on the company’s cap table.  NOTE: Certificate issue dates depend on payment method. ACH exercises use the exercise request date. Wire transfer exercises use the fully-funded date.",
      "originalText": "If you do not currently have this view, <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/online-transactions\" target=\"_blank\">review the instructions for the old method</a>.&nbsp;<br><br>US private companies can enable online transactions to allow option exercise, repurchases, and other transactions to be executed online.&nbsp;<br><br>For option exercising, this enables optionholders to submit exercise requests online. After admin approval, Carta Payments collects funds from optionholders using ACH (US optionholders) or wire transfer (non-US optionholders). After receiving the funds in full, the collected funds are deposited via ACH into the company’s preferred deposit bank account. Shares are then issued to shareholders and their certificates will appear on the company’s cap table.&nbsp;<br><br>NOTE: Certificate issue dates depend on payment method. ACH exercises use the exercise request date. Wire transfer exercises use the fully-funded date.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "5529927811111646386",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "To enable or disable online transactions, navigate to Company > Settings > Transaction Settings. To enable for the first time, click the Set upbutton.   carta/public/11/images/3075555950479802646_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "To enable or disable online transactions, navigate to Company &gt; Settings &gt; Transaction Settings. To enable for the first time, click the Set up button.&nbsp;<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3075555950479802646_rtaImage\" width=\"90%\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/3075555950479802646_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "When enabling for the first time, review and agree to the Carta Option Exercise Payment Terms.  carta/public/11/images/6751724085658341381_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "When enabling for the first time, review and agree to the Carta Option Exercise Payment Terms.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6751724085658341381_rtaImage\" width=\"90%\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/6751724085658341381_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Select the preferred deposit bank account. If there is no bank account set up yet for online transactions, click on the Connect payment method button.     carta/public/11/images/7077327728549100982_rtaImage    If a bank account is set up for online transactions, review the account to ensure it is correct.  carta/public/11/images/2765135500814764574_C_aww2sIFz1zRDwivDl6BEz_jJFAFyhdQgwjKM6H5at2IjULZF1KmWoMgKsaoKSH--OVUmk3lfMX7g2Q3IN2sLDkhprcVWpy2WXaBJpl-OyOz-kX1s5h30jO9MFutF9dlviFyZjY    To select a different account, click Change account. You can select an existing payment account or connect a new payment account. For more details on connecting payment accounts, review the Company Payment Information support article.  carta/public/11/images/1062243194496905678_OzFRVuROJsSgsMnvmrV9y011xK420qk4E_OWN_7Cs9wzp4JZ9c9gFtqsyU-hxOawz7hNOXPM57aHei-DmOKylsJCajxEY_LloirZZsIz8htZuWerljoHsOhfSHbh0JCpwwtU3FAJ",
        "originalText": "Select the preferred deposit bank account.&nbsp;If there is no bank account set up yet for online transactions, click on the Connect payment method button.&nbsp;<br> <br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7077327728549100982_rtaImage\" width=\"90%\"><br> <br> If a bank account is set up for online transactions, review the account to ensure it is correct.<br> <img src=\"carta/public/11/images/2765135500814764574_C_aww2sIFz1zRDwivDl6BEz_jJFAFyhdQgwjKM6H5at2IjULZF1KmWoMgKsaoKSH--OVUmk3lfMX7g2Q3IN2sLDkhprcVWpy2WXaBJpl-OyOz-kX1s5h30jO9MFutF9dlviFyZjY\" width=\"90%\"><br> <br> To select a different account, click Change account. You can select an existing payment account or connect a new payment account. For more details on connecting payment accounts, review the <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/company-payment-information\" target=\"_blank\">Company Payment Information support article</a>.<br> <img src=\"carta/public/11/images/1062243194496905678_OzFRVuROJsSgsMnvmrV9y011xK420qk4E_OWN_7Cs9wzp4JZ9c9gFtqsyU-hxOawz7hNOXPM57aHei-DmOKylsJCajxEY_LloirZZsIz8htZuWerljoHsOhfSHbh0JCpwwtU3FAJ\" width=\"90%\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/1062243194496905678_OzFRVuROJsSgsMnvmrV9y011xK420qk4E_OWN_7Cs9wzp4JZ9c9gFtqsyU-hxOawz7hNOXPM57aHei-DmOKylsJCajxEY_LloirZZsIz8htZuWerljoHsOhfSHbh0JCpwwtU3FAJ"
