    "id": "-8046395609353727330",
    "text": {
      "text": "How does Carta integrate with Namely?"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-7196399061714410355",
    "text": {
      "text": "Namely is HR software for mid-sized companies, designed to be used by everyone, every day. Carta has a built-in API integration with Namely that synchronizes information between systems.  Integrating Carta with Namely creates a seamless experience in Carta for employee updates and departures. Carta admins can then minimize the time spent on manual tasks, and eliminate the risk of making a mistake.  The integration provides the following benefits:",
      "originalText": "<a href=\"https://namely.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Namely</a> is HR software for mid-sized companies, designed to be used by everyone, every day. Carta has a built-in API integration with Namely that synchronizes information between systems.<br><br>Integrating Carta with Namely creates a seamless experience in Carta for employee updates and departures. Carta admins can then minimize the time spent on manual tasks, and eliminate the risk of making a mistake.<br><br>The integration provides the following benefits:"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-1843057336366000994",
    "list": {
      "item": [{
        "text": "Flagging Terminated Employees. Employee terminations made in Namely appear as pending termination events in Carta",
        "originalText": "Flagging Terminated Employees. Employee terminations made in Namely appear as pending termination events in Carta"
      }, {
        "text": "Flagging Stakeholder Updates. Employee profile updates made in Namely appear as pending stakeholder profile updates in Carta",
        "originalText": "Flagging Stakeholder Updates. Employee profile updates made in Namely appear as pending stakeholder profile updates in Carta"
      }, {
        "text": "Easy setup. The integration can be set up quickly, without involving support or engineering",
        "originalText": "Easy setup. The integration can be set up quickly, without involving support or engineering"
      }, {
        "text": "Automatic daily synchronization. Once a day, Carta automatically pulls data from Namely and presents pending employee updates",
        "originalText": "Automatic daily synchronization. Once a day, Carta automatically pulls data from Namely and&nbsp;presents pending employee updates"
      }, {
        "text": "On-demand synchronization. Carta can check for updates on-demand any time by admins",
        "originalText": "On-demand synchronization. Carta can check for updates on-demand any time by admins"
      }]
