        "text": "Make sure Employee IDs match. The Carta + Namely integration is based on the Employee ID field. Ensure that your stakeholders have matching Employee IDs in Carta and Namely. Employee IDs in Carta can be bulk updated from the Stakeholders > All stakeholders page. Click Manageand select Update stakeholders.    Ensure that the Carta Stakeholder Employee ID field is updated with the Namely Employee Number, not the Namely Employee ID.  carta/public/11/images/4985803631453346292_p9T1W79lw_fvLVHz6h12dKrp4fPHENLgIL8FaQI6s1zU0cWpKx2ANanOHxrC_GMaPqE_d_s3IODOMcO6io8GAgqGl0tOoYyyGCLLfVnqyCoeQJxmGmtXLILmhaPzONi2jNSYkqgC",
