        "text": "Find your Namely Domain. Inspect the website address you use to login to Namely; this is your company name. Copy this value and save it for later.    For example, if you login to Namely by navigating to https://mycompany.namely.com/, then your domain is “mycompany”.  carta/public/11/images/542479248771965051_k5FrZ0pXMK4qxSOmG_6D8Q-sncU_GbCTQZp5xwT0JMonnP8EGzjBFSgOTJ3slcq3u85EPQISg0FUY3TPYrHmRi0aOYhLKtHub_62KeZRqZXFHFdVP5WE5P-gcczbP-24h---GrUq",
