        "text": "If the integration is able to connect successfully, the screen will show the test was completed, then click Next: import employees ids which will match Employee IDs between Namely and Carta.  carta/public/11/images/3470959158729061475_3R9Xl2350a8xwUhTCouj2-lo57XgYsVJhxKS_k32OiGo1Xi85u5GvCjUbMsS6I_bElHoD9jGYZmkLix0C-ylmcJiLO8o1lTQQ2UZ3RBLzaAD7_npYQssCpLG-4r_SqoI61jedU-j",
