        "text": "Make sure Employee IDs match. The Carta + BambooHR integration is based on the Employee ID field. Ensure that your stakeholders have matching Employee IDs in Carta and BambooHR. Employee IDs in Carta can be bulk updated from the Stakeholders > All stakeholders page. Click Manage and select Update stakeholders.    Ensure that the Carta Stakeholder Employee ID field is updated with the BambooHR Employee Number, not the BambooHR Employee ID.  carta/public/11/images/8680356165492208663_8OmXoVYrxN90emHGMtRDgcbqhpbdhaDBLRqEsz-SIGmaoUJInAAus5np0xkK4xRM3Kl5c5w7dN6J8sExkxvmtpL-a4NMdel9JSvCkQeGDfILIgpbYg_BvSTbD4aKAtzn9ZkdpVOq",
        "originalText": "Make sure Employee IDs match. The Carta + BambooHR integration is based on the Employee ID field. Ensure that your stakeholders have matching Employee IDs in Carta and BambooHR. Employee IDs in Carta can be bulk updated from the Stakeholders &gt; All stakeholders page. Click Manage and select Update stakeholders.<br> <br> Ensure that the Carta Stakeholder Employee ID field is updated with the BambooHR Employee Number, not the BambooHR Employee ID.<br> <img height=\"265\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8680356165492208663_8OmXoVYrxN90emHGMtRDgcbqhpbdhaDBLRqEsz-SIGmaoUJInAAus5np0xkK4xRM3Kl5c5w7dN6J8sExkxvmtpL-a4NMdel9JSvCkQeGDfILIgpbYg_BvSTbD4aKAtzn9ZkdpVOq\" width=\"259\"><br> &nbsp;",
