    "id": "4713527755485595828",
    "text": {
      "text": "How does Carta integrate with Workday?"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "4382664170510195573",
    "text": {
      "text": "Workday offers enterprise-level software solutions for financial management, human resources, and planning. Carta has a built-in API integration with Workday that synchronizes information between systems.  Integrating Carta with Workday creates a seamless experience in Carta for employee updates and departures. Carta admins can then minimize the time spent on manual tasks, and eliminate the risk of making a mistake.  The integration provides the following benefits:",
      "originalText": "<a href=\"https://www.workday.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Workday</a> offers enterprise-level software solutions for financial management, human resources, and planning. Carta has a built-in API integration with Workday that synchronizes information between systems.<br><br>Integrating Carta with Workday creates a seamless experience in Carta for employee updates and departures. Carta admins can then minimize the time spent on manual tasks, and eliminate the risk of making a mistake.<br><br>The integration provides the following benefits:"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-1545657091701377767",
    "list": {
      "item": [{
        "text": "Flagging Terminated Employees. Employee terminations made in Workday appear as pending termination events in Carta",
        "originalText": "Flagging Terminated Employees. Employee terminations made in Workday appear as pending termination events in Carta"
      }, {
        "text": "Flagging Stakeholder Updates. Employee profile updates made in Workday appear as pending stakeholder profile updates in Carta",
        "originalText": "Flagging Stakeholder Updates. Employee profile updates made in Workday appear as pending stakeholder profile updates in Carta"
      }, {
        "text": "Easy setup. The integration can be set up quickly, without involving support or engineering",
        "originalText": "Easy setup. The integration can be set up quickly, without involving support or engineering"
      }, {
        "text": "Automatic daily synchronization. Once a day, Carta automatically pulls data from Workday and presents pending employee updates",
        "originalText": "Automatic daily synchronization. Once a day, Carta automatically pulls data from Workday and&nbsp;presents pending employee updates"
      }, {
        "text": "On-demand synchronization. Carta can check for updates on-demand any time by admins",
        "originalText": "On-demand synchronization. Carta can check for updates on-demand any time by admins"
      }]
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-5795633965413131250",
    "text": {
