    "id": "-7428931126953951011",
    "text": {
      "text": "The Carta integration with Workday flags stakeholder terminations in Workday. From there, the Carta admin can take action to also terminate the stakeholder in Carta.  In order to terminate a stakeholder in Carta, the following data points are required:",
      "originalText": "The Carta integration with Workday flags stakeholder terminations in Workday. From there, the Carta admin can take action to also terminate the stakeholder in Carta.<br><br>In order to terminate a stakeholder in Carta, the following data points are required:"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-4647085794214961741",
    "list": {
      "item": [{
        "text": "Termination Date",
        "originalText": "Termination Date"
      }, {
        "text": "Termination Type",
        "originalText": "Termination Type"
      }, {
        "text": "New Relationship",
        "originalText": "New Relationship"
      }, {
        "text": "New email",
        "originalText": "New email"
      }]
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-3661891202492796550",
    "text": {
      "text": "The Carta integration can pull theTermination Date andEmailfrom Workday.  Each time the integration checks for updates, it searches for employees that haveTermination Dates in Workday, but are not reflected in Carta. If such employees are found, they are shown in thePending stakeholder terminations screen.  There are two kinds of pending terminations that can be shown.",
      "originalText": "The Carta integration can pull the Termination Date and Email from Workday.<br><br>Each time the integration checks for updates, it searches for employees that have Termination Dates in Workday, but are not reflected in Carta. If such employees are found, they are shown in the Pending stakeholder terminations screen.<br><br>There are two kinds of pending terminations that can be shown."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "8937744424126003510",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
