  "subject": {
    "id": "940418949328500280",
    "text": {
      "text": "How does Carta integrate with BambooHR?"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-1894478319152618968",
    "text": {
      "text": "Learn about how to set up the integration with BambooHR.",
      "originalText": "<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/integration-bamboohr\" target=\"_blank\">Learn about how to set up the integration with BambooHR</a>.<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "4021700492715138114",
    "text": {
      "text": "BambooHR is all-in-one HR software made for small and medium businesses and the people who work in them. Carta has a built-in API integration with BambooHR that synchronizes information between systems.  Integrating Carta with BambooHR creates a seamless experience in Carta for employee updates and departures. Carta admins can then minimize the time spent on manual tasks, and eliminate the risk of making a mistake.",
      "originalText": "<a href=\"https://bamboohr.com/\" target=\"_blank\">BambooHR</a> is all-in-one HR software made for small and medium businesses and the people who work in them. Carta has a built-in API integration with BambooHR that synchronizes information between systems.<br><br>Integrating Carta with BambooHR creates a seamless experience in Carta for employee updates and departures. Carta admins can then minimize the time spent on manual tasks, and eliminate the risk of making a mistake."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "8199880011809074795",
    "text": {
      "text": "The integration provides the following benefits:",
      "originalText": "The integration provides the following benefits:"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-5482702859479907283",
    "list": {
      "item": [{
        "text": "Flagging Terminated Employees. Employee terminations made in BambooHR appear as pending termination events in Carta.",
        "originalText": "Flagging Terminated Employees. Employee terminations made in BambooHR appear as pending termination events in Carta."
      }, {
        "text": "Flagging Stakeholder Updates. Employee profile updates made in BambooHR appear as pending stakeholder profile updates in Carta.",
        "originalText": "Flagging Stakeholder Updates. Employee profile updates made in BambooHR appear as pending stakeholder profile updates in Carta."
      }, {
        "text": "Easy setup. The integration can be set up quickly, without involving support or engineering.",
        "originalText": "Easy setup. The integration can be set up quickly, without involving support or engineering."
      }, {
        "text": "Automatic daily synchronization. Once a day, Carta automatically pulls data from BambooHR and presents pending employee updates.",
        "originalText": "Automatic daily synchronization. Once a day, Carta automatically pulls data from BambooHR and presents pending employee updates."
      }, {
        "text": "On-demand synchronization. Carta can check for updates on-demand any time by admins.",
        "originalText": "On-demand synchronization. Carta can check for updates on-demand any time by admins."
      }]
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-5550406779587426830",
    "text": {
      "text": "To set up the integration, follow the instructions on how to set up an integration with BambooHR here. Once setup is complete, you can:",
      "originalText": "To set up the integration, follow the instructions on <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/integration-bamboohr\" target=\"_blank\"><u>how to set up an integration with BambooHR here</u>.</a> Once setup is complete, you can:"
    }
