        "originalText": "Navigate to Securities &gt; Templates.<br> <img height=\"174\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/619282680561405344_EpvHyvtwXOAZ9Bp9ve0zJY4fMtl3PoxAS-3CWv9x1WKPMcxlpfDsUD9XFGJvMB9uplkV901BLD0jX0d4R7tUxomD-021wuDo_Y3KMEtrwqmOGBs-YSfNGKzxG8JLymshDsan7pBr\" width=\"432\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/619282680561405344_EpvHyvtwXOAZ9Bp9ve0zJY4fMtl3PoxAS-3CWv9x1WKPMcxlpfDsUD9XFGJvMB9uplkV901BLD0jX0d4R7tUxomD-021wuDo_Y3KMEtrwqmOGBs-YSfNGKzxG8JLymshDsan7pBr"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "In the Performance conditions tab, click Create performance condition to set up a new performance condition.  carta/public/11/images/3532068777437232342_A0WSqez08zPrRGSIPA_qaylnn5SOy5TJYndPyel8WmzrGg0gsnXxRYzq6wj1pXWBGZixTFbaMWvEXFTZr49hYgjYm89LwhHkyPOUJWnS7O7Fa_lKpgvrEELOBgPOG7uyePp9cnov",
        "originalText": "In the Performance conditions tab, click Create performance condition to set up a new performance condition.<br> <img height=\"96\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3532068777437232342_A0WSqez08zPrRGSIPA_qaylnn5SOy5TJYndPyel8WmzrGg0gsnXxRYzq6wj1pXWBGZixTFbaMWvEXFTZr49hYgjYm89LwhHkyPOUJWnS7O7Fa_lKpgvrEELOBgPOG7uyePp9cnov\" width=\"430\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/3532068777437232342_A0WSqez08zPrRGSIPA_qaylnn5SOy5TJYndPyel8WmzrGg0gsnXxRYzq6wj1pXWBGZixTFbaMWvEXFTZr49hYgjYm89LwhHkyPOUJWnS7O7Fa_lKpgvrEELOBgPOG7uyePp9cnov"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Add the Condition name and set the Condition type.Event based performance conditions are typically used for liquidity events and pay out at either 0 or 100% of target.Non-market based andMarket based performance conditions can have both variable (pay out at greater than or less than 100%) or non variable payouts.Market based performance conditions use metrics that are based on the company’s stock price, whileNon-market based are typically operational or business goals that do not include the company’s stock price.   The Vests post-termination toggle is used to indicate whether awards that have time vested will pay out upon performance achievement if the stakeholder terminates between time vest and performance achievement.SelectingYes will allow stakeholders that have met the time vesting criteria to keep the award if they term before the performance condition has been met.SelectingNo will cause participants to forfeit the award if they have not met both the time vesting and performance condition upon termination. carta/public/11/images/472496775211988723_FUccAKcb2cr-URnI-Ryx3GOvml0wqGTgY5JGJ5UWOcHRXw8a_06a-kbmRSWXS42ymPLBahLWOSvGYhkRAmt85zMUNiARTHFzEYFoSID8n7n1QnbptORJWWn_yIPKm9n63VGTU2Ig",
        "originalText": "Add the Condition name and set the Condition type.  Event based performance conditions are typically used for liquidity events and pay out at either 0 or 100% of target. Non-market based and Market based performance conditions can have both variable (pay out at greater than or less than 100%) or non variable payouts. Market based performance conditions use metrics that are based on the company’s stock price, while Non-market based are typically operational or business goals that do not include the company’s stock price.  <br> The Vests post-termination toggle is used to indicate whether awards that have time vested will pay out upon performance achievement if the stakeholder terminates between time vest and performance achievement.  Selecting Yes will allow stakeholders that have met the time vesting criteria to keep the award if they term before the performance condition has been met. Selecting No will cause participants to forfeit the award if they have not met both the time vesting and performance condition upon termination.<br> <img height=\"482\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/472496775211988723_FUccAKcb2cr-URnI-Ryx3GOvml0wqGTgY5JGJ5UWOcHRXw8a_06a-kbmRSWXS42ymPLBahLWOSvGYhkRAmt85zMUNiARTHFzEYFoSID8n7n1QnbptORJWWn_yIPKm9n63VGTU2Ig\" width=\"387\">  ",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/472496775211988723_FUccAKcb2cr-URnI-Ryx3GOvml0wqGTgY5JGJ5UWOcHRXw8a_06a-kbmRSWXS42ymPLBahLWOSvGYhkRAmt85zMUNiARTHFzEYFoSID8n7n1QnbptORJWWn_yIPKm9n63VGTU2Ig"
        }
      }]
