  }, {
    "id": "1313944798771209354",
    "text": {
      "text": "Performance conditions can be attached to multiple vesting schedules; achievement is governed by managing the condition itself and flows back to all affected tranches for vesting.",
      "originalText": "Performance conditions can be attached to multiple vesting schedules; achievement is governed by managing the condition itself and flows back to all affected tranches for vesting."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "3282798968610784986",
    "text": {
      "text": "In theVesting schedules tab of theSecurities > Templates page, the performance condition(s) can be tied to a vesting schedule or individual vesting tranches by choosing the performance condition in the related field. Here is an example when creating a new vesting template: carta/public/11/images/2105014880909847365_QiAKl-mzEOwvqJPpfMeVwoVUMuFf0_9OfHaZMTT6V1Jz1J27UCmmt0R7J1MNRx_Pf77zivrWgQ53TBQlBU8b5GpS2DPbpk718TDvmgoXKv80S0ZSgC32sNFdrqYvgkVhT1VEk4w5",
      "originalText": "In the Vesting schedules tab of the Securities &gt; Templates page, the performance condition(s) can be tied to a vesting schedule or individual vesting tranches by choosing the performance condition in the related field. Here is an example when creating a new vesting template:<br><img height=\"351\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/2105014880909847365_QiAKl-mzEOwvqJPpfMeVwoVUMuFf0_9OfHaZMTT6V1Jz1J27UCmmt0R7J1MNRx_Pf77zivrWgQ53TBQlBU8b5GpS2DPbpk718TDvmgoXKv80S0ZSgC32sNFdrqYvgkVhT1VEk4w5\" width=\"484\">",
