        "url": "carta/public/11/images/2105014880909847365_QiAKl-mzEOwvqJPpfMeVwoVUMuFf0_9OfHaZMTT6V1Jz1J27UCmmt0R7J1MNRx_Pf77zivrWgQ53TBQlBU8b5GpS2DPbpk718TDvmgoXKv80S0ZSgC32sNFdrqYvgkVhT1VEk4w5"
      }
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-5837223723923682967",
    "text": {
      "text": "Associating grants with a performance vesting schedule will allow administrators to manage condition achievement by evaluating the condition itself. Performance tranches on the award will not pay out until the related performance criteria are achieved.",
