    "id": "-2615009871160259292",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "This can be done from the Performance conditions tab by clicking the V drop down and selecting Recognize for the desired vesting condition.  carta/public/11/images/497583031815316405_N_MfFxdzHXE1F1bQgKF-N6uJdeumE7VTtgZ2HC3xHpk4HnhyYBi0SxBtdzp34zdGHw3bGkM16XPF5l-5gJI8qWvUmdhTINRYG3eZrP3B9LA5ksX7v7xjY-0HyTIsEaY6AYbhJchr",
        "originalText": "This can be done from the Performance conditions tab by clicking the V drop down and selecting&nbsp;Recognize for the desired vesting condition.<br> <img height=\"150\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/497583031815316405_N_MfFxdzHXE1F1bQgKF-N6uJdeumE7VTtgZ2HC3xHpk4HnhyYBi0SxBtdzp34zdGHw3bGkM16XPF5l-5gJI8qWvUmdhTINRYG3eZrP3B9LA5ksX7v7xjY-0HyTIsEaY6AYbhJchr\" width=\"434\"><br> &nbsp;",
