        }
      }, {
        "text": "Set the Condition status to Achieved or Not Achieved, along with the Recognition date and Payout percentage (percentage of target vesting amount that pays out).  Depending on the setup for the performance condition, this may be above or below 100%.  carta/public/11/images/7532098008444190221_2myHOJ7mup8FiEf-Pr1SLe2R-qVboNEGf1CUXJGX7dJaPTyZdDxUdV029VgOFMcHDMma8WUr3VCqpXvLGFGrAjU_NK0pWLdtGuMTD35G7Tm_Eny0aBmTq2oqI-2asLu0to_v5ONA",
        "originalText": "Set the Condition status to Achieved or Not Achieved, along with the Recognition date and Payout percentage (percentage of target vesting amount that pays out).<br> Depending on the setup for the performance condition, this may be above or below 100%.<br> <img height=\"418\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7532098008444190221_2myHOJ7mup8FiEf-Pr1SLe2R-qVboNEGf1CUXJGX7dJaPTyZdDxUdV029VgOFMcHDMma8WUr3VCqpXvLGFGrAjU_NK0pWLdtGuMTD35G7Tm_Eny0aBmTq2oqI-2asLu0to_v5ONA\" width=\"435\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/7532098008444190221_2myHOJ7mup8FiEf-Pr1SLe2R-qVboNEGf1CUXJGX7dJaPTyZdDxUdV029VgOFMcHDMma8WUr3VCqpXvLGFGrAjU_NK0pWLdtGuMTD35G7Tm_Eny0aBmTq2oqI-2asLu0to_v5ONA"
