    "id": "45051620701828747",
    "text": {
      "text": "Performance conditions for performance awards can now be individually set per vesting tranche. Administrators can control the payout of performance conditions, including payouts greater than or less than 100% per vesting tranche.  When creating a custom vesting template, performance conditions can be set per vesting tranche. These performance conditions are controlled through the performance module and admins can set payout percentages upon condition achievement. These performance conditions will apply to every grant attached to the performance vesting schedule. carta/public/11/images/941611678804392722_F1AilfQqWLoP2XCZQXLEgZQEcjIcPYCip2otO_heCMvFtCLb_aNZ-jCrnSgu-9zaQIGc0wT3AdkKNvpC6lhMGS7mqSPbiEt6VzHDzi2HyVgLkezLPwoEQ5ifozZFH_tTATqRMi1G",
      "originalText": "Performance conditions for performance awards can now be individually set per vesting tranche. Administrators can control the payout of performance conditions, including payouts greater than or less than 100% per vesting tranche.<br><br>When creating a custom vesting template, performance conditions can be set per vesting tranche. These performance conditions are controlled through the performance module and admins can set payout percentages upon condition achievement.<br>These performance conditions will apply to every grant attached to the performance vesting schedule.<br><img height=\"312\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/941611678804392722_F1AilfQqWLoP2XCZQXLEgZQEcjIcPYCip2otO_heCMvFtCLb_aNZ-jCrnSgu-9zaQIGc0wT3AdkKNvpC6lhMGS7mqSPbiEt6VzHDzi2HyVgLkezLPwoEQ5ifozZFH_tTATqRMi1G\" width=\"474\">",
      "associatedImage": {
        "url": "carta/public/11/images/941611678804392722_F1AilfQqWLoP2XCZQXLEgZQEcjIcPYCip2otO_heCMvFtCLb_aNZ-jCrnSgu-9zaQIGc0wT3AdkKNvpC6lhMGS7mqSPbiEt6VzHDzi2HyVgLkezLPwoEQ5ifozZFH_tTATqRMi1G"
      }
    }
  }, {
    "id": "1458956382316987265",
    "text": {
      "text": "Performance awards can also be added on to milestone vesting templates. These act as a second performance trigger in addition to the milestone event. Milestone vesting schedules can be used with or without performance conditions. carta/public/11/images/7763568143050450819_l2vx6cJxNx5PZ2jjZKp5gea3KyyzDhg5VXu-ITlVMh7IomhTpfO5tvq2Xy5pC_ka4vbU-qmjM4sUKuPQq7JNEUOYOBxbqsuv0d24fURSPM6tc-M9kVCGv7CoLG7B7DXUXjsqs4rn",
      "originalText": "Performance awards can also be added on to milestone vesting templates. These act as a second performance trigger in addition to the milestone event. Milestone vesting schedules can be used with or without performance conditions.<br><img height=\"298\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7763568143050450819_l2vx6cJxNx5PZ2jjZKp5gea3KyyzDhg5VXu-ITlVMh7IomhTpfO5tvq2Xy5pC_ka4vbU-qmjM4sUKuPQq7JNEUOYOBxbqsuv0d24fURSPM6tc-M9kVCGv7CoLG7B7DXUXjsqs4rn\" width=\"484\">",
      "associatedImage": {
        "url": "carta/public/11/images/7763568143050450819_l2vx6cJxNx5PZ2jjZKp5gea3KyyzDhg5VXu-ITlVMh7IomhTpfO5tvq2Xy5pC_ka4vbU-qmjM4sUKuPQq7JNEUOYOBxbqsuv0d24fURSPM6tc-M9kVCGv7CoLG7B7DXUXjsqs4rn"
      }
    }
  }, {
    "id": "4089820876467530942",
    "text": {
      "text": "Achievement of a performance condition will flow back to all grants tied to vesting tranches set up with that condition. carta/public/11/images/9211498077207908238_jq62i_9n-JwdSaLMgmK9UfRXtWa2jFqMnOd9-YbOXIu6VnLTa397UUHuN6AFWvjBJ2n9jFhFOui30_HscUH8NCc3bTqQsqjuwx7GMc1k7cooopcLF8EG9PP5EbcPTx5yef2CXaMa",
      "originalText": "Achievement of a performance condition will flow back to all grants tied to vesting tranches set up with that condition.<br><img height=\"402\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/9211498077207908238_jq62i_9n-JwdSaLMgmK9UfRXtWa2jFqMnOd9-YbOXIu6VnLTa397UUHuN6AFWvjBJ2n9jFhFOui30_HscUH8NCc3bTqQsqjuwx7GMc1k7cooopcLF8EG9PP5EbcPTx5yef2CXaMa\" width=\"437\">",
