        "originalText": "Select the notification type.<br> <img height=\"297\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3211617445539282562_aIRK3HqkYF5sXwiTeHbWqwMuCCd814S2sb0iSgEh_gzCjlRF5FXSCDDdG1n0CkeC5y9-dnMGXOi_ZunScr_eGmiq7YMTYXMFAZHTXwPYJJH4eM0nrzzC-KJnGs9mSunCPieYQ0gY\" style=\"margin-left: -7.306569343065632px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"445.7007299270073\">  Send with daily digest: This option will send the notification as part of a daily email such as the one below, separated by firm. Any message you include will be shown below the shared document.<br> <img height=\"426\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3879077264238847416_h1sa1ci1H1T_L4sJNCqa_P8NRV5gOMG2uK9LLRqXacBGfmCZe_qvhDHIFFvHqAs-V8iIKF7WkXnCrwC3RfAEpMLxBBvvoz7bg7BxvRFYx-c90mWLMqn_68o5EIcv-koikSwmS4S1\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"289\"> Send immediately: This option will send the notification(s) immediately. The subject and message can be customized.<br> <img height=\"427\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/376707768472045581_yh91Kk3nw4zgu_jnKR_V80kSSVh8oQpeyiuNGCL4QWeetT0WujclS3p1zRa8XgOhDKF3n2FyUF0sueAc4z8jW1X_T961YkWbeNaHA599L6S3gO7Enem5yNud6npL8jgMMLe0Vl4z\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"290\">  ",
        "associatedImage": {
