diately validated and errors are shown from the spreadsheet, highlighting the row number, or from theErrors tab on the right side slider. carta/public/11/images/7971605633234640448_IAFu95JkDguvueHzKqAeCzq8v6Be0SzLdz_QX8m-su4nZqg7oeNKKYDJN_5_rUod8Z7XODoXBMsy0L7ANCwoU7D8lt8tmg8Ewo8QOKtlbXBOPu6rQ0xWMcGjHgwbJ2UuJbaU6k9cFor more customization of fields (e.g.Vesting Schedule, Documents, Acceleration terms, etc.), select the “Custom …” option from the cell’s dropdown to add the custom values from the right side slider. carta/public/11/images/1442040913101587292_A5I4BbTeKbC0PXZwHrGq8aOKyUOn6Er1GTtB24gAv_RNFfrQUSlLUWmk2EWaorduahCk3EI5DFVPlbd72Rv5zHCSkV1pEbMJas93P2Yo4ag-ZWUg5EBZw3Z8oAac9QFdi5G4t-Ea carta/public/11/images/1719227105865560494_iDdW2niPMYJvSIQjM0kroVgnSROStiFIZ2ru7TSJXT95JRd6Fb_5EWSp_XYumryd0dQbw_hWRHxX4uU72s2f5HSrctn7WGogML17ZVKvQvg1RDk8f-eycIR78z3dz4wYK0uQytPP",
        "originalText": "This new drafting workflow allows every Admin to easily edit and add draft issuances individually or in bulk. There are a few new elements.<br> <img height=\"221\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6768796604645982567_GsmUJmgiudIRGU4n4YsNZjBFNCycibZiZLOIUkF6r9R0DrO1Y5DSGkAohAY0ltjEJr7Woj1bbIim_7ArEQQeb7RItOCHZhzOOs6fR3Uj_8_nyOrwFO078e9oQ8IxkisDTbC9eaxk\" width=\"439\">  The magnifying glass on the left side allows the Admin to search the drafts.<br> <img height=\"104\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/2269268853548632448_tPxXg3n5BecP7QmdVK7vQjcQm0OcJzswhiVMTINzWLNHlEJUfP5FXEgzTLIcGMrd1KF9xeB7REGCW5m81Gmh5y4P27tGKtu-M8vRyip85JyHclQSka5N9B83QviBN8gKYc7C-OYV\" width=\"82\"><br> &nbsp; Click Import on the left side to import draft information from an external spreadsheet to review on Carta before issuing.<br> <img height=\"122\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/927249142575395866_QnvsuSoF0eZbl5iYUr1a7xdt9LS7yoefVMEvxj7wlRIIRQc6htuqDV1pak8oqLYCPCGJOv2IRWafMdMthUt8R5q07T2nI49PAgfK2ve3215By8ryrTI0jkGrjBg42yQgpVVFOMQD\" width=\"219\"><br> &nbsp; On the upper right corner, a New drafted total is shown and that total is reduced from the Remaining available for issuance under the Plan to assist in reviewing Plan changes.<br> <img height=\"108\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3243759155075492786_k32IYmpRjKUIdjwxi3fNe8MRV7vJjdikjAFEzqNtFg7JhTfbtNeziZuY1DDTgFsuIdQvz9qFm8xrC3sAfoPh57j9mS2oSyFcL4mUblbBpNbmzSHy0VK5JMwusmJ65kpjku8WXvhy\" width=\"397\"><br> &nbsp; As another form of review, you can click this icon to export a Cap Table Report with Drafts.<br> <img height=\"119\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1795640899761828200_gSWHmH3MsCs6nK1n7XeAXm1U3I-4Wrzm3aqCjQsdO7C2mnZv7f9MRGisPAjOh3RJ166epr097whAQQso3CsllqHrtRp-cK7JA84G108LiKPzFf0o5wHuPPjpa5zwNk1J5GhWWSqX\" width=\"215\"><br> &nbsp; After data is entered, there are a few similarities to Excel spreadsheet that will make edits easier.  Data from cells can be copy and pasted into another cell Click and drag the bottom right corner to copy the text Select a column or row and press the Del key on your keyboard to clear the data  <img height=\"246\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/849830423502650018_7RgB7xV1nlRpZUl-4c4fGBP7Yv_dV30cH4QKuENwlQz0OertrNOxkFNmfHIPdkBxeeNDSXRbK4CX0a7WXFZ7IDyBbjlpBjYtjagHjtj9WitKAxp_JbI3uW8Alq9EKMGtbqTkYMmD\" width=\"138\"><br> &nbsp; Inputs are immediately validated and errors are shown from the spreadsheet, highlighting the row number, or from the Errors tab on the right side slider.<br> <img height=\"78\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7971605633234640448_IAFu95JkDguvueHzKqAeCzq8v6Be0SzLdz_QX8m-su4nZqg7oeNKKYDJN_5_rUod8Z7XODoXBMsy0L7ANCwoU7D8lt8tmg8Ewo8QOKtlbXBOPu6rQ0xWMcGjHgwbJ2UuJbaU6k9c\" width=\"385\"><br> &nbsp; For more customization of fields (e.g. Vesting Schedule, Documents, Acceleration terms, etc.), select the “Custom …” option from the cell’s dropdown to add the custom values from the right side slider.<br> <img height=\"290\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1442040913101587292_A5I4BbTeKbC0PXZwHrGq8aOKyUOn6Er1GTtB24gAv_RNFfrQUSlLUWmk2EWaorduahCk3EI5DFVPlbd72Rv5zHCSkV1pEbMJas93P2Yo4ag-ZWUg5EBZw3Z8oAac9QFdi5G4t-Ea\" width=\"369\"><br> <img height=\"273\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1719227105865560494_iDdW2niPMYJvSIQjM0kroVgnSROStiFIZ2ru7TSJXT95JRd6Fb_5EWSp_XYumryd0dQbw_hWRHxX4uU72s2f5HSrctn7WGogML17ZVKvQvg1RDk8f-eycIR78z3dz4wYK0uQytPP\" width=\"372\"><br> &nbsp;  ",
