        }
      }, {
        "text": "Review the Plan changes and any data warnings. If needed, click Back to spreadsheet in the upper left to make any edits.  carta/public/11/images/1648484476955656594_yT-VSShopV4jTYxhxfxtuzScNRs1IkMdu0tvo-CMSNLDgAzl1BhHk6qz8fk_tAOUuSVVD-W3ZnVdYVuQj10qojZsU1nJ8PdL3JC_mhK_PwKWL2XEokQc_WGcEUs8CT6lXfWZQbrAIf needed, clickCheck Rule 701 to review 701 compliance. carta/public/11/images/6867424062450983012_Vodx5WK6E4CBn8fBuYKgXQg2QgUWZnEaRCdTpcuTKTq-_z040UMnZMC07fYZWlYCEIYiDY0Q4fEWTUGP8TUvGEfNIg1LsQE1F_NBLP-2U5X_ORXEaWSva3fVY4n1gAmDXxOJpMLX",
        "originalText": "Review the Plan changes and any data warnings. If needed, click Back to spreadsheet in the upper left to make any edits.<br> <img height=\"415\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1648484476955656594_yT-VSShopV4jTYxhxfxtuzScNRs1IkMdu0tvo-CMSNLDgAzl1BhHk6qz8fk_tAOUuSVVD-W3ZnVdYVuQj10qojZsU1nJ8PdL3JC_mhK_PwKWL2XEokQc_WGcEUs8CT6lXfWZQbrA\" width=\"432\">  If needed, click Check Rule 701 to review <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/rule-701\" target=\"_blank\">701 compliance</a>.<br> <img height=\"245\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6867424062450983012_Vodx5WK6E4CBn8fBuYKgXQg2QgUWZnEaRCdTpcuTKTq-_z040UMnZMC07fYZWlYCEIYiDY0Q4fEWTUGP8TUvGEfNIg1LsQE1F_NBLP-2U5X_ORXEaWSva3fVY4n1gAmDXxOJpMLX\" width=\"383\"><br> &nbsp;  ",
