        }
      }, {
        "text": "To issue the drafts to the company cap table, click Release RSUs in the upper right corner.  carta/public/11/images/8651818201786084887_bXZ7cBZIgd0_U1yEd8Ti5gxPhY4xIMG3ED3thNksyhvPTmt7ySH02d00YHW-yJhtxO_Qy5augHlnxC0PLMaigy4zaBbXijqda7XrnPbZ7xyrXa_VkdQXor5miFeSkTFDjNJo-lQp",
        "originalText": "To issue the drafts to the company cap table, click Release RSUs in the upper right corner.<br> <img height=\"51\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8651818201786084887_bXZ7cBZIgd0_U1yEd8Ti5gxPhY4xIMG3ED3thNksyhvPTmt7ySH02d00YHW-yJhtxO_Qy5augHlnxC0PLMaigy4zaBbXijqda7XrnPbZ7xyrXa_VkdQXor5miFeSkTFDjNJo-lQp\" width=\"124\"><br> &nbsp;",
