{
  "id": "-344724795639007578",
  "subject": {
    "id": "-344724795639007578",
    "text": {
      "text": "Investor Updates"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-2969329534004985471",
    "text": {
      "text": "WithInvestor Updates, Carta companies can keep all stakeholders on their cap table (investors, board members, employees, and advisors) up to date on Carta. This gives companies the tools to compose a mixed media update and attach all relevant files. The financials templates are great for companies who are looking for guidance on what is important to investors. Companies sending update can also keep track of who has viewed updates.  Users withLegal Administrator orCompany Editor permissions will be able to send outInvestor Updates.",
      "originalText": "With Investor Updates, Carta companies can keep all stakeholders on their cap table (investors, board members, employees, and advisors) up to date on Carta. This gives companies the tools to compose a mixed media update and attach all relevant files. The financials templates are great for companies who are looking for guidance on what is important to investors. Companies sending update can also keep track of who has viewed updates.<br><br>Users with&nbsp;Legal Administrator&nbsp;or&nbsp;Company Editor&nbsp;permissions will be able to send out&nbsp;Investor Updates."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-250461671808891593",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "Navigate to Stakeholders > Investor Updates.  carta/public/11/images/4234550305023519441_rtaImage    This will take you to a page with all of your previously sent updates, where you can track views.  carta/public/11/images/4438667093057284615_rtaImage    carta/public/11/images/8467762320726561749_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Navigate to Stakeholders &gt; Investor Updates.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/4234550305023519441_rtaImage\"><br> <br> This will take you to a page with all of your previously sent updates, where you can track views.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/4438667093057284615_rtaImage\"><br> <br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8467762320726561749_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/8467762320726561749_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click Compose new update. You can title your update, specify reporting cadence, a reporting period, and an as of date to help set the context for the update to your recipients. Click Save.  carta/public/11/images/8379065017346365725_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Click Compose new update. You can title your update, specify reporting cadence, a reporting period, and an as of date to help set the context for the update to your recipients. Click Save.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8379065017346365725_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/8379065017346365725_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "In the update draft page, select recipients, compose a text update, and attach files.  carta/public/11/images/5520902107372642995_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "In the update draft page, select recipients, compose a text update, and attach files.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5520902107372642995_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/5520902107372642995_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "When selecting recipients, you can pick from the stakeholders on your captable - employees, advisors, etc. Use filters to speed up the selection process, including selecting the set of stakeholders your previous update was sent to.  carta/public/11/images/322814425816431557_rtaImage    carta/public/11/images/7589448037300024778_rtaImage    When composing the message, the text editor allows you to incorporate text, images, and videos.  carta/public/11/images/4960168283483112415_rtaImage    Our file uploader supports most file types. When reporting financials and KPIs to your investor, we have a set of templates that you may find useful:  carta/public/11/images/703677774232102863_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "When selecting recipients, you can pick from the stakeholders on your captable - employees, advisors, etc. Use filters to speed up the selection process, including selecting the set of stakeholders your previous update was sent to.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/322814425816431557_rtaImage\"><br> <br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7589448037300024778_rtaImage\"><br> <br> When composing the message, the text editor allows you to incorporate text, images, and videos.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/4960168283483112415_rtaImage\"><br> <br> Our file uploader supports most file types. When reporting financials and KPIs to your investor, we have a set of templates that you may find useful:<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/703677774232102863_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/703677774232102863_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "When you are ready to send out the update, click Review and send.  carta/public/11/images/7843096860315451216_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "When you are ready to send out the update, click Review and send.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7843096860315451216_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/7843096860315451216_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Review the details of the update, then click Send the update.  carta/public/11/images/7745461538652352462_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Review the details of the update, then click&nbsp;Send the update.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7745461538652352462_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/7745461538652352462_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "The recipients will receive an email notice that the company has send a new update, where they can log into their Carta account to view.  carta/public/11/images/5807328134460414723_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "The recipients will receive an email notice that the company has send a new update, where they can log into their Carta account to view.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5807328134460414723_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/5807328134460414723_rtaImage"
        }
      }]
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-7267428298223726358",
    "text": {
      "text": "We hope you find this feature useful. If you have any feedback, submit a case via Carta's Help Center. Learn more about Carta's Help Center.",
      "originalText": "We hope you find this feature useful. If you have any feedback, submit a case via <a href=\"https://app.carta.com/profiles/update?help=true\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Carta's Help Center</u></a>. <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/carta-help-center\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more about Carta's Help Center</a>."
    }
  }]
}

{
  "id": "6042107118236525629",
  "subject": {
    "id": "6042107118236525629",
    "text": {
      "text": "Tracking, adding, and updating authorized shares"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "7324473677677332625",
    "text": {
      "text": "After creating a share class, users with Legal Administrator permissions will need to set each share class’ authorized shares before issuing securities. For LLCs, setting authorized shares is not required. Once the authorized shares are set, then shares can be issued.  A share class’ authorized shares should be updated after every financing round to follow the updated incorporation document, even if the total authorized amount is unchanged.",
      "originalText": "After <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/create-a-share-class\" target=\"_blank\">creating a share class</a>, users with Legal Administrator permissions will need to set each share class’ authorized shares before issuing securities. For LLCs, setting authorized shares is not required. Once the authorized shares are set, then <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/workflow-securities\" target=\"_blank\">shares can be issued</a>.<br><br>A share class’ authorized shares should be updated after every financing round to follow the updated incorporation document, even if the total authorized amount is unchanged."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-6723854846455410341",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "Navigate to Securities > Shares.  carta/public/11/images/4002956933201812947_X3P_fI5qYX6ywnoMOVUP99J1VTb46OfDuFL3fGEt5seTSiJgLHeE-3_KLu8jggiEDYShXNky5Lo8xIXRlLTQcPZCmA8MhHJ0Qo2U78fFGzS8DO_h9u9GzgIAcqJO_ANop1vz0rFe",
        "originalText": "Navigate to Securities &gt; Shares.<br> <img height=\"151\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/4002956933201812947_X3P_fI5qYX6ywnoMOVUP99J1VTb46OfDuFL3fGEt5seTSiJgLHeE-3_KLu8jggiEDYShXNky5Lo8xIXRlLTQcPZCmA8MhHJ0Qo2U78fFGzS8DO_h9u9GzgIAcqJO_ANop1vz0rFe\" width=\"428\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/4002956933201812947_X3P_fI5qYX6ywnoMOVUP99J1VTb46OfDuFL3fGEt5seTSiJgLHeE-3_KLu8jggiEDYShXNky5Lo8xIXRlLTQcPZCmA8MhHJ0Qo2U78fFGzS8DO_h9u9GzgIAcqJO_ANop1vz0rFe"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click Manage share classes and select Manage authorized.  carta/public/11/images/3183236525264232564_p-PGRRWDbOvjoITbAVb6T_jhrY3qaX9zGi-eLS3hzHD8bq8WN-jz4UnGut7VanWG_bQOYP-cu8jx9Q4sA3SQMe-u1PutMSdgU-0p95qdN4JU-xZrYfOnvNhhgWwCNPLqZKZlfrsf",
        "originalText": "Click&nbsp;Manage share classes and select Manage authorized.<br> <img height=\"256\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3183236525264232564_p-PGRRWDbOvjoITbAVb6T_jhrY3qaX9zGi-eLS3hzHD8bq8WN-jz4UnGut7VanWG_bQOYP-cu8jx9Q4sA3SQMe-u1PutMSdgU-0p95qdN4JU-xZrYfOnvNhhgWwCNPLqZKZlfrsf\" width=\"309\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/3183236525264232564_p-PGRRWDbOvjoITbAVb6T_jhrY3qaX9zGi-eLS3hzHD8bq8WN-jz4UnGut7VanWG_bQOYP-cu8jx9Q4sA3SQMe-u1PutMSdgU-0p95qdN4JU-xZrYfOnvNhhgWwCNPLqZKZlfrsf"
        }
