        "text": "Click on the + to the right of the latest entry, which will duplicate that row.  carta/public/11/images/2245392513279178085_pK0juKlC3lTrGgIm5f1aYPN4G1AiRjdrpTcya1r9YLR-bgC7XW8Dv8xrbJ-Ji7dXmTWXoli5MiJFNNvA-BsXsw01fSSVn2NEVx5tMgfCp1eAoR29-Rz_QY-U_sbX5ZD01nigY4aO",
