    "id": "2997607674024138491",
    "text": {
      "text": "Where can I find my 83(b) election form for PIUs on Carta?",
      "originalText": "Where can I find my 83(b) election form for PIUs on Carta?"
    },
    "signals": [{
      "valueL": "2"
    }]
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "2432211667742028814",
    "text": {
      "text": "Carta now has a feature for recipients of PIUs where an 83(b) election is pre populated and can be downloaded and then stored in Carta. This feature is being enabled on a company by company basis. If you have been issued a PIU and are not seeing the 83(b) form by following the instructions below, it means that the issuer of your PIU hasn’t turned this feature on. Contact the issuing company to have them request this feature to be enabled.",
      "originalText": "Carta now has a feature for recipients of PIUs where an 83(b) election is pre populated and can be downloaded and then stored in Carta. This feature is being enabled on a company by company basis. If you have been issued a PIU and are not seeing the 83(b) form by following the instructions below, it means that the issuer of your PIU hasn’t turned this feature on. <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/contacting-the-issuer\" target=\"_blank\">Contact the issuing company</a> to have them request this feature to be enabled."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-2097000359623861119",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "After being issued a PIU, the 83(b) election can be found on the 83(b) elections tab of the PIU details. Click on the file link from the Generated 83(b) form section to download a pre-populated 83(b).  carta/public/11/images/3054845074260334689_hfQWpQbukBmjLwKeYn_KQcIY80AEn8ZaXkW2_9BUR9Zq9s6pczwLsAklUwytAwkuKJNmuSbF-08FKdnbtQyXsVQiBbq3prMqJuw7E0bq3yqzCMO6GOxLsUPg8wD7RejH07sySnza",
        "originalText": "After being issued a PIU, the 83(b) election can be found on the 83(b) elections tab of the PIU details. Click on the file link from the Generated 83(b) form section to download a pre-populated 83(b).<br> <img height=\"270\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3054845074260334689_hfQWpQbukBmjLwKeYn_KQcIY80AEn8ZaXkW2_9BUR9Zq9s6pczwLsAklUwytAwkuKJNmuSbF-08FKdnbtQyXsVQiBbq3prMqJuw7E0bq3yqzCMO6GOxLsUPg8wD7RejH07sySnza\" width=\"430\"><br> &nbsp;",
