        }
      }, {
        "text": "Follow the instructions provided in the PDF to complete and sign the form.",
        "originalText": "Follow the instructions provided in the PDF to complete and sign the form.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Upload the signed form to the Signed copy of the form section of the table.",
        "originalText": "Upload the signed form to the Signed copy of the form section of the table.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Enter the date the form was mailed to the IRS.",
        "originalText": "Enter the date the form was mailed to the IRS.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Click Update this 83(b) election to save the date and executed form and share access to the issuing company.  carta/public/11/images/5960088292667281703_IiNC1-BeQFkr_HBcxwepX9AH6Q-238P4QDxQJF0Vt2Y-VJMSUlSk4QZCLwxAmPBGknH36j37RI8Pd22ud2c715wpdkG9pM8PkOw5OHvBXRbVMkyO2UYD_85N7UcKINvcAbbS5T3p    Alternatively, if an 83(b) election for this issuance will not be made, the issuing company can be made aware by checking the I do not wish to make an 83(b) election... box.  carta/public/11/images/4096671282044582853_yu11jP66tmNekX7CK115LYHK7ctHdHy4i_Vz5fTkp8nOZz16rJfJGPYadUMRreFUqWd-vwKmwtUyFnz873AmFKOi6LD1liBmMJKKXPeD9VJvm_rc60rSArBNPchhy4j1TW97wX-H",
        "originalText": "Click Update this 83(b) election to save the date and executed form and share access to the issuing company.<br> <img height=\"287\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5960088292667281703_IiNC1-BeQFkr_HBcxwepX9AH6Q-238P4QDxQJF0Vt2Y-VJMSUlSk4QZCLwxAmPBGknH36j37RI8Pd22ud2c715wpdkG9pM8PkOw5OHvBXRbVMkyO2UYD_85N7UcKINvcAbbS5T3p\" width=\"431\"><br> <br> Alternatively, if an 83(b) election for this issuance will not be made, the issuing company can be made aware by checking the I do not wish to make an 83(b) election... box.<br> <img height=\"269\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/4096671282044582853_yu11jP66tmNekX7CK115LYHK7ctHdHy4i_Vz5fTkp8nOZz16rJfJGPYadUMRreFUqWd-vwKmwtUyFnz873AmFKOi6LD1liBmMJKKXPeD9VJvm_rc60rSArBNPchhy4j1TW97wX-H\" width=\"427\">",
