{
  "id": "666004863881127263",
  "subject": {
    "id": "666004863881127263",
    "text": {
      "text": "Setting Cap Table Access for Stakeholders"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-3254203785889808984",
    "text": {
      "text": "Companies can share their cap tables with their investors securely through Carta. Employees and other stakeholders can also gain better insight into their holdings. This page displays stakeholders who have accepted securities for your company and information about when they invested and their ownership percentage in your company.",
      "originalText": "Companies can share their cap tables with their investors securely through Carta. Employees and other stakeholders can also gain better insight into their holdings. This page displays stakeholders who have accepted securities for your company and information about when they invested and their ownership percentage in your company."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "5486514852117347924",
    "text": {
      "text": "Holders can request cap table access during the acceptance of a preferred certificate or from an Investment Fund.",
      "originalText": "Holders can request cap table access during the <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/accepting-a-certificate\" target=\"_blank\">acceptance of a preferred certificate</a> or <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/investor-cap-table\" target=\"_blank\">from an Investment Fund</a>."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "3740997632408768233",
    "text": {
      "text": "Users withCompany Editor orLegal Administrator on the company’s Permissions and Roles page can view theCap table access page and set or modify the access.",
      "originalText": "Users with Company Editor or Legal Administrator on the company’s <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/corporate-permissions\" target=\"_blank\">Permissions and Roles</a> page can view the Cap table access page and set or modify the access."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "7387497101580398677",
    "text": {
      "text": "There are five different cap table views that can be granted: No access, Individual view, Summary view, Intermediate view, andDetailed view. Learn more about the levels of cap table access.",
      "originalText": "There are five different cap table views that can be granted: No access, Individual view, Summary view, Intermediate view, and Detailed view. <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/levels-of-cap-table-access\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more about the levels of cap table access</a>."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-5512275554897399633",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
