        }
      }, {
        "text": "Type your signature in the popup and click Accept Certificate.  carta/public/11/images/892258647251582295_uHf0YtPNGkGz6fIgc_8nt_mqK4YCwGgjuWE6lqSea5PgLkexpcy-hbySPavKJwcqgJPXEt8kJ6Z_65Lsbd5cAYoaQVjjHSqRenSfDwPxlwDvM7oLkF7jpTK-EF6o1Jnku8kliF54    When accepting Preferred shares, cap table access can be requested and the company admin can grant one of the five access levels. If this option is not available, then you may already have cap table access.  To request, check off the box, then click Accept certificate.  carta/public/11/images/4477764346727675301_JVQLYGYVS1-yAV2VVg_ULzl7SVathwc9d_AXfejrRRjsGXrtvYGt3hPwTx-eFYwNqKvE1enYb1mB1j8wVq7FwbeJVuNo8cxiFqfvHJyhKDhFVukObKQEfGvDk6vKdMW9iqQeEFVo",
        "originalText": "Type your signature in the popup and click Accept Certificate.<br> <img height=\"331\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/892258647251582295_uHf0YtPNGkGz6fIgc_8nt_mqK4YCwGgjuWE6lqSea5PgLkexpcy-hbySPavKJwcqgJPXEt8kJ6Z_65Lsbd5cAYoaQVjjHSqRenSfDwPxlwDvM7oLkF7jpTK-EF6o1Jnku8kliF54\" width=\"428\"><br> <br> When accepting Preferred shares, cap table access can be requested and the company admin can grant one of the <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/levels-of-cap-table-access\" target=\"_blank\">five access levels</a>. If this option is not available, then you may already have cap table access.<br> To request, check off the box, then click Accept certificate.<br> <img height=\"403\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/4477764346727675301_JVQLYGYVS1-yAV2VVg_ULzl7SVathwc9d_AXfejrRRjsGXrtvYGt3hPwTx-eFYwNqKvE1enYb1mB1j8wVq7FwbeJVuNo8cxiFqfvHJyhKDhFVukObKQEfGvDk6vKdMW9iqQeEFVo\" width=\"427\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/4477764346727675301_JVQLYGYVS1-yAV2VVg_ULzl7SVathwc9d_AXfejrRRjsGXrtvYGt3hPwTx-eFYwNqKvE1enYb1mB1j8wVq7FwbeJVuNo8cxiFqfvHJyhKDhFVukObKQEfGvDk6vKdMW9iqQeEFVo"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Congratulations. You have accepted your security.  carta/public/11/images/1743783426141062025_qnG5DQ6ktpk9nULOTsLu-qGIWDUqli8-nTuYBwCla8YgshEipYlMiIfnZ39Z8taD_hQBXVtocojZdckveTQGZJJl5C2ELwPseDdlEyzg2ybW8__hOBkgFjKBgHCrqhNk4InJdBc-",
        "originalText": "Congratulations. You have accepted your security.<br> <img height=\"149\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1743783426141062025_qnG5DQ6ktpk9nULOTsLu-qGIWDUqli8-nTuYBwCla8YgshEipYlMiIfnZ39Z8taD_hQBXVtocojZdckveTQGZJJl5C2ELwPseDdlEyzg2ybW8__hOBkgFjKBgHCrqhNk4InJdBc-\" style=\"margin-left: -0.315289648622989px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"332.63057929724596\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
