{
  "id": "-7454949091482720781",
  "subject": {
    "id": "-7454949091482720781",
    "text": {
      "text": "Request Cap Table Access - Investment Fund"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "645219781375631730",
    "text": {
      "text": "Investors on Carta can request access to company cap tables when they accept securities. On Carta, company cap tables are updated upon any securities transaction, so that the cap tables are always current and accurate.",
      "originalText": "Investors on Carta can request access to company cap tables when they accept securities. On Carta, company cap tables are updated upon any securities transaction, so that the cap tables are always current and accurate."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-7291140854363363826",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "From the left side panel, navigate to Cap table access.  carta/public/11/images/1889065731724935230_vWnVzD04amlfMyFkQjPHWlpjJXq68pN7vdPRPXQjdctqrHHazYvHe2aHlH-G6zkm0g9T8c2F2daLb7cUU1RwL1ePC-1yKzoF_Cli_-YZcvAlbAbbIKdhPG27QEuVAaFeFjqnjeBE",
        "originalText": "From the left side panel, navigate to Cap table access.<br> <img height=\"273\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1889065731724935230_vWnVzD04amlfMyFkQjPHWlpjJXq68pN7vdPRPXQjdctqrHHazYvHe2aHlH-G6zkm0g9T8c2F2daLb7cUU1RwL1ePC-1yKzoF_Cli_-YZcvAlbAbbIKdhPG27QEuVAaFeFjqnjeBE\" width=\"533\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/1889065731724935230_vWnVzD04amlfMyFkQjPHWlpjJXq68pN7vdPRPXQjdctqrHHazYvHe2aHlH-G6zkm0g9T8c2F2daLb7cUU1RwL1ePC-1yKzoF_Cli_-YZcvAlbAbbIKdhPG27QEuVAaFeFjqnjeBE"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Check off the company that you would like to request cap table access.  carta/public/11/images/6406977010024839307_irjOQlpgT75xFtbzCAhGS_Sgvr5Xvq_E4w3cmWzaHIOXXL3h5WSiyO5XyPVFMVWOFOIpM9sXBw3_sLK3x4DupakPUSu3S5PvOOHm0JYQoOn8FluHZ-u3f3y2eoAyOCAzDx_pOxR7",
        "originalText": "Check off the company that you would like to request cap table access.<br> <img height=\"237\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6406977010024839307_irjOQlpgT75xFtbzCAhGS_Sgvr5Xvq_E4w3cmWzaHIOXXL3h5WSiyO5XyPVFMVWOFOIpM9sXBw3_sLK3x4DupakPUSu3S5PvOOHm0JYQoOn8FluHZ-u3f3y2eoAyOCAzDx_pOxR7\" width=\"533\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/6406977010024839307_irjOQlpgT75xFtbzCAhGS_Sgvr5Xvq_E4w3cmWzaHIOXXL3h5WSiyO5XyPVFMVWOFOIpM9sXBw3_sLK3x4DupakPUSu3S5PvOOHm0JYQoOn8FluHZ-u3f3y2eoAyOCAzDx_pOxR7"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click Actions > Request cap table access.  carta/public/11/images/1463365729282155773_q6Yam-i74jnuwIQsXkv2HtkBFYntPHw4KxvL2XCUyp2Ja5Uw00PBpQg3yLxdOdPHp3cMh56DYfXtCHpBeDAPcgd3kYKWNIyGe-kIa8I_DhKKcJZgPMUaUq7eAYyLBx-omcveKv7V",
        "originalText": "Click Actions &gt; Request cap table access.<br> <img height=\"245\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1463365729282155773_q6Yam-i74jnuwIQsXkv2HtkBFYntPHw4KxvL2XCUyp2Ja5Uw00PBpQg3yLxdOdPHp3cMh56DYfXtCHpBeDAPcgd3kYKWNIyGe-kIa8I_DhKKcJZgPMUaUq7eAYyLBx-omcveKv7V\" width=\"538\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/1463365729282155773_q6Yam-i74jnuwIQsXkv2HtkBFYntPHw4KxvL2XCUyp2Ja5Uw00PBpQg3yLxdOdPHp3cMh56DYfXtCHpBeDAPcgd3kYKWNIyGe-kIa8I_DhKKcJZgPMUaUq7eAYyLBx-omcveKv7V"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "The cap table request will go to the individual(s) that the company has selected to handle investor access requests. The company can choose from several different levels of access to provide.",
        "originalText": "The cap table request will go to the individual(s) that the company has selected to handle investor access requests. The company can choose from <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/levels-of-cap-table-access\" target=\"_blank\">several different levels</a> of access to provide."
      }, {
        "text": "Once access has been granted, you will have access to the company's real-time cap table as of any date in the company's history, such as a quarter-end or year-end for reporting purposes. In addition, if you have detailed access, you can utilize our round modeling and waterfall analyses based on the company's cap table data.",
        "originalText": "Once access has been granted, you will have access to the company's real-time cap table as of any date in the company's history, such as a quarter-end or year-end for reporting purposes. In addition, if you have detailed access, you can utilize our round modeling and waterfall analyses based on the company's cap table data."
      }]
    }
