        "text": "Click Save to proceed.",
        "originalText": "Click Save to proceed.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "After entering the event, the current FMV will be marked as not under safe harbor in the 409A dashboard.  carta/public/11/images/6938570984905150546_TK0KQmKxpWNU1PEe4rmTBaSLtsK7MkYnC8h0v0mxsdQj4nk_ltOMTQVEMy2AVPWWPsapztvjHqBCVvuuTW6nCDtVFS_9Lxi_BqXxDd8TQF3ynghP9uzUpn3jw2xWix9DsvH9awKX",
