      "text": "Option holders will see a notice when exercising their options notifying them that the company is undergoing a new valuation, and that their taxes might change post valuation. carta/public/11/images/8010971809831328509_qVZwLJkRxeGnmOtR4snIH7aSQsSe6HcFiLXYjPLniV0YVEHlW6hEcK4HhifKss5BmxQYI4SSxafWryrLXqeOWHEcmcQoYxmBnuQyNJ6S4np2pdkaF-P-bu03kIXt0ftejQ_4Sn1J",
