    "id": "-5117390601184430232",
    "text": {
      "text": "Capital accounts & Fund transactions",
      "originalText": "Capital accounts &amp; Fund transactions"
    },
    "signals": [{
      "key": "FontBolded",
      "valueB": true
    }, {
      "valueL": "2"
    }]
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-9214013626990868853",
    "text": {
      "text": "By sharing Capital account for a particular fund, your investors will be able to view their capital account transaction data. For the Capital accounts view, your investors can only see their own capital account statement information including all transactions provided by the fund. The datepicker can be set by the investor to anytime between the date of their first capital account transactions with the fund and the share-through date. For the Fund transaction page, the investor can view a list of all their raw capital account transactions before the share-through date. The Capital accounts & Fund transactions function the same for both Carta fund administration and non-fund administration users of the information sharing feature. carta/public/11/images/6458146826643517552_RZpachWajrZ3Sa1ftO-Ds4n_ctMM4k3cVTK-quEEV358bE--tL2wD3WYzAd1fUfgDFZ12oraokNoLeMt4SNx4W-HUXHVsqfiggt9Isn2osrIo8xKGLP-LASav7UH4_ztU9zN2N9u carta/public/11/images/8777321202752601675_7UJIiJkVrlfCleryqoAyJJx29TwU_Lg4eX38nhqNuZu1cUsh5TH-TjVpadr3QDD3U3RapS6z8DpkC3CqeDQdkiInrhLEwak_z6AEOzwA8nF0anqlpflVs3M3gVq_uQzLFMzWYWMb carta/public/11/images/2136191569796323820_thCinfgP0r_hSwhUmi1B_acHMAJBZhGx3c1L-cYj8M5cLEe6in6eHjwHF84eZC_3E34EtLmS2LLb4dmuCSU6yTavTkXkQILJfibNn3v7EnyrKrhufIXuM-7X8jvQZlD5pnBnGar3",
      "originalText": "By sharing Capital account for a particular fund, your investors will be able to view their capital account transaction data. For the Capital accounts view, your investors can only see their own capital account statement information including all transactions provided by the fund. The datepicker can be set by the investor to anytime between the date of their first capital account transactions with the fund and the share-through date. For the Fund transaction page, the investor can view a list of all their raw capital account transactions before the share-through date. The Capital accounts &amp; Fund transactions function the same for both Carta fund administration and non-fund administration users of the information sharing feature.<br><img height=\"375\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6458146826643517552_RZpachWajrZ3Sa1ftO-Ds4n_ctMM4k3cVTK-quEEV358bE--tL2wD3WYzAd1fUfgDFZ12oraokNoLeMt4SNx4W-HUXHVsqfiggt9Isn2osrIo8xKGLP-LASav7UH4_ztU9zN2N9u\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"624\"> <img height=\"440\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8777321202752601675_7UJIiJkVrlfCleryqoAyJJx29TwU_Lg4eX38nhqNuZu1cUsh5TH-TjVpadr3QDD3U3RapS6z8DpkC3CqeDQdkiInrhLEwak_z6AEOzwA8nF0anqlpflVs3M3gVq_uQzLFMzWYWMb\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"624\"> <img height=\"355\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/2136191569796323820_thCinfgP0r_hSwhUmi1B_acHMAJBZhGx3c1L-cYj8M5cLEe6in6eHjwHF84eZC_3E34EtLmS2LLb4dmuCSU6yTavTkXkQILJfibNn3v7EnyrKrhufIXuM-7X8jvQZlD5pnBnGar3\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"624\">",
      "associatedImage": {
        "url": "carta/public/11/images/2136191569796323820_thCinfgP0r_hSwhUmi1B_acHMAJBZhGx3c1L-cYj8M5cLEe6in6eHjwHF84eZC_3E34EtLmS2LLb4dmuCSU6yTavTkXkQILJfibNn3v7EnyrKrhufIXuM-7X8jvQZlD5pnBnGar3"
