{
  "id": "-6252437594336312338",
  "subject": {
    "id": "-6252437594336312338",
    "text": {
      "text": "Recover Access to Carta Account"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-797140602135881900",
    "text": {
      "text": "If you have lost access to the email that is associated with your Carta account, our support team can help you add a new email address to your account with the help from the organization you are associated with on Carta.",
      "originalText": "If you have lost access to the email that is associated with your Carta account, our support team can help you add a new email address to your account with the help from the organization you are associated with on Carta."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "3015280435028705054",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "If you have a Personal Portfolio or Investment Firm with Carta:    You will need to contact your issuing company or contact Carta Support. If you contact Support, we will need to contact your issuing company in order to confirm your identity. Provide the following information when contacting:The mailing address on file.The new email that should be associated with your account.The email address currently connected to your account (that is currently inaccessible).",
        "originalText": "If you have a Personal Portfolio or Investment Firm with Carta:<br> <br> You will need to <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/contacting-the-issuer\" target=\"_blank\">contact your issuing company</a> or <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/contact-us\" target=\"_blank\">contact Carta Support</a>. If you contact Support, we will need to contact your issuing company in order to confirm your identity. Provide the following information when contacting:  The mailing address on file. The new email that should be associated with your account. The email address currently connected to your account (that is currently inaccessible).  <br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "If you work with a law firm and do not have any holdings in a company, contact your law firm directly or contact Carta Support. Our team will need confirmation from your law firm organization (if your law firm is set up on Carta), or from the companies that you work with and have accounts on Carta.    The company or law firm will need to confirm the following information:The email currently connected to your account (that is currently inaccessible).The new email that should be associated with your account.The companies you have access to on Carta. The company or law firm administrators will respond with the email and confirm all information is correct.",
        "originalText": "If you work with a law firm and do not have any holdings in a company, contact your law firm directly or <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/contact-us\" target=\"_blank\">contact Carta Support</a>. Our team will need confirmation from your law firm organization (if your law firm is set up on Carta), or from the companies that you work with and have accounts on Carta.<br> <br> The company or law firm will need to confirm the following information:  The email currently connected to your account (that is currently inaccessible). The new email that should be associated with your account. The companies you have access to on Carta.  The company or law firm administrators will respond with the email and confirm all information is correct.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Carta Support will add the new email address to your account and reach out to confirm the email address has been updated.",
        "originalText": "Carta Support will add the new email address to your account and reach out to confirm the email address has been updated.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "You will receive an email to verify the new email.",
        "originalText": "You will receive an email to verify the new email.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Once you have access to your account you can remove the old email by navigating to Settings > People.  carta/public/11/images/7795543033329572291_tj_L5JeAo92npKx7Y_3TEdLHZ7xQlZ9ZGyAyF5H59QBY4R6yZmhpVgVZXF953I0DdzF2gHLtRKHEJVNYcIAd1qOXO-3jt8qs9syFiF8LNzrHt8PeubAVQvEFUNiU7qWN-C77pRHJ",
        "originalText": "Once you have access to your account you can remove the old email by navigating to Settings &gt; People.<br> <img height=\"129\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7795543033329572291_tj_L5JeAo92npKx7Y_3TEdLHZ7xQlZ9ZGyAyF5H59QBY4R6yZmhpVgVZXF953I0DdzF2gHLtRKHEJVNYcIAd1qOXO-3jt8qs9syFiF8LNzrHt8PeubAVQvEFUNiU7qWN-C77pRHJ\" width=\"421\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/7795543033329572291_tj_L5JeAo92npKx7Y_3TEdLHZ7xQlZ9ZGyAyF5H59QBY4R6yZmhpVgVZXF953I0DdzF2gHLtRKHEJVNYcIAd1qOXO-3jt8qs9syFiF8LNzrHt8PeubAVQvEFUNiU7qWN-C77pRHJ"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click Edit to the right of the old user email that will be removed.",
        "originalText": "Click Edit to the right of the old user email that will be removed.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Click the trash can icon to delete the user.  carta/public/11/images/8173667950074254982_x94YhMKdql5tT_XSQ9bjmppnpwPiAN2KuK3K6YhIH-rDwEIJ0w8SlYUHo7O3TeuRnwjLsy-9ukKPux6wwESTAMBgcdaVTnDvy4sm1TM-hxZVhuV1NnDbohkGScWv-1kWfyerEpKL",
        "originalText": "Click the trash can icon to delete the user.<br> <img height=\"195\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8173667950074254982_x94YhMKdql5tT_XSQ9bjmppnpwPiAN2KuK3K6YhIH-rDwEIJ0w8SlYUHo7O3TeuRnwjLsy-9ukKPux6wwESTAMBgcdaVTnDvy4sm1TM-hxZVhuV1NnDbohkGScWv-1kWfyerEpKL\" width=\"414\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/8173667950074254982_x94YhMKdql5tT_XSQ9bjmppnpwPiAN2KuK3K6YhIH-rDwEIJ0w8SlYUHo7O3TeuRnwjLsy-9ukKPux6wwESTAMBgcdaVTnDvy4sm1TM-hxZVhuV1NnDbohkGScWv-1kWfyerEpKL"
        }
      }]
    }
  }, {
    "id": "6005967540352612206",
    "text": {
      "text": "NOTE: It is recommended to add an additional email address to avoid relying on company confirmation to update email and access your account. You may also review how to troubleshoot other login issues.",
      "originalText": "NOTE: It is recommended to add&nbsp;<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/contacting-the-issuer\" target=\"_blank\">an additional email</a> address to avoid relying on company confirmation to update email and access your account. You may also <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/troubleshooting-login-issues\" target=\"_blank\">review how to troubleshoot other login issues</a>."
    }
  }]
}

{
