    "text": {
      "text": "Transferring Fund Commitments"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-646158562223230909",
    "text": {
      "text": "Staff members have a tool to quickly transfer fund commitments. If a transfer is needed, please reach out to your Carta fund administrator or contact our Investor Services Support team through the Help center.  Below are steps on how to process the transfer yourself, but it is strongly encouraged that the transfer is done by a staff member.",
