        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click Import/Export. A modal to download the capital account transactions will appear. Click Download template.  carta/public/11/images/4792460145783624132_foB_6ORZhTAV4JIAxtfp7twepg_PhmtFe4qkGwpIc2pbV2EdluFblmBUWmpM9BAm6MSeBGBPmCAMI9RyDsYx9xJ4a-IujaS3gq7ky7IMbLQD7Yjr7Rm7SCIn1pCTBS3PIl7tqRpy  carta/public/11/images/8250515235975441027_7wCUkwSE_X8fKt0hS2UJvl4H0hdqI6EH4oKyJdxfsprb0TxizGq9V0R0g15jK7p4-ejd0uQj3zjsELBDui7B4piOWyPWpcRDQ9BBSI5scGAdZvXzB22CuBWDXWSy6NAIxHjGLAWe",
        "originalText": "Click Import/Export. A modal to download the capital account transactions will appear. Click Download template.<br> <img height=\"246\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/4792460145783624132_foB_6ORZhTAV4JIAxtfp7twepg_PhmtFe4qkGwpIc2pbV2EdluFblmBUWmpM9BAm6MSeBGBPmCAMI9RyDsYx9xJ4a-IujaS3gq7ky7IMbLQD7Yjr7Rm7SCIn1pCTBS3PIl7tqRpy\" width=\"466\"><br> <img height=\"204\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8250515235975441027_7wCUkwSE_X8fKt0hS2UJvl4H0hdqI6EH4oKyJdxfsprb0TxizGq9V0R0g15jK7p4-ejd0uQj3zjsELBDui7B4piOWyPWpcRDQ9BBSI5scGAdZvXzB22CuBWDXWSy6NAIxHjGLAWe\" width=\"481\">",
