      }, {
        "text": "Navigate back on the platform to Statements > Capitalaccount statements. In the Partner name drop down bar, search for the partner whose commitment is getting transferred.  carta/public/11/images/8244153486303756791_lSvqgRQSQHKAJjVHwQKBsRiJxgMPKZ1fqnLuBSnWovXXbLMJ-m2Nw9b8lmird1JKLZ8Pw38JvYH9keH-CPIAS76GTJ0cmE8ozlU86DKpRCKjM0UKpTlyZQa-RXv0vvdiLmch0M6s",
