      }, {
        "text": "Navigate back to the sheet and copy and paste the transferor name from the Reference sheet to the Transactions sheet.  carta/public/11/images/2430552908101317569_D4pOpdTRCj9HdfrwTy7GARseen5H8lh0s-Y0sI6zQkMT42Rry6HfxZiWiPI-Bt5esAEX5J9DoszCcR4Msor_CH_5kjqzUZOGeyT1rpRJzSSKaRkzos2do0GbV8hIf4033svhnTvm  carta/public/11/images/155440611262101116_4hQ98X6K2qq_BnwrkFEU8Y7Gorgoai3EkDDJ_7LNuZ2961fAxekj123uOkWPC3LZihJyNGcBJBi0fXjsBb7OKkHV2ETqMk1xSi7qXBmpeYOdRYkkF32gAnldbT8tkZTNWcqoiYQ6",
        "originalText": "Navigate back to the sheet and copy and paste the transferor name from the Reference sheet to the Transactions sheet.<br> <img height=\"404\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/2430552908101317569_D4pOpdTRCj9HdfrwTy7GARseen5H8lh0s-Y0sI6zQkMT42Rry6HfxZiWiPI-Bt5esAEX5J9DoszCcR4Msor_CH_5kjqzUZOGeyT1rpRJzSSKaRkzos2do0GbV8hIf4033svhnTvm\" width=\"432\"><br> <img height=\"516\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/155440611262101116_4hQ98X6K2qq_BnwrkFEU8Y7Gorgoai3EkDDJ_7LNuZ2961fAxekj123uOkWPC3LZihJyNGcBJBi0fXjsBb7OKkHV2ETqMk1xSi7qXBmpeYOdRYkkF32gAnldbT8tkZTNWcqoiYQ6\" width=\"462\">",
