        }
      }, {
        "text": "Referring back to the capital account statement tab, you will need to input the amount as the inverse of the amount that needs to be transfered. For the column 'Is this a transfer', 'Yes' will need to be inputted.In this example, Aron Foundation transferred 50% of their commitment to Brendan Basquez, so you will want to only input 50% of the transaction amount. Here, the Capital Contribution for Aron Foundation is $2,294,374.00 so the amount of ($1,147,187) will need to be inputted. carta/public/11/images/398823350535315059_ZEKuLqRkhUzavGlHuDnZ4BMpcKMCUj9du__Y6WA5NMp5-rkqXutGds7InS_1R18qYYd7VeNLrniqf00K6KzCKMWU3GT5NnDe0CNjM1hG-E7GAnGF0YjEMeCBKRCnCprkcH6f2giq",
        "originalText": "Referring back to the capital account statement tab, you will need to input the amount as the inverse of the amount that needs to be transfered. For the column 'Is this a transfer', 'Yes' will need to be inputted.  In this example, Aron Foundation transferred 50% of their commitment to Brendan Basquez, so you will want to only input 50% of the transaction amount. Here, the Capital Contribution for Aron Foundation is $2,294,374.00 so the amount of ($1,147,187) will need to be inputted.<br> <img height=\"208.48101265822785\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/398823350535315059_ZEKuLqRkhUzavGlHuDnZ4BMpcKMCUj9du__Y6WA5NMp5-rkqXutGds7InS_1R18qYYd7VeNLrniqf00K6KzCKMWU3GT5NnDe0CNjM1hG-E7GAnGF0YjEMeCBKRCnCprkcH6f2giq\" width=\"481\">  ",
