        }
      }, {
        "text": "For the transferee, the amount does not need to be inverted.In the example below, a Capital Contribution line of $1,147,187 will need to be added. carta/public/11/images/5590478200209915701_PUAN474sR-zm5hTX2n-sH29-UxfGin_Nn7gn84v2W82pnGIkbwJG44dxC3ShpXo8oqA87-F80qX3hkNqR0wczY9yaqHHnexg9uj8-aljwGsjsvB5Pq5U935PakgoJZoK8Bhgmrrx",
