{
  "id": "4103881117402973097",
  "subject": {
    "id": "4103881117402973097",
    "text": {
      "text": "Information for Terminated Employees"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "1927183031027512676",
    "text": {
      "text": "When an employee leaves a company, they will still have access to their Carta account with their previous work email and password. It is recommended to change the primary email of the employee’s Carta account to a personal email address as soon as possible to avoid complications after termination. Review this article if there are issues with logging in.",
      "originalText": "When an employee leaves a company, they will still have access to their Carta account with their previous work email and password. It is recommended to <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/how-to-change-email-address\" target=\"_blank\">change the primary email</a> of the employee’s Carta account to a personal email address as soon as possible to avoid complications after termination. <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/troubleshooting-login-issues\" target=\"_blank\">Review this article</a> if there are issues with logging in."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-424103579216123041",
    "text": {
      "text": "In the Carta account, the ex-employee can see their previously accepted securities. The securities are flagged asTerminated as it is still within the post-termination exercise period. Once the exercise period has expired, the option grant will no longer be outstanding.",
      "originalText": "In the Carta account, the ex-employee can see their previously accepted securities. The securities are flagged as Terminated as it is still within the <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/exercise-expiration-periods\" target=\"_blank\">post-termination exercise period</a>. Once the exercise period has expired, the option grant will no longer be outstanding."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "2839972132310060167",
    "text": {
      "text": "No notifications will be sent regarding the termination, however, they may receive an exercise expiration notice. If there are exercisable options remaining upon termination, the earliest reminder email will be sent out 21 days before the options expire with additional reminders sent as the expiration date approaches.",
      "originalText": "No notifications will be sent regarding the termination, however, they may receive an <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/exercise-expiration-notice\" target=\"_blank\">exercise expiration notice</a>. If there are exercisable options remaining upon termination, the earliest reminder email will be sent out 21 days before the options expire with additional reminders sent as the expiration date approaches."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "5633430385182429944",
    "text": {
      "text": "For questions regarding the termination or option grant details, contact the issuing company directly.",
      "originalText": "For questions regarding the termination or option grant details, <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/contacting-the-issuer\" target=\"_blank\">contact the issuing company</a> directly."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "1494859021998684118",
    "text": {
      "text": "We recommend that terminated employees go through the following steps. These steps can also be reviewed prior to departing from the company to review details ahead of time.",
      "originalText": "We recommend that terminated employees go through the following steps. These steps can also be reviewed prior to departing from the company to review details ahead of time.<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "4442278793290962946",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "Review the login email. To double-check to see if the primary email is a personal email address, click on the user’s name in the upper right and select Profile and Security. Follow this article to update the primary email, if needed.",
        "originalText": "Review the login email. To double-check to see if the primary email is a personal email address, click on the user’s name in the upper right and select Profile and Security. Follow <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/how-to-change-email-address\" target=\"_blank\">this article</a> to update the primary email, if needed.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "View the grant details by navigating to the Holdings page in Holdings > Portfolio, then click on the option grant image or ID.  carta/public/11/images/2216544687662290264_SO3-StBYQ_oDXUWIts-9SHagoKrLBzSiTaW49BTFD1XEamOuPMfdQvbgPPe6AeHWRRZ0GoHjL0hdTOJhzQcf6_PMSXcabpM1M6z6EF4u5MAZrhPtx7F8kTYbsnfN64C5iEiCHPUA    After clicking to open a grant they will be able to see how many options have vested and other option grant details.  carta/public/11/images/7066999563673329803_Xt2JcMhEk5XMj4Kc0sJw5sg5-19OgU9v5a6yRnWTqEB6PGw8X2RxrVN17lJb_s0aGg_877oHJ9Y4BIr9XyW1sGlGBdXg1WN2h77OJSbxQA8xYXHYD-H16grO5zIbQ-ZKNstpFyk6",
        "originalText": "View the grant details by navigating to the Holdings page in Holdings &gt; Portfolio, then click on the option grant image or ID.<br> <img height=\"415\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/2216544687662290264_SO3-StBYQ_oDXUWIts-9SHagoKrLBzSiTaW49BTFD1XEamOuPMfdQvbgPPe6AeHWRRZ0GoHjL0hdTOJhzQcf6_PMSXcabpM1M6z6EF4u5MAZrhPtx7F8kTYbsnfN64C5iEiCHPUA\" width=\"434\"><br> <br> After clicking to open a grant they will be able to see how many options have vested and other option grant details.<br> <img height=\"343\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7066999563673329803_Xt2JcMhEk5XMj4Kc0sJw5sg5-19OgU9v5a6yRnWTqEB6PGw8X2RxrVN17lJb_s0aGg_877oHJ9Y4BIr9XyW1sGlGBdXg1WN2h77OJSbxQA8xYXHYD-H16grO5zIbQ-ZKNstpFyk6\" width=\"434\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/7066999563673329803_Xt2JcMhEk5XMj4Kc0sJw5sg5-19OgU9v5a6yRnWTqEB6PGw8X2RxrVN17lJb_s0aGg_877oHJ9Y4BIr9XyW1sGlGBdXg1WN2h77OJSbxQA8xYXHYD-H16grO5zIbQ-ZKNstpFyk6"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Exercising vested options: Vested options can only be exercised after the termination date as any unvested options have returned to the issuing company’s option pool. These vested, unexercised options will be exercisable until the exercise expiration date is reached.    3A. If the option holder would like to exercise and the company has electronic exercises enabled - they will need to first connect their bank account.  NOTE: If connecting manually, the verification can take 2-3 business days.    3B. Once their bank account is connected, they will be able to exercise from the Holdings page and follow the ACH exercise workflow. If the company does not have electronic exercises enabled, contact the issuing company to exercise manually.  NOTE: The ACH workflow is only available for US residents of US-based companies.    In addition, this article covers the basic tax implications of exercising. Contact a tax advisor to see if exercising is right for you.  carta/public/11/images/7245371569119108004_rarhDywOdzJa5cWxdJ7qIsP0Rd9o_-xVgu1LD-u0TaJzdrMiFxShF_DEyoLLM_xVBs7WhYGZONm1JObzzsWFVBK0dWHs72dKRqskg5Sxu3nrldjNdTIKxG9rV6RlPvGX2-RJWSep",
        "originalText": "Exercising vested options: Vested options can only be exercised after the termination date as any unvested options have returned to the issuing company’s option pool. These vested, unexercised options will be exercisable until the exercise expiration date is reached.<br> <br> 3A. If the option holder would like to exercise and the company has electronic exercises enabled - they will need to first <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/set-bank-account\" target=\"_blank\">connect their bank account</a>.<br> NOTE: If connecting manually, the verification can take 2-3 business days.<br> <br> 3B. Once their bank account is connected, they will be able to exercise from the Holdings page and follow the <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/exercising-options-on-carta\" target=\"_blank\">ACH exercise workflow</a>. If the company does not have electronic exercises enabled, contact the issuing company to <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/exercise-option-grant-manually\" target=\"_blank\">exercise manually</a>.<br> NOTE: The ACH workflow is only available for US residents of US-based companies.<br> <br> In addition, this article covers the <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/tax-forms-grants\" target=\"_blank\">basic tax implications of exercising</a>. Contact a tax advisor to see if exercising is right for you.<br> <img height=\"279\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7245371569119108004_rarhDywOdzJa5cWxdJ7qIsP0Rd9o_-xVgu1LD-u0TaJzdrMiFxShF_DEyoLLM_xVBs7WhYGZONm1JObzzsWFVBK0dWHs72dKRqskg5Sxu3nrldjNdTIKxG9rV6RlPvGX2-RJWSep\" width=\"433\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/7245371569119108004_rarhDywOdzJa5cWxdJ7qIsP0Rd9o_-xVgu1LD-u0TaJzdrMiFxShF_DEyoLLM_xVBs7WhYGZONm1JObzzsWFVBK0dWHs72dKRqskg5Sxu3nrldjNdTIKxG9rV6RlPvGX2-RJWSep"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "If there are company-specific issues, questions, or concerns, use the Report Issue feature to contact the issuing company.",
        "originalText": "If there are company-specific issues, questions, or concerns, <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/contacting-the-issuer\" target=\"_blank\">use the <i>Report Issue</i> feature to contact the issuing company</a>."
      }]
    }
  }]
}

