        "text": "A summary of the bank details will appear, click Save.  carta/public/11/images/8758063535276595867_Xwut2EcjovvtF-YRtcGdzD7AxgKZuYQ_7fBU7FfWssIGN-PolrewIVJC7B0ooAyWrgzBtgt3F8IZ6HSQt0CSKYlvC4RMZ315vB9AAEHbyb6b9ktIKFVooMvI4sHwVVLpwN6xVsZd",
        "originalText": "A summary of the bank details will appear, click Save.<br> <img height=\"192\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8758063535276595867_Xwut2EcjovvtF-YRtcGdzD7AxgKZuYQ_7fBU7FfWssIGN-PolrewIVJC7B0ooAyWrgzBtgt3F8IZ6HSQt0CSKYlvC4RMZ315vB9AAEHbyb6b9ktIKFVooMvI4sHwVVLpwN6xVsZd\" width=\"287\">",
