        }
      }, {
        "text": "After you have received the test deposits in your bank account, return to the Payment Information page, click on the V drop down, and select Verify account. carta/public/11/images/5756023979549101719_aTUj5ZaN7eRASBdlZo6C7Fk1kXzEQTEV9R6GUSvhAfoBGRC-3a9B50wQLqOSjmQovp2BRCglKGkshGJA2SZdIHppijmF__26CkOr6YiS5eR0osOI7Ic6bYGwXF-yFy3pTQDUHBqa",
        "originalText": "After you have received the test deposits in your bank account, return to the Payment Information page, click on the V drop down, and select Verify account.<br> <img height=\"52\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5756023979549101719_aTUj5ZaN7eRASBdlZo6C7Fk1kXzEQTEV9R6GUSvhAfoBGRC-3a9B50wQLqOSjmQovp2BRCglKGkshGJA2SZdIHppijmF__26CkOr6YiS5eR0osOI7Ic6bYGwXF-yFy3pTQDUHBqa\" width=\"389\">",
