        }
      }, {
        "text": "Enter the two unique test deposit amounts. Click Verify to proceed. The bank account being verified can also be Set as default by checking off the box prior to confirming verification.  carta/public/11/images/8212025141817648527_ijR0eXiuDjKCXPFQKodNp_3Dg7tRif_qBdNgY9YvSNIZdC0Kf1F7HS4WXp1Py61RP2wE9OE0CqvBq3u-gEOypc2cBKce00TMjlbNoml_OAA6Uyy6oPG_Y5TcublRiHsmIG0Lxscp",
