{
  "id": "2461697035672105528",
  "subject": {
    "id": "2461697035672105528",
    "text": {
      "text": "How to Participate in a Tender Offer"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-3802641724279393605",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "If you have been invited to participate in a tender offer, you will receive an email to participate.  carta/public/11/images/1580271713385147695_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "If you have been invited to participate in a <a href=\"http://carta.com/blog/tender-offer-faq/\" target=\"_blank\">tender offer</a>, you will receive an email to participate.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1580271713385147695_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/1580271713385147695_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Once logged in to Carta, a task will appear under the Secondary sales tab. Click Get Started to participate.  carta/public/11/images/7335255159791286171_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Once logged in to Carta, a task will appear under the Secondary sales tab. Click Get Started to participate.<br> <img src=\"carta/public/11/images/7335255159791286171_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 468px;height: 179px;\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/7335255159791286171_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Sign the non-disclosure agreement.  carta/public/11/images/5133751135118163331_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Sign the non-disclosure agreement.<br> <img src=\"carta/public/11/images/5133751135118163331_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 468px;height: 390px;\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/5133751135118163331_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Review the transaction overview and click on Participate.  carta/public/11/images/6375338800473335315_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Review the transaction overview and click on Participate.<br> <img src=\"carta/public/11/images/6375338800473335315_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 468px;height: 438px;\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/6375338800473335315_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Review and agree to the offer documents by clicking the View links to the right.  carta/public/11/images/7138336963787064162_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Review and agree to the offer documents by clicking the View links to the right.<br> <img src=\"carta/public/11/images/7138336963787064162_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 468px;height: 303px;\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/7138336963787064162_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "After you have checked the box to confirm you have read all documents, click Save and continue.",
        "originalText": "After you have checked the box to confirm you have read all documents, click Save and continue."
      }, {
        "text": "On the Sell elections page, enter the number of shares you would like to sell next to each eligible security. carta/public/11/images/7616840787414279335_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "On the Sell elections page, enter the number of shares you would like to sell next to each eligible security.<img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7616840787414279335_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/7616840787414279335_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "If you are requesting a cashless exercise, you will then be prompted to review and agree to the option paperwork and exercise notice for each option.  carta/public/11/images/7514765074025943320_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "If you are requesting a cashless exercise, you will then be prompted to review and agree to the option paperwork and exercise notice for each option.<br> <img src=\"carta/public/11/images/7514765074025943320_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 468px;height: 371px;\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/7514765074025943320_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Confirm your account information and upload a copy of your valid government ID (for example, a driver's license, non-driver ID or a passport).  carta/public/11/images/292414736485638771_rtaImage    9a. If you are placing an order for an entity, upload an Agent authorization document that verifies you are authorized to sign on behalf of the entity.  carta/public/11/images/6858825271392889189_rtaImage    9b. Electronically or manually complete the spousal consent form (if applicable).  carta/public/11/images/3105590038844419197_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Confirm your account information and upload a copy of your valid government ID (for example, a driver's license, non-driver ID or a passport).<br> <img src=\"carta/public/11/images/292414736485638771_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 468px;height: 493px;\"><br> <br> 9a. If you are placing an order for an entity, upload an Agent authorization document that verifies you are authorized to sign on behalf of the entity.<br> <img src=\"carta/public/11/images/6858825271392889189_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 468px;height: 455px;\"><br> <br> 9b. Electronically or manually complete the spousal consent form (if applicable).<br> <img src=\"carta/public/11/images/3105590038844419197_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 468px;height: 426px;\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/3105590038844419197_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Electronically or manually complete the applicable tax form.  carta/public/11/images/6490628663750097999_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Electronically or manually complete the applicable tax form.<br> <img src=\"carta/public/11/images/6490628663750097999_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 468px;height: 321px;\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/6490628663750097999_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Review your order and your connected bank account and agree to Carta’s Payment Terms and Conditions. If you need to change the account, please see this article. A bank account must be connected to participate. If you do not use the instant connection option, there is an additional step of verifying your bank account through test deposits that will need to be completed prior to settling the tender offer. The transfer of funds cannot be executed without connecting and verifying your bank account. For more information on this process, review this article.    If you do not have a US bank account, you will be required to provide wire instructions to receive your proceeds via wire transfer.  carta/public/11/images/2442920404732556038_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Review your order and your connected bank account and agree to Carta’s Payment Terms and Conditions. If you need to change the account, please see <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/changing-bank-account-information\" target=\"_blank\">this article</a>. A bank account must be connected to participate. If you do not use the instant connection option, there is an additional step of verifying your bank account through test deposits that will need to be completed prior to settling the tender offer. The transfer of funds cannot be executed without connecting and verifying your bank account. For more information on this process, review <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/set-bank-account\" target=\"_blank\">this article</a>.<br> <br> If you do not have a US bank account, you will be required to provide wire instructions to receive your proceeds via wire transfer.<br> <img src=\"carta/public/11/images/2442920404732556038_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 468px;height: 363px;\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/2442920404732556038_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Review and agree to the Terms and Conditions and select Submit order.  carta/public/11/images/640869997367258330_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Review and agree to the Terms and Conditions and select Submit order.<br> <img src=\"carta/public/11/images/640869997367258330_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 468px;height: 237px;\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/640869997367258330_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Once submitted, you will be able to review your order on the Order summary page.  carta/public/11/images/7104458785953093638_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Once submitted, you will be able to review your order on the Order summary page.<br> <img src=\"carta/public/11/images/7104458785953093638_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 468px;height: 453px;\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/7104458785953093638_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "To revisit the tender offer dashboard at any time, log into your portfolio and navigate to the Sell link at the top.  carta/public/11/images/2060074288978881138_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "To revisit the tender offer dashboard at any time, log into your portfolio and navigate to the Sell link at the top.<br> <img src=\"carta/public/11/images/2060074288978881138_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 468px;height: 92px;\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/2060074288978881138_rtaImage"
        }
      }]
    }
  }, {
