        }
      }, {
        "text": "Select individual awards to apply the custom assumptions to by selecting the box next to the grant number.  carta/public/11/images/7316653833789162913_6DIEsuup9C-uMjd4Jkl2JG0sXVTvtGgOJz4M_O88wYw3Otxr31H5lUyrVMJnhqvcAnTe8NzGy4JTFut753HRp2a2ReK7KDL_J_8xWEo0Drk3JsT88RViQ0fAggaEAAPZgoojz8bM    Or you can select all awards to apply the custom assumptions as seen below.  carta/public/11/images/6628315481581811527_ApbkB2V4JF4qOg3e9lb3yZxsQO3kI_YdDbG9xx81DtYtllBGXoPBWNSHiArUjI3tfxQdkzraI02XVPHl2FQMM-gWg3KGB0rv_f4GdO_3Hy_5IV-Zf8oEPm6syYnqdEsML8ZRcvMo",
        "originalText": "Select individual awards to apply the custom assumptions to by selecting the box next to the grant number.<br> <img height=\"137\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7316653833789162913_6DIEsuup9C-uMjd4Jkl2JG0sXVTvtGgOJz4M_O88wYw3Otxr31H5lUyrVMJnhqvcAnTe8NzGy4JTFut753HRp2a2ReK7KDL_J_8xWEo0Drk3JsT88RViQ0fAggaEAAPZgoojz8bM\" width=\"431\"><br> <br> Or you can select all awards to apply the custom assumptions as seen below.<br> <img height=\"165\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6628315481581811527_ApbkB2V4JF4qOg3e9lb3yZxsQO3kI_YdDbG9xx81DtYtllBGXoPBWNSHiArUjI3tfxQdkzraI02XVPHl2FQMM-gWg3KGB0rv_f4GdO_3Hy_5IV-Zf8oEPm6syYnqdEsML8ZRcvMo\" width=\"431\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/6628315481581811527_ApbkB2V4JF4qOg3e9lb3yZxsQO3kI_YdDbG9xx81DtYtllBGXoPBWNSHiArUjI3tfxQdkzraI02XVPHl2FQMM-gWg3KGB0rv_f4GdO_3Hy_5IV-Zf8oEPm6syYnqdEsML8ZRcvMo"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click the blue Actions button and select Edit expense detail.  carta/public/11/images/8941214850847419791_9LXcitIArV9hdLfGPQ46l8Bhio4fPSZrryS9FSNXfANx_dO4Z3Q6LEf40RkCIO28zjwGpdjTrZoAkIokj9fgAz3b8iouyJHaOJiTy3X2VNIESNw71UUWBddsrIgUKXQ4UEsPlY-4",
        "originalText": "Click the blue Actions button and select Edit expense detail.<br> <img height=\"199\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8941214850847419791_9LXcitIArV9hdLfGPQ46l8Bhio4fPSZrryS9FSNXfANx_dO4Z3Q6LEf40RkCIO28zjwGpdjTrZoAkIokj9fgAz3b8iouyJHaOJiTy3X2VNIESNw71UUWBddsrIgUKXQ4UEsPlY-4\" width=\"427\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/8941214850847419791_9LXcitIArV9hdLfGPQ46l8Bhio4fPSZrryS9FSNXfANx_dO4Z3Q6LEf40RkCIO28zjwGpdjTrZoAkIokj9fgAz3b8iouyJHaOJiTy3X2VNIESNw71UUWBddsrIgUKXQ4UEsPlY-4"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "A modal will then pop-up on the screen, prompting you to select which assumption you would like to change. Upload a custom term, interest rate, volatility, fair value (or option value as calculated offline in your own Black-Scholes calculator), the amortization method, or the expense status (where you can choose to include or exclude any awards).  carta/public/11/images/8400508865945150714_at2F86jh-91WjFT-X8kk5tjORy4lSqarPsQsZDji3-fZEsdsekH7-KSF0J4N_XjjQNNzSQ2hbE7pL6uqFOw7OQSxfKkoWUpa06Im8y4yVvDQOEm0OQT6cyLzNf-hDDJ2M5H1kT8X    NOTE: if you are attempting to edit the custom expected term, Carta will need you to also upload a custom interest rate and volatility as our calculation for these inputs are based on the Simplified Method to determine expected term.",
        "originalText": "A modal will then pop-up on the screen, prompting you to select which assumption you would like to change. Upload a custom term, interest rate, volatility, fair value (or option value as calculated offline in your own Black-Scholes calculator), the amortization method, or the expense status (where you can choose to include or exclude any awards).<br> <img height=\"225\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8400508865945150714_at2F86jh-91WjFT-X8kk5tjORy4lSqarPsQsZDji3-fZEsdsekH7-KSF0J4N_XjjQNNzSQ2hbE7pL6uqFOw7OQSxfKkoWUpa06Im8y4yVvDQOEm0OQT6cyLzNf-hDDJ2M5H1kT8X\" width=\"428\"><br> <br> NOTE: if you are attempting to edit the custom expected term, Carta will need you to also upload a custom interest rate and volatility as our calculation for these inputs are based on the Simplified Method to determine expected term.",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/8400508865945150714_at2F86jh-91WjFT-X8kk5tjORy4lSqarPsQsZDji3-fZEsdsekH7-KSF0J4N_XjjQNNzSQ2hbE7pL6uqFOw7OQSxfKkoWUpa06Im8y4yVvDQOEm0OQT6cyLzNf-hDDJ2M5H1kT8X"
        }
      }]
    }
  }, {
    "id": "8687058868544114519",
    "text": {
      "text": "If you need assistance calculating the interest rate and volatility based on your custom term assumption or would like to upload multiple custom assumptions for the awards by using a bulk assumptions importer, submit a case via Carta's Help Center. Learn more about Carta's Help Center.",
