        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click Actions, then Edit plan details.  carta/public/11/images/7980048287691980068_srjkHc_0YsqV-4dnWTk4ifeykoZ8kW87nyq8ryFTIaswrUK2A5SvfM4HGmbTKTZP8HkcYqP1_qi_DV08wokgE0icdVhtly-HlAK9cjMxKNrxvkRv7DjBa9sudBm6-91zp8wUIIID",
        "originalText": "Click Actions, then Edit plan details.<br> <img height=\"135\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7980048287691980068_srjkHc_0YsqV-4dnWTk4ifeykoZ8kW87nyq8ryFTIaswrUK2A5SvfM4HGmbTKTZP8HkcYqP1_qi_DV08wokgE0icdVhtly-HlAK9cjMxKNrxvkRv7DjBa9sudBm6-91zp8wUIIID\" width=\"430\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/7980048287691980068_srjkHc_0YsqV-4dnWTk4ifeykoZ8kW87nyq8ryFTIaswrUK2A5SvfM4HGmbTKTZP8HkcYqP1_qi_DV08wokgE0icdVhtly-HlAK9cjMxKNrxvkRv7DjBa9sudBm6-91zp8wUIIID"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Scroll to the bottom to update the repurchase period. Changes to these fields will only apply to future issuances.  carta/public/11/images/8567801708021492648_1UZpNwSFr8wiBvkdBsFHXI_Xzx-AyU8-yODB-1UUrLqPviXZBVpfEP7sdlXNYogH2V2gzx-hLq76_j-xeixqPnZBHuw-DOHcyUQrtgLn_xcNDMZG2COiGpKF0Rc-jUOKX2gdpl2A",
