          "url": "carta/public/11/images/4762217470575027206_SWI5zaq_2PdG36s3OQXpLgr7w9jb-hMRQBAwnZ9IVrMJKYxOgbvoY3r1_-WB9fG5gBzanNEhfJItAg6VTtHKWDzBELF9lIv59OH-E0QwyUOE5pJysMphPurTfY5MDzL310l5cXbn"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "On the Audit confirmation report line, select the date for the report and click Export. carta/public/11/images/19750226280993324_oapUNaUDCjfLkllNmEbqsm83cAsTnCJdqM0vZ8IaA3EdL82wpWglx2gwhKG3JqVLBjwjlrIIIALLGeCqTi5ASIa3xUF1MmX7dJRRky5KGPNRHn14rlyCyUsvbC1q1Bd2Qltth752",
        "originalText": "On the Audit confirmation report line, select the date for the report and click Export. <img height=\"281\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/19750226280993324_oapUNaUDCjfLkllNmEbqsm83cAsTnCJdqM0vZ8IaA3EdL82wpWglx2gwhKG3JqVLBjwjlrIIIALLGeCqTi5ASIa3xUF1MmX7dJRRky5KGPNRHn14rlyCyUsvbC1q1Bd2Qltth752\" width=\"624\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/19750226280993324_oapUNaUDCjfLkllNmEbqsm83cAsTnCJdqM0vZ8IaA3EdL82wpWglx2gwhKG3JqVLBjwjlrIIIALLGeCqTi5ASIa3xUF1MmX7dJRRky5KGPNRHn14rlyCyUsvbC1q1Bd2Qltth752"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "The report will download as an Excel spreadsheet and show all of the securities currently held by your investment firm, with each holding entity listed on a separate tab.",
        "originalText": "The report will download as an Excel spreadsheet and show all of the securities currently held by your investment firm, with each holding entity listed on a separate tab."
      }]
    }
  }, {
    "id": "7753305194656073189",
    "text": {
      "text": "TheSafekeeping column indicates that the security is held electronically on Carta (\"Carta customer - digital safekeeping\"). This column also indicates securities that we custody on paper in our vault (\"Non-Carta customer - physical safekeeping\"). In addition, this column may indicate \"Withdrawn\" if we no longer custody the security.",
      "originalText": "<br>The Safekeeping column indicates that the security is held electronically on Carta (\"Carta customer - digital safekeeping\"). This column also indicates securities that we custody on paper in our vault (\"Non-Carta customer - physical safekeeping\"). In addition, this column may indicate \"Withdrawn\" if we no longer custody the security."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "1297945053919688754",
    "text": {
      "text": "NOTE: If you have any questions regarding the audit confirmation report, submit a case via Carta's Help Center. Learn more about Carta's Help Center.",
      "originalText": "NOTE: If you have any questions regarding the audit confirmation report, submit a case via Carta's <a href=\"https://app.carta.com/profiles/update?help=true\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Help Center</u></a>. <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/carta-help-center\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Learn more about Carta's Help Center</u></a>."
    }
  }]
