      "item": [{
        "text": "Navigate to the fund containing the investor(s) with whom you would like to share documents, and go to Partners > Partner documents.  carta/public/11/images/6112287018901473024_QXt0rwWzLNM-mL62ATFxb8prY87HfPxRgE1OwNlW_Dm29pnJTGJromECPdrFU0kOyGCifY9Ze6zy0JWefdehSEn0KRxAir_ufgjmGrC7UZg2fy5VcCDtKTwukXSkBcdALQKKWzGC",
        "originalText": "Navigate to the fund containing the investor(s) with whom you would like to share documents, and go to Partners &gt; Partner documents.<br> <img height=\"285\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6112287018901473024_QXt0rwWzLNM-mL62ATFxb8prY87HfPxRgE1OwNlW_Dm29pnJTGJromECPdrFU0kOyGCifY9Ze6zy0JWefdehSEn0KRxAir_ufgjmGrC7UZg2fy5VcCDtKTwukXSkBcdALQKKWzGC\" width=\"624\">",
