        "originalText": "After logging into Carta, click your name in the upper right hand corner and select Profile and security.<br> <img height=\"233\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/2443909322269324065_nTulmfzaiiZVCtmp-K_JIM8rAasSFcjz_C9PM_Li108TKfEMci0rIz57vOMGpYL0MbhEk5vpb08Drk2QgYQsPrEohf9rgplRac75e6cqsNyoIaAUVDruejLRZj0gUA3Tor7kLyYe\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"368\">",
        "associatedImage": {
