        "text": "Click on + Add payment method and select Connect bank account instantly or Add payment method manually.If connecting instantly, proceed to step 4.If connecting manually, proceed to step 5. carta/public/11/images/3392266049467999666_kF3KMCitTNioPg-P7Jg3ZShHc1J2NrgcaC38W_MHKwDwYlSNjoMFI-SLKHkkTFUlUqfRTegnwXMyMpOFGd_RIv1qj5TwxZCsEXf30agLjw5akEfaDuqilTyJN-dsO2lTucrP_bR2",
        "originalText": "Click on + Add payment method and select Connect bank account instantly or Add payment method manually.  If connecting instantly, proceed to step 4. If connecting manually, proceed to step 5.  <img height=\"108\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3392266049467999666_kF3KMCitTNioPg-P7Jg3ZShHc1J2NrgcaC38W_MHKwDwYlSNjoMFI-SLKHkkTFUlUqfRTegnwXMyMpOFGd_RIv1qj5TwxZCsEXf30agLjw5akEfaDuqilTyJN-dsO2lTucrP_bR2\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"385\">",
