        "originalText": "A payment method can be added instantly or manually. Select Connect to the right of Bank account (instant) to link your bank account information instantly.<br> <img height=\"213\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5389955681632606510_pTxuhXRJNsKrtPheCM0I9E5Vo4d-skFvmxwf_o-YPvZVf0iufpSa6X0VK5k6o1en700l7jc7f3VV0quwttYGvcSdDPt7O02RFjMPv9sCwWLUQSR0SnF-GIgevQDy82CvvtJKUrAq\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"437\">  Carta partners with Plaid to instantly connect your bank account.<br> <img height=\"287\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/2320613452173396999_CfwJa4DlBx7ehM5yk1VrStDmTnUU0Fn9bqUajnqhy7w_e_h6Tw-YHR0kXweiIFD6MCzqIcnlHf5JQlD3vtbDnzPm6akMqfh6FOt3vX4N-DvjegWjcdeU1TlV9Hd-ZaJnDlQH7MZj\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"192\"> Select, or search for, the bank from the list. For this article, Chase Bank will be used as the example.<br> <img height=\"269\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5420021800064035725__QTHuHjsQJZRe6yzLxsJ7SGyEGCCAoi5zyulVOeosIwqqImGFhDV3y1m99JC-o1rpMHNYQCPNUNOTHAPZ_rJNg7zHAWlf2-tIUrEOjQbvptC2FIg4KVIt8ssRvHXEpYs2qSVk9A4\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"191\"> Enter your bank account credentials.<br> <img height=\"267\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7280776180876427561_Uubog6I6Ab4u_UyPSGzChK2DHK4Sa4kSPNbqs4cVY4UtJ-yIY8mpaYdS85cRgil5RjJ-sv1Kq5jw5jK2oq8IAS3XjhyMhbNhWBI7mMPVJX8dY14H1vq6p4FCsvXI7tAq_jutxo26\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"191\"> Select the Checkings account and click Continue.<br> <img height=\"295\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3471356883412007705_zKuOJ3_xmbjfewppEHenp_uZi6l7xGtVRVJKV9IUBTcVFCvGhEw4FolrLZZeaXCsvyfhS4nzbhNUyADN0iJ8rdunSjQS7hLbqbIL9LWjdzDSICd-qZ3kloWJf0UrvwTqctsrpaHU\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"191\">  ",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/3471356883412007705_zKuOJ3_xmbjfewppEHenp_uZi6l7xGtVRVJKV9IUBTcVFCvGhEw4FolrLZZeaXCsvyfhS4nzbhNUyADN0iJ8rdunSjQS7hLbqbIL9LWjdzDSICd-qZ3kloWJf0UrvwTqctsrpaHU"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "If you cannot enter your bank credentials instantly, select Connect to the right of Bank account (manual) instead.  carta/public/11/images/3050561598344072115_jA_6mfcnmf2o8fMAvx3HtuMXP0zC-h8DgzazhT7NifNUVZTOnBVrkcMU8F65FijH0jaHUpYX1lDkKUQLpfkZ9M2ENs435jpPy_isFQ3mckFtYIV1aaHgT5N4DDHRvJmWuab59rfTIn the popup window, input bank account details. Check off theACH transactions option to enable electronic options exercise for US optionholders. ClickNext. carta/public/11/images/5719300686421665293_lVAnwH6Xjon8GjsvXTwwZAYrgu3YCm2ni3jClvF23NEDuFrARR8ESifx3VoJ85gFI-1zbzZNsOBgc6e0d4boBWspiEYdKfJt5FGC73Q4_gnfxAKcXc3eMgLZ8Fq45F7Mb9MXDZPaReview the information entered and clickSave.< carta/public/11/images/6077802349161605116_PmV89FFNvTRRKpKf7A4tmlJTZDd7q-tKOQadZm9y1lI_WkooW3md7smv8zjJs1Pj214Nrm6OjmcRxeGaCWPwYK4D4iUeytZ2m9zcSNr5pSnnVB8hyKyKsZRd8EMxzPT4i7vj3P2zTwo unique test deposits will be made into your bank account in 2-3 business days. These test deposits will come from either \"ACH Credit ESHARES INC - DUES\" or \"ESHARES INC PAYROLL PPD\".  NOTE: Many brokerage accounts do not allow ACH deposits - if you are not receiving the verification deposits, please confirm with your bank that it allows ACH deposits to be made into your account. carta/public/11/images/8756846148257243207_NKHHDN8hZVGGfF1d6fTh-yGxV5WUDChfsiyti4RcDQhEwl6RiP-V5vmAHFWGzB_4VyaDmeXNFozdMgdcSOT1RTHtmxVCfeFTR2OKSM0mgC9Au5yHUGFdr0bkzV1wvav6ESxmD_48Once you return to thePayment page, click onActions > Verify account. carta/public/11/images/1571279995359008237_jYjCtR8P6-cn8-Ufe3C2qUJ_g28WyvT6d1H_5yT9BjdKfaRy-j0LDjmj70L9CRPIn3wvHtQLw5lZk3NB5dDdKmQBjNeVos_RqN1mFJSJEaP3xM_eXoZmoRViD2b_qFia94TabQ72Enter the two unique test deposit amounts. ClickVerify to proceed. The bank account being verified can also beSet as default by checking off the box prior to confirming verification. carta/public/11/images/2933090924363276514_tNaVYek2EDpSk5UqVkdArZ-bsMUKCSy3T_Sy5cbyXD_UUu0wQCtmN3F1HGXDQ0eZjib5dxU5uU1YvlRy-uGF1gooKSC_BwCqhqXSQHNZV8I8EObLicuv4I1BBiQWq7GVaQnUTAUK Upon successful verification, payment transactions will be created to reverse the two unique test deposits.",
        "originalText": "If you cannot enter your bank credentials instantly, select Connect to the right of Bank account (manual) instead.<br> <img height=\"213\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/3050561598344072115_jA_6mfcnmf2o8fMAvx3HtuMXP0zC-h8DgzazhT7NifNUVZTOnBVrkcMU8F65FijH0jaHUpYX1lDkKUQLpfkZ9M2ENs435jpPy_isFQ3mckFtYIV1aaHgT5N4DDHRvJmWuab59rfT\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"437\">  In the popup window, input bank account details. Check off the ACH transactions option to enable electronic options exercise for US optionholders. Click Next.<br> <img height=\"203\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/5719300686421665293_lVAnwH6Xjon8GjsvXTwwZAYrgu3YCm2ni3jClvF23NEDuFrARR8ESifx3VoJ85gFI-1zbzZNsOBgc6e0d4boBWspiEYdKfJt5FGC73Q4_gnfxAKcXc3eMgLZ8Fq45F7Mb9MXDZPa\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"195\"> Review the information entered and click Save.&lt;<br> <img height=\"143\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/6077802349161605116_PmV89FFNvTRRKpKf7A4tmlJTZDd7q-tKOQadZm9y1lI_WkooW3md7smv8zjJs1Pj214Nrm6OjmcRxeGaCWPwYK4D4iUeytZ2m9zcSNr5pSnnVB8hyKyKsZRd8EMxzPT4i7vj3P2z\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"195\"> Two unique test deposits will be made into your bank account in 2-3 business days. These test deposits will come from either \"ACH Credit ESHARES INC - DUES\" or \"ESHARES INC PAYROLL PPD\".<br> NOTE: Many brokerage accounts do not allow ACH deposits - if you are not receiving the verification deposits, please confirm with your bank that it allows ACH deposits to be made into your account.<br> <img height=\"25\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8756846148257243207_NKHHDN8hZVGGfF1d6fTh-yGxV5WUDChfsiyti4RcDQhEwl6RiP-V5vmAHFWGzB_4VyaDmeXNFozdMgdcSOT1RTHtmxVCfeFTR2OKSM0mgC9Au5yHUGFdr0bkzV1wvav6ESxmD_48\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"377\"> Once you return to the Payment page, click on Actions &gt; Verify account.<br> <img height=\"53\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1571279995359008237_jYjCtR8P6-cn8-Ufe3C2qUJ_g28WyvT6d1H_5yT9BjdKfaRy-j0LDjmj70L9CRPIn3wvHtQLw5lZk3NB5dDdKmQBjNeVos_RqN1mFJSJEaP3xM_eXoZmoRViD2b_qFia94TabQ72\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"393\"> Enter the two unique test&nbsp;deposit amounts. Click Verify to proceed. The bank account being verified can also be Set as default by checking off the box prior to confirming verification.<br> <img height=\"232\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/2933090924363276514_tNaVYek2EDpSk5UqVkdArZ-bsMUKCSy3T_Sy5cbyXD_UUu0wQCtmN3F1HGXDQ0eZjib5dxU5uU1YvlRy-uGF1gooKSC_BwCqhqXSQHNZV8I8EObLicuv4I1BBiQWq7GVaQnUTAUK\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"296\"> &nbsp;Upon successful verification, payment transactions will be created to reverse the two unique&nbsp;test&nbsp;deposits.  ",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/2933090924363276514_tNaVYek2EDpSk5UqVkdArZ-bsMUKCSy3T_Sy5cbyXD_UUu0wQCtmN3F1HGXDQ0eZjib5dxU5uU1YvlRy-uGF1gooKSC_BwCqhqXSQHNZV8I8EObLicuv4I1BBiQWq7GVaQnUTAUK"
        }
