        "originalText": "If the email address that received&nbsp;the invitation has not been registered, click&nbsp;Create Account.&nbsp;If the email address that received the invitation has been registered, click View Account.&nbsp;  Review this <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/account-registration\" target=\"_blank\">support article</a> for detailed guidance on the registration process. If you have forgotten your password, click Forgot Password? on the login page or follow <a href=\"https://app.carta.com/accounts/password/reset/\" target=\"_blank\">this link</a>.  <img height=\"383\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8104298600881126220_48_36FcgKBIjEc1svx22OYfxUssgwG3doAu1LwPeHjy_GYh-y50xazMOn2KzwAEThOtnu-__i_mBP1yTw2z1NJYf_9rGqDyg7FFdQwua0OgHFVx6JfKjYXkVW7KIMPzsUPIUtNy3\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"376\"> <img height=\"341\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/2876348274278877313_ieD7CR6yWQGyME859rFbxMBO05hxKn7i-p3i2nlnSjjC8lOlsrADkIDPS-RYQYJSD-Lu1CVW3F_4euNX44rss3MbpDoAsVCbggovK8MDxP-nPTG_hyUsbnQuNQe5XcEQclouIod5\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"463\">",
