        }
      }, {
        "text": "Once logged into Carta, you will be directed to a modal to agree to electronic communications with the fund. carta/public/11/images/7937913175475058731_TdKVn60PK1aJLcyk_muhZWDKeKVex5959uEw_Sco49M8a_CLCrNEkiCuEg5xFZ_SJRl-lGcZ5JWknE29fj7OtoAOXJxFPlkQMfA2pBNDi5MV3H7748jm03hADfBA4dFw_pJweZYn",
        "originalText": "Once logged into Carta, you will be directed to a modal to agree to electronic communications with the fund.&nbsp; <img height=\"316\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/7937913175475058731_TdKVn60PK1aJLcyk_muhZWDKeKVex5959uEw_Sco49M8a_CLCrNEkiCuEg5xFZ_SJRl-lGcZ5JWknE29fj7OtoAOXJxFPlkQMfA2pBNDi5MV3H7748jm03hADfBA4dFw_pJweZYn\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"624\">",
