      "text": "Issue Restricted Stock Awards (RSAs)"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "7544735274059311933",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "Navigate to Securities > Equity Awards. In the RSAs tab, click Draft shares. These shares will be deducted from the equity plan.    Note: If you are not able to access the Draft shares button, check the Permissions and Roles page as you will need to have Legal Administrator permissions.  carta/public/11/images/1467852841912320369_qlj18mQglo1wHdf4FbHq_qHGfWAJ1OprsO5n0zmUnO0qSYRilq3Lq5rPi8FJ8IqnfrCDIwUl9KYPYGVaQHn-iNbuRliXs7jsR6xwzMxcett8j-OfkpF1AqFKEkxyjgBWdsKU5L3c",
        "originalText": "Navigate to Securities &gt; Equity Awards. In the RSAs tab, click Draft shares. These shares will be deducted from the equity plan.<br> <br> Note: If you are not able to access the Draft shares&nbsp;button, check the <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/corporate-permissions\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Permissions and Roles</a> page as you will need to have Legal Administrator permissions.<br> <img height=\"123\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/1467852841912320369_qlj18mQglo1wHdf4FbHq_qHGfWAJ1OprsO5n0zmUnO0qSYRilq3Lq5rPi8FJ8IqnfrCDIwUl9KYPYGVaQHn-iNbuRliXs7jsR6xwzMxcett8j-OfkpF1AqFKEkxyjgBWdsKU5L3c\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"436\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/11/images/1467852841912320369_qlj18mQglo1wHdf4FbHq_qHGfWAJ1OprsO5n0zmUnO0qSYRilq3Lq5rPi8FJ8IqnfrCDIwUl9KYPYGVaQHn-iNbuRliXs7jsR6xwzMxcett8j-OfkpF1AqFKEkxyjgBWdsKU5L3c"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click on the draft that you would like to edit, or click Add certificate.    NOTE: For shares that have been approved by the board but not purchased yet, choose Board approved under status. These shares will reduce the number of shares under the Equity Plan but will not be added to Shares Outstanding until they are purchased from the ledger once paid for by the holder, as described here.  carta/public/11/images/6052746258657145056_eDIzjKVzBSIx93mjz5nyIKFDcqRMu3k2TB82PkVFXl4lIb41OaE9AKZ5Rzd_tjyfqVHmxQdposQupI-5bjk12HeFIkmeDTAhNx7qWByDf8PQ5ZW26dyPR50-Al7HVSIVwSJ190eY",
