        "originalText": "Custom plan of platform features: Lists out the features with a brief description that is available for your use. If there is a feature that is not on the list, but you would like to subscribe to, you can reach out to your Account Manager if you have not had contact with your assigned Account Manager.<br> <img height=\"663\" src=\"carta/public/11/images/8466779623695398027_rVK-3uaghvLuu9vPZmKi85OjxHoyLgMZ8MmmHtz74clW3uVq3wn5qBxT8l_OLRA6S9ze00Myi2M47KPv9rSKQ_twDQP1UMxquaLtZjgYb58z6VjYtrIc6MxZUZBLUmtKX-1wCL8q\" width=\"619\">",
