{
  "id": "7322236511119831654",
  "subject": {
    "id": "7322236511119831654",
    "text": {
      "text": "How do I add a non-Carta 409A FMV?"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "6055121120130189893",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "Navigate to Compliance > 409A to enter a non-Carta determined fair market value (FMV) to the company’s account.  carta/public/13/images/48953841532143107_Ss6V1WH-oY3na8sU_DLH3iSbiEE6P8PEVTwtMa8TvOTx22-yb6ACbriQjqFQpx6j4t52wx7mrQgZh8PnJXFd9GKxzvlQN64_oNjljmoCUffrj4BTy_x8Vw6_k1rT_pHEQ29Fobo_=s0",
        "originalText": "Navigate to Compliance &gt; 409A to enter a non-Carta determined fair market value (FMV) to the company’s account.<br> <img height=\"211\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/48953841532143107_Ss6V1WH-oY3na8sU_DLH3iSbiEE6P8PEVTwtMa8TvOTx22-yb6ACbriQjqFQpx6j4t52wx7mrQgZh8PnJXFd9GKxzvlQN64_oNjljmoCUffrj4BTy_x8Vw6_k1rT_pHEQ29Fobo_=s0\" width=\"205\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/48953841532143107_Ss6V1WH-oY3na8sU_DLH3iSbiEE6P8PEVTwtMa8TvOTx22-yb6ACbriQjqFQpx6j4t52wx7mrQgZh8PnJXFd9GKxzvlQN64_oNjljmoCUffrj4BTy_x8Vw6_k1rT_pHEQ29Fobo_=s0"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click Manage fair market value and select Add fair market value.  carta/public/13/images/395843567750512190_k8NQQB3hlMfqux92xChuJVsccxf6r86TfSQL_liKN2l8XSZyvAbvarUyYsF82spWGizkKk2A2HPQLzvmj-TD9K_sm58VbYBRCoxoejHUj8GBB0Tmb1dM4he0T_ZRskapibGfr3kj=s0",
        "originalText": "Click Manage fair market value and select Add fair market value.<br> <img height=\"260\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/395843567750512190_k8NQQB3hlMfqux92xChuJVsccxf6r86TfSQL_liKN2l8XSZyvAbvarUyYsF82spWGizkKk2A2HPQLzvmj-TD9K_sm58VbYBRCoxoejHUj8GBB0Tmb1dM4he0T_ZRskapibGfr3kj=s0\" width=\"528\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/395843567750512190_k8NQQB3hlMfqux92xChuJVsccxf6r86TfSQL_liKN2l8XSZyvAbvarUyYsF82spWGizkKk2A2HPQLzvmj-TD9K_sm58VbYBRCoxoejHUj8GBB0Tmb1dM4he0T_ZRskapibGfr3kj=s0"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "In the modal, choose the valuation source and the FMV date range of the added FMV. If the account has multiple Common share classes, the FMV may need to be entered for each Common share class field. Upload a copy of the 409A report, as well.  carta/public/13/images/7915827303999519357_qzg5UGEMVwVrey8pGDvtJBRjDHRYiyL0STVOEklt-lkp__u47UtXQ_1MgIGw3aqM4L3Kaa2b_Kihpwy4QJuU397oiLb_TEmEjcU7aQ_9jqFJ0Jx4LBnZrymN_HZWVP8Pr1koyH8k=s0    If Non-Carta 409A is selected as the source, select the Valuation providerand Reason for non-Carta 409A from the drop down lists.  carta/public/13/images/114358394036037442_VLalSlLU3L7lxiYLJCOpXMo78jWSialpjPZDACOSJ6nyVMYSTP7S_8DFgE6TLc1UmY3sxB9CSvviT2D07th59Hga_LqpIXzUyWDfZ50ZwVvX0gjJLH90J1NPU9ly1t4IPf2ZYejj=s0",
        "originalText": "In the modal, choose the valuation source and the FMV date range of the added FMV. If the account has multiple Common share classes, the FMV may need to be entered for each Common share class field. Upload a copy of the 409A report, as well.<br> <img height=\"536\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/7915827303999519357_qzg5UGEMVwVrey8pGDvtJBRjDHRYiyL0STVOEklt-lkp__u47UtXQ_1MgIGw3aqM4L3Kaa2b_Kihpwy4QJuU397oiLb_TEmEjcU7aQ_9jqFJ0Jx4LBnZrymN_HZWVP8Pr1koyH8k=s0\" width=\"481\"><br> <br> If Non-Carta 409A is selected as the source, select the Valuation provider and Reason for non-Carta 409A from the drop down lists.<br> <img height=\"655\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/114358394036037442_VLalSlLU3L7lxiYLJCOpXMo78jWSialpjPZDACOSJ6nyVMYSTP7S_8DFgE6TLc1UmY3sxB9CSvviT2D07th59Hga_LqpIXzUyWDfZ50ZwVvX0gjJLH90J1NPU9ly1t4IPf2ZYejj=s0\" width=\"479\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/114358394036037442_VLalSlLU3L7lxiYLJCOpXMo78jWSialpjPZDACOSJ6nyVMYSTP7S_8DFgE6TLc1UmY3sxB9CSvviT2D07th59Hga_LqpIXzUyWDfZ50ZwVvX0gjJLH90J1NPU9ly1t4IPf2ZYejj=s0"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click Save and the newly added FMV can be seen from the 409A dashboard.  carta/public/13/images/3565048062434610486_plNPon0gNxr_sVaZuju4Tcmtg-h7e5755xb_sSutGLPR1ggExwChDjN9CNz1Ozh0-f-kG4tKN-S1f9fro-sGxtstgFvlKjloRaH-zGDiEezwJ0Mn4GMBtcZGGHNrXvQ6tj6iAJRB=s0",
        "originalText": "Click Save and the newly added FMV can be seen from the 409A dashboard.<br> <img height=\"285\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/3565048062434610486_plNPon0gNxr_sVaZuju4Tcmtg-h7e5755xb_sSutGLPR1ggExwChDjN9CNz1Ozh0-f-kG4tKN-S1f9fro-sGxtstgFvlKjloRaH-zGDiEezwJ0Mn4GMBtcZGGHNrXvQ6tj6iAJRB=s0\" width=\"534\"><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
