{
  "id": "-742408081500152564",
  "subject": {
    "id": "-742408081500152564",
    "text": {
      "text": "Pausing a Vesting Schedule"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "6828294284944199779",
    "text": {
      "text": "The most common reason a vesting schedule would need to be paused is due to a Leave of Absence. To pause a vesting schedule on a certificate, equity award, or warrant, the user will need to haveLegal Administrator permissions. Click here to learn more about the update to historical vesting for option grants.",
      "originalText": "The most common reason a vesting schedule would need to be paused is due to a Leave of Absence. To pause a vesting schedule on a certificate, equity award, or warrant, the user will need to have Legal Administrator permissions.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/pause-vesting#historical-vesting\"><u>Click here to learn more about the update to historical vesting for option grants</u></a>.<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "7652452674816363118",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "After logging into Carta, go to the Securities > Equity Awards page. This article is referencing an option grant as an example, but these steps can be replicated for other security types.  carta/public/13/images/7339421634031492142_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "After logging into Carta, go to the Securities &gt; Equity Awards page. This article is referencing an option grant as an example, but these steps can be replicated for other security types.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/7339421634031492142_rtaImage\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/7339421634031492142_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Search for the desired option grant, click the V drop-down to the right of the grant's row, and select Modify vesting schedule.  carta/public/13/images/8608221251963744005_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Search for the desired option grant, click the V drop-down to the right of the grant's row, and select Modify vesting schedule.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/8608221251963744005_rtaImage\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/8608221251963744005_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Create a custom vesting schedule by importing a standard schedule, or copying and pasting from Excel.  carta/public/13/images/3835459112586758646_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Create a custom vesting schedule by <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/import-a-standard-schedule\" target=\"_blank\">importing a standard schedule</a>, or <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/custom-vesting-schedule-excel\" target=\"_blank\"><u>copying and pasting from Excel</u>.</a><br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/3835459112586758646_rtaImage\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/3835459112586758646_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Commonly, since the vesting schedule would be paused for a few months, the method of importing a standard schedule is used more. Enter a vesting schedule name and confirm the vesting type and start date.  carta/public/13/images/1276212009369006277_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Commonly, since the vesting schedule would be paused for a few months, the method of importing a standard schedule is used more. Enter a vesting schedule name and confirm the vesting type and start date.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/1276212009369006277_rtaImage\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/1276212009369006277_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "For the periods where vesting is paused, zero out the number of options to vest. For example, the holder of option grant ES-13 will be on a leave of absence from Nov. 1 to Jan. 1, so period #5 through #7 will display 0 options to vest. Then those three periods will be added to the bottom of the vesting schedule so that the cumulative total is 100%.  carta/public/13/images/8106769604756370666_rtaImage  carta/public/13/images/5836065236503393459_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "For the periods where vesting is paused, zero out the number of options to vest. For example, the holder of option grant ES-13 will be on a leave of absence from Nov. 1 to Jan. 1, so period #5 through #7 will display 0 options to vest. Then those three periods will be added to the bottom of the vesting schedule so that the cumulative total is 100%.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/8106769604756370666_rtaImage\"><br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/5836065236503393459_rtaImage\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/5836065236503393459_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click Next: add modification reason. Add a brief description of the modification, which will be sent to the option holder if the option grant has been accepted, and click Next: review modifications.  carta/public/13/images/2113678546891065502_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Click Next: add modification reason. Add a brief description of the modification, which will be sent to the option holder if the option grant has been accepted, and click Next: review modifications.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/2113678546891065502_rtaImage\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/2113678546891065502_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Lastly, scroll to the bottom to Save vesting schedule.",
        "originalText": "Lastly, scroll to the bottom to Save vesting schedule."
      }]
    }
  }, {
    "id": "2661099669470099679",
