      "text": "Update - Historical Vesting for Option Grants",
      "originalText": " Update - Historical Vesting for Option Grants"
    },
    "signals": [{
      "valueL": "2"
    }]
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "5268371637168014008",
    "text": {
      "text": "The concept of historical vesting schedules has recently been introduced to vesting schedules applied to option grants on Carta. When a vesting schedule is modified for any reason (e.g. option partial cancellation, accelerated vesting, paused vesting, etc), another version of the option grant’s vesting schedule will be created with the effective date of the modification. The option grant’s previous vesting schedule is stored and linked to the new vesting schedule generated by the vesting modification.  This is an important concept because As-of date reporting in Carta has been updated to understand that option grants can have multiple vesting schedules. Here are some examples of the effective date of the new vesting schedule when a particular tool is used:",
      "originalText": "The concept of historical vesting schedules has recently been introduced to vesting schedules applied to option grants on Carta. When a vesting schedule is modified for any reason (e.g. <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/partially-cancel-option-grants\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><u>option partial cancellation</u></a>, <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/accelerate-vesting\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><u>accelerated vesting</u></a>, <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/pause-vesting\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><u>paused vesting</u></a>, etc), another version of the option grant’s vesting schedule will be created with the effective date of the modification. The option grant’s previous vesting schedule is stored and linked to the new vesting schedule generated by the vesting modification.<br><br>This is an important concept because As-of date reporting in Carta has been updated to understand that option grants can have multiple vesting schedules. Here are some examples of the effective date of the new vesting schedule when a particular tool is used:"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-5904815707014662385",
    "list": {
      "item": [{
        "text": "Partial cancellation tool: Entered by the user during the partial cancellation workflow",
        "originalText": "<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/partially-cancel-option-grants\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Partial cancellation tool</u></a>: Entered by the user during the partial cancellation workflow"
      }, {
        "text": "Modify vesting tool: Entry date of the modification (i.e. \"today's\" date)",
        "originalText": "<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/modify-a-vesting-schedule\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Modify vesting tool</u></a>: Entry date of the modification (i.e. \"today's\" date)"
      }, {
        "text": "Accelerate vesting tool: Entry date of the acceleration",
        "originalText": "<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/accelerate-vesting\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Accelerate vesting tool</u></a>: Entry date of the acceleration"
      }]
    }
