  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "7960794629864389546",
    "text": {
      "text": "Users withLegal Administratorpermissions can modify vesting schedules to accelerate vesting on securities. Click here to learn more about the update to historical vesting for option grants.",
      "originalText": "Users with Legal Administrator permissions can modify vesting schedules to accelerate vesting on securities.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/accelerate-vesting#historical-vesting\"><u>Click here to learn more about the update to historical vesting for option grants</u></a>.<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-2698928114477468226",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "To accelerate a vesting schedule, navigate to Securities > Equity Awardspage.",
        "originalText": "To accelerate a vesting schedule, navigate to Securities &gt; Equity Awards page.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Click on the Vdrop-down for the appropriate award. Select Accelerate Vesting.  carta/public/13/images/780637645346424191_rtaImage    NOTE: Accelerate vesting is not available for exercised grants or grants with milestone vesting schedules. Milestone vesting tranches are not automatically triggered, regardless of the vesting date. Because Milestones are simply text fields for vesting conditions, the Carta platform is not able to recognize that the vesting terms have been met. For these cases, submit a case via Carta's Help Center. Learn more about Carta's Help Center.",
        "originalText": "Click on the V&nbsp;drop-down&nbsp;for the appropriate award. Select Accelerate Vesting.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/780637645346424191_rtaImage\"><br> <br> NOTE: Accelerate vesting is not available for exercised grants or grants with milestone vesting schedules. Milestone vesting tranches are not automatically triggered, regardless of the vesting date. Because Milestones are simply text fields for vesting conditions, the Carta platform is not able to recognize that the vesting terms have been met. For these cases, submit a case via <a href=\"https://app.carta.com/profiles/update?help=true\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Carta's Help Center</u></a>. Learn more about <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/carta-help-center\" target=\"_blank\">Carta's Help Center</a>.<br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/780637645346424191_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Enter the Vesting acceleration date and Accelerated quantity.  As you enter the quantity, you will be able to preview the schedule. The schedule will automatically calculate and create a modified vesting schedule. Accelerated quantity will be pulled from the following consecutive tranches until the last modified tranche shows the remaining balance from the original vesting schedule.  carta/public/13/images/930744520705760365_rtaImageThe checked tranches indicate vested tranches.The tranches shaded in blue indicate the updated tranches.The tranches shaded in green indicate a new tranche added to the schedule.",
        "originalText": "Enter the Vesting acceleration date&nbsp;and Accelerated quantity.<br> As you enter the quantity, you will be able to preview the schedule. The schedule will automatically calculate and create a modified vesting schedule. Accelerated quantity will be pulled from the following consecutive tranches until the last modified tranche shows the remaining balance from the original vesting schedule.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/930744520705760365_rtaImage\">  The checked tranches indicate vested tranches. The tranches shaded in blue indicate the updated tranches. The tranches shaded in green indicate a new tranche added to the schedule.  <br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/930744520705760365_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click Next: add acceleration reason at the bottom of the popup to add the modification reason, then save the acceleration. The schedule title is automatically noted as \"Accelerated.\"  carta/public/13/images/9037885953894523182_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Click Next: add acceleration reason at the bottom of the popup to add the modification reason, then save the acceleration. The schedule title is automatically noted as \"Accelerated.\"<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/9037885953894523182_rtaImage\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/9037885953894523182_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "You can review the accelerated vesting schedule in the vesting schedule tab of the security details.  carta/public/13/images/266592271185903043_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "You can review the accelerated vesting schedule in the vesting schedule tab of the security details.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/266592271185903043_rtaImage\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/266592271185903043_rtaImage"
        }
      }]
    }
  }, {
