        }
      }, {
        "text": "You will be able to choose one of the vesting schedules from your library by clicking on the drop-down for Schedule or you can create a custom schedule, shown here. You can also modify the vesting start date, early exercisability, or you can include acceleration language.    To modify the vesting start-date of a custom schedule, you will need to modify each tranche's vesting date from the Create a custom schedulebuilder.  carta/public/13/images/7079055275438550953_oNbjIoOa-xi7VSLMqnps_uA7tVGWcMh8hDFD3_HWT-9p3H2T7iAFZOFHZt2dh5RfsDbXFAzjbfCh2ycFKU-9mEG7caqAAqVRIQ95CitcHUurMwb6vGONjFswVttJId_eAyPEWIoy    After making the necessary changes, click Next: add modification reason.",
