        "originalText": "Review the changes made and click Save vesting schedule at the bottom.<br> <img height=\"710\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/696792172477359612_nDlp_wZ8NtVw9x20qpO4p-eoTY0PCz4GpkS4MSvZVdfesOWMn25WgKRUuDnwIb4gJIWJx9j6HtsD3HJrUreLf3-61UYKBXyGIp_54FAvG0565GFMMLkDNRhXC87ro57t67Q7psZO\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"339\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
