        }
      }, {
        "text": "After saving the vesting schedule modifications, an email will be sent to the officer and security holder if the security has been signed and accepted by all parties. If the security has been signed by the officer and not accepted by the holder, then only the officer will receive the email notification. If the security has not been signed by the officer, then no email will be sent out.",
