{
  "id": "-2002366817317198450",
  "subject": {
    "id": "-2002366817317198450",
    "text": {
      "text": "Why we need stakeholder email addresses"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-4322476513265445962",
    "text": {
      "text": "Carta asks for companies to provide their stakeholders' email addresses in order to invite company officers to log in, sign their electronic issuances, and to invite equity stakeholders to accept securities.",
      "originalText": "Carta asks for companies to provide their stakeholders' email addresses in order to invite company officers to log in, sign their electronic issuances, and to invite equity stakeholders to accept securities.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-5522705893000602786",
    "text": {
      "text": "Email addresses make sure that the correct stakeholders have electronic access to their equity in your company. It is also the primary means for holders to receive notices about company events, equity events and keep their contact information accurate and up-to-date. The email address should be for the specific stakeholder even if they do not check their email frequently. At the very least, it needs to be the email address of an individual who has power-of-attorney to receive legal documents on behalf of the security holder. If this is the case, then the company should have verification of the power-of-attorney before they send out any securities. If the security holder is a minor (under the age of 18), then the email address used should be that of the minor's legal guardian.",
      "originalText": "Email addresses make sure that the correct stakeholders have electronic access to their equity in your company.&nbsp;It is also the primary means for holders to receive notices about company events, equity events and keep their contact information accurate and up-to-date.&nbsp;The email address should be for the specific stakeholder even if they do not check their email frequently.&nbsp;At the very least, it needs to be the email address of an individual who has power-of-attorney to receive legal documents on behalf of the security holder. If this is the case, then the company should have verification of the power-of-attorney before they send out any securities.&nbsp;If the security holder is a minor (under the age of 18), then the email address used should be that of the minor's legal guardian.<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "8447336966494516525",
    "text": {
      "text": "Since Carta is a live self-service platform, each stakeholder on the cap table will be notified to accept their securities on Carta. Upon receiving this notification, the holders will be able to create their own account on Carta (under the email provided by the company or a different personal email).",
      "originalText": "Since Carta is a live self-service platform, each stakeholder on the cap table will be notified to accept their securities on Carta. Upon receiving this notification, the holders will be able to create their own account on Carta (under the email provided by the company or a different personal email).<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "6990008319038336206",
    "text": {
      "text": "In Carta, there are two places you can see the email information for your stakeholders.",
      "originalText": "In Carta, there are two places you can see the email information for your stakeholders.&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "6944403122203709308",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "Stakeholders > All Stakeholders: This ledger lists the email address that the company input upon sending the security.",
        "originalText": "Stakeholders &gt; All Stakeholders: This ledger lists the email address that the company input upon sending the security.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Stakeholder contact spreadsheet in Capitalization > Reporting: This will show the email address that users used to accept their securities on Carta.  carta/public/13/images/5458069126293682553_HlO3iW6wJFu5MeuOQEPZNWk83WdOHkkYAFRqtCKJSuCIiMvQye3NY9SO9i0jn3GPmvU6ZqNiusBSL7PwD_Psf4Vc1kt6fn2fd7azv6hLjU5yT1IrpUZTAFPeTEQ8C0SIjFxexgah",
        "originalText": "Stakeholder contact spreadsheet in Capitalization &gt; Reporting: This will show the email address that users used to accept their securities on Carta.<br> <img height=\"121\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/5458069126293682553_HlO3iW6wJFu5MeuOQEPZNWk83WdOHkkYAFRqtCKJSuCIiMvQye3NY9SO9i0jn3GPmvU6ZqNiusBSL7PwD_Psf4Vc1kt6fn2fd7azv6hLjU5yT1IrpUZTAFPeTEQ8C0SIjFxexgah\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"383\">",
