  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "9210524168025146906",
    "text": {
      "text": "Company users set as the Option exercise approver role are able to individually review the submitted online option exercise requests and historical option exercises from the Transactions > Exercises page on Carta.",
      "originalText": "Company users set as the <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/editing-option-exercise-approver\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><u><i>Option exercise approver</i> role</u></a> are able to individually review the submitted online option exercise requests and historical option exercises from the <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/exercise-ledger\" target=\"_blank\"><u><i>Transactions &gt; Exercises</i> page</u></a> on Carta."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-384456639449515112",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "After an optionholder initiates an exercise through their portfolio, the designated option exercise approver will receive an email to approve the pending exercise. If no option exercise approver has been selected, the exercise will default to the Equity award signatory to accept. However, the funds will not begin transferring until the exercise is approved.  carta/public/13/images/4872995678904255735_GnB1jaC5sylyCUX_CLM413YbRTCGHlHFM_UwQrVtpy0fAXNZNCercPMzQHZI-xCmHtkUsMm7cPgQGxCaomKyNN8zvO2wLTzzrzBl5YY3StTeYh0muSjPMj2vrTxTuMxSiSmbgbnx",
        "originalText": "After an optionholder <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/exercising-options-on-carta\" target=\"_blank\"><u>initiates an exercise through their portfolio</u></a>, the <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/editing-option-exercise-approver\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><u>designated option exercise approver</u></a> will receive an email to approve the pending exercise. If no option exercise approver has been selected, the exercise will default to the Equity award signatory to accept. However, the funds will not begin transferring until the exercise is approved.<br> <img height=\"579\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/4872995678904255735_GnB1jaC5sylyCUX_CLM413YbRTCGHlHFM_UwQrVtpy0fAXNZNCercPMzQHZI-xCmHtkUsMm7cPgQGxCaomKyNN8zvO2wLTzzrzBl5YY3StTeYh0muSjPMj2vrTxTuMxSiSmbgbnx\" width=\"287\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/4872995678904255735_GnB1jaC5sylyCUX_CLM413YbRTCGHlHFM_UwQrVtpy0fAXNZNCercPMzQHZI-xCmHtkUsMm7cPgQGxCaomKyNN8zvO2wLTzzrzBl5YY3StTeYh0muSjPMj2vrTxTuMxSiSmbgbnx"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Log into your Carta account. Review the task to approve the exercise(s) initiated via ACH or wire. In addition, users added to the company’s Account users page have access to the Exercises ledger by navigating to Transactions > Exercises.  carta/public/13/images/1783728526011580263_tZ298qqq6ybX0_SdE3eS37UNxz0jji7du9uNoQEpQcROKrNMOLH-ldXCobu7phIGCIMbPofOfsiVIVHZF1UMYsLJktx8aiP0HLEbeaU9coZ8poGfM7MZlLZTpD_WgSW35Egohf4g",
        "originalText": "Log into your <a href=\"https://login.app.carta.com/\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Carta</u></a> account. Review the task to approve the exercise(s) initiated via <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/exercising-options-on-carta\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><u>ACH</u></a> or <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/exercising-via-wire\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><u>wire</u></a>. In addition, users added to the company’s <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/corporate-permissions\" target=\"_blank\"><u><i>Account users</i> page</u></a> have access to the <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/exercise-ledger\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><u><i>Exercises</i> ledger</u></a> by navigating to Transactions &gt; Exercises.<br> <img height=\"114\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/1783728526011580263_tZ298qqq6ybX0_SdE3eS37UNxz0jji7du9uNoQEpQcROKrNMOLH-ldXCobu7phIGCIMbPofOfsiVIVHZF1UMYsLJktx8aiP0HLEbeaU9coZ8poGfM7MZlLZTpD_WgSW35Egohf4g\" width=\"529\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/1783728526011580263_tZ298qqq6ybX0_SdE3eS37UNxz0jji7du9uNoQEpQcROKrNMOLH-ldXCobu7phIGCIMbPofOfsiVIVHZF1UMYsLJktx8aiP0HLEbeaU9coZ8poGfM7MZlLZTpD_WgSW35Egohf4g"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "The Exercises ledger provides a summary of all exercises that have been submitted and pending approval, as well as a count of pending 83(b) elections for early exercises.  Read more about the Exercises ledger here.  carta/public/13/images/1132484949472616351_PMAc_JE1yq8D1bCFZ_xg6jLIdeX_jt-_fbfudh7LiNIx3XK8UkMC8kAuOgdSr60dTmlhP0wPbJY_W0DdtMCG43M5bbGrcffglKMAOmsxao6qz3iE93hGPUPWGS1cRnSZJcCjJk2L",
        "originalText": "The Exercises ledger provides a summary of all exercises that have been submitted and pending approval, as well as a count of pending 83(b) elections for early exercises.<br> <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/exercise-ledger\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Read more about the <i>Exercises</i> ledger here</u></a>.<br> <img height=\"125\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/1132484949472616351_PMAc_JE1yq8D1bCFZ_xg6jLIdeX_jt-_fbfudh7LiNIx3XK8UkMC8kAuOgdSr60dTmlhP0wPbJY_W0DdtMCG43M5bbGrcffglKMAOmsxao6qz3iE93hGPUPWGS1cRnSZJcCjJk2L\" width=\"523\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
