        "originalText": " To review a pending exercise request to approve, click the V dropdown to the right of the request’s row and select Review exercise request.<br> <img height=\"64\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/7759309150674280850_0FtaBUnmU8AIFcVRwQnMGcK5sCOkN1Uplvm__rstZSVx_thfFYlgfSp3mF-L9FSoCSWqnlMrCU-pHBfWZEPjqqbUWJSLuzIUzmZWdI04pzExuiQrb-aoBertmJxKE1oFbXdHo4c6\" width=\"530\">",
