        }
      }, {
        "text": "Once the exercise is reviewed, the option exercise approver will type their name to sign, then click Save.  carta/public/13/images/9044928067370336766_DTVhTeKVosO8Q0KvJoTW7JyR0hILGFhdjWvakSz2Vbwgv2bjKsHlFnX6yXh6ro31FnEI408gI0fPtkEJAwL72mzZw9XZQ7qH9duD-fG7qqPnHqzG9c3Q2U4lG3iA3BYGNRKnJRiw",
        "originalText": "Once the exercise is reviewed, the option exercise approver will type their name to sign, then click Save.<br> <img height=\"227\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/9044928067370336766_DTVhTeKVosO8Q0KvJoTW7JyR0hILGFhdjWvakSz2Vbwgv2bjKsHlFnX6yXh6ro31FnEI408gI0fPtkEJAwL72mzZw9XZQ7qH9duD-fG7qqPnHqzG9c3Q2U4lG3iA3BYGNRKnJRiw\" width=\"527\"><br> &nbsp;",
