        }
      }, {
        "text": "If the holder’s bank approves the ACH, the exercise will be processed.  The transfer of funds process is complete in 5-7 business days. Review the funds transfer here for US options exercises and for non-US option exercises.",
        "originalText": "If the holder’s bank approves the ACH, the exercise will be processed.<br> The transfer of funds process is complete in 5-7 business days. Review the funds transfer here for <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/fund-transfer-workflow\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><u>US options exercises</u></a> and for <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/non-us-fund-transfer-workflow\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><u>non-US option exercises</u></a>.<br> &nbsp;"
