  "linked": [{
    "id": "205569071679066240",
    "text": {
      "text": "This new tool that allows companies to adjust tax withholding amounts after an exercise has been approved by the option exercise approver or if an exercise has been reflected manually.  The tax withholding adjustment will not replace the original tax withholding amounts entered upon approving the exercise request, but a history will be available via reporting in the near future.  NOTE:",
      "originalText": "This new tool that allows companies to adjust tax withholding amounts after an exercise has been approved by the <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/editing-option-exercise-approver\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><u>option exercise approver</u></a> or if an exercise has been <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/exercising-manually\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><u>reflected manually</u></a>.<br><br>The tax withholding adjustment will not replace the original tax withholding amounts entered upon approving the exercise request, but a history will be available via reporting in the near future.<br><br>NOTE:"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-3628059663519011798",
    "list": {
      "item": [{
        "text": "Only existing tax types set up in the Tax rules page can be added during the adjustment workflow. If a new tax type needs to be added to an exercise, add the tax rule in the Compliance > Tax rules page prior to making adjustments to the approved exercise.",
        "originalText": "Only existing tax types set up in the <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/manage-tax-withholding\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><u><i>Tax rules</i> page</u></a> can be added during the adjustment workflow. If a new tax type needs to be added to an exercise, add the tax rule in the Compliance &gt; Tax rules page prior to making adjustments to the approved exercise.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "For all tax adjustments using the Adjust taxes tool on Carta, any funds transfer (refund or requests for additional funds) must be completed off the Carta platform.",
