      "text": "Adding and Modifying an Additional Email"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-3287444555540016292",
    "text": {
      "text": "Additional emails are required upon account registration to assist the user with providing a secondary login email in case access is lost to the primary email address. For example, an employee creating a Carta account with their work email address, but after they have departed, they will lose access to their work email. It is recommended to add a personal email address as theadditional email, so the account can be accessed after company departure.  NOTE: When adding an additional email, you may receive an error stating \"Something went wrong\" or a generic error to \"Contact Support\". To troubleshoot for most cases, the message appears when attempting to add an email that has already been used to create a Carta account. If you would like to use that email address to access your portfolio, you can add that email as an additional email to your Carta account as described in this article. If needed, you can merge your Carta accounts.",
      "originalText": "Additional emails&nbsp;are required upon <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/account-registration\" target=\"_blank\"><u>account registration</u></a> to assist the user with providing a secondary login email in case access is lost to the primary email address. For example, an employee creating a Carta account with their work email address, but after they have departed, they will lose access to their work email. It is recommended to add a personal email address as the additional email, so the account can be accessed after company departure.<br><br>NOTE:&nbsp;When adding an additional email, you may receive an error stating \"Something went wrong\" or a generic error to \"Contact Support\". To troubleshoot for most cases, the message appears when attempting to add an email that has already been used to create a Carta account. If you would like to use that email address to access your portfolio, you can add that email as an additional email to your Carta account as described in this article. If needed, you can <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/merging-multiple-carta-accounts\" target=\"_blank\"><u>merge your Carta accounts</u></a>."
    }
