      "originalText": "<br>Carta supports over 90 HRIS and Payroll providers for our Carta Total Compensation product. These integrations will support existing stakeholder updates and terminations in the future.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/total-comp#integrate-hris\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Learn more about HRIS integrations for Total Compensation</u></a>.<br>&nbsp;<br>Carta supports native API integrations with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/how-carta-workday-integrate\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Workday</u></a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/how-carta-namely-integrate\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Namely</u></a>, and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/how-carta-bamboohr-integrate\" target=\"_blank\"><u>BambooHR</u></a>&nbsp;to flag&nbsp;<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/update-stakeholder-details\" target=\"_blank\"><u>existing stakeholder updates and terminations</u></a>.<br>&nbsp;<br>For Enterprise customers, Carta also supports&nbsp;<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/flat-file-hris-integrations\" target=\"_blank\"><u>flat file integrations</u></a>&nbsp;with HR and Payroll providers that support automatic report uploads via STFP. Contact your Carta Account Manager for&nbsp;access to this feature."
