        "originalText": "<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/exercising-options-on-carta\" target=\"_blank\">Exercise options on Carta using ACH</a>  Connect your bank account instantly via Plaid in the workflow. However, if you need to connect your bank account manually or cannot find your bank in the list via Plaid, <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/set-bank-account\" target=\"_blank\">here are steps to connect your bank account</a> prior to exercising. See a <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/exercising-as-an-option-holder#ach-video\"><u>video tutorial</u></a> of the ACH workflow at the bottom of this article.  "
      }, {
