        "text": "If a holder or company administrator did not receive the email notification about the security, the email can be resent through Carta. Select the securities that need to be resent, click Actions, and select Resend emails.  carta/public/13/images/231139287624869393_dZoD2ysQetlhZFdLHI7Q5yFZj9jE1pwtBQlZ2KDP2ETaG0GFZPNqufJVFxiGpgsImZ1aK585_mVZu74Snff_cc-Hj7Y2cO_YPkleq8amd7gKy4WVT2raTgmox65tLsYpOWB4D47J",
        "originalText": "If a holder or company administrator did not receive the email notification about the security, the email can be resent through Carta. Select the securities that need to be resent, click Actions, and select Resend emails.<br> <img height=\"182\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/231139287624869393_dZoD2ysQetlhZFdLHI7Q5yFZj9jE1pwtBQlZ2KDP2ETaG0GFZPNqufJVFxiGpgsImZ1aK585_mVZu74Snff_cc-Hj7Y2cO_YPkleq8amd7gKy4WVT2raTgmox65tLsYpOWB4D47J\" width=\"433\"><br> &nbsp;",
