      "text": "Exercise Options on Carta via Wire (Legacy)"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "1328758047988463111",
    "text": {
      "text": "Non-US option holders of private US companies can exercise through Carta via wire transfer. This is an old flow that will be deprecated soon. Refer to this workflow for non-US optionholders to exercise their options.",
      "originalText": "Non-US option holders of private US companies can exercise through Carta via wire transfer. This is an old flow that will be deprecated soon. <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/exercise-options-via-wire\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Refer to this workflow</u></a> for non-US optionholders to exercise their options.<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "580967905839055284",
    "text": {
      "text": "NOTE: The wire transfer will need to be completed outside of Carta through your banking provider. Cartadoes not wire the funds. Once the funds are wired to the company, the company exercise approver will confirm the payment is received and will issue a stock certificate for you through Carta. The date that Carta confirms the exercise funds will be the exercise date. Learn more.",
      "originalText": "NOTE: The wire transfer will need to be completed outside of Carta through your banking provider. Carta does not wire the funds. Once the funds are wired to the company, the company exercise approver will confirm the payment is received and will issue a stock certificate for you through Carta. The date that Carta&nbsp;confirms the exercise funds&nbsp;will be the exercise date. <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/why-this-exercise-date\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Learn more</u></a>.<br>&nbsp;"
    }
