  "linked": [{
    "id": "6977363425596804162",
    "list": {
      "item": [{
        "text": "Historical financials: Information about the company's last twelve month revenue and EBITDA (earnings before interest, taxes, depreciation, and amortization) as well as the previous twelve months revenue and EBITDA. Since the 409A valuation is a valuation of the company at a point in time, the data used is as of a specific date.    For example, Meetly conducted their 409A valuation as of 03/01/2019 (this is their valuation date). For the historical financials, the company provided the last twelve months (03/01/2018-2/28/2019) and the previous last twelve months (03/01/2017-02/28/2018).",
        "originalText": "Historical financials: Information about the company's last twelve month revenue and EBITDA (earnings before interest, taxes, depreciation, and amortization) as well as the previous twelve months revenue and EBITDA. Since the 409A valuation is a valuation of the company at a point in time, the data used is as of a specific date.<br> <br> For example, Meetly conducted their 409A valuation as of 03/01/2019 (this is their valuation date). For the historical financials, the company provided the last twelve months (03/01/2018-2/28/2019) and the previous last twelve months (03/01/2017-02/28/2018).<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Summary financial forecast: In addition to their historical financials, the company will also share the projected next twelve month's revenue and EBITDA. Using the same example above, this would mean Meetly has shared 03/01/2019-02/29/2020 financial projections for revenue and EBITDA.",
        "originalText": "Summary financial forecast: In addition to their historical financials, the company will also share the projected next twelve month's revenue and EBITDA. Using the same example above, this would mean Meetly has shared 03/01/2019-02/29/2020 financial projections for revenue and EBITDA.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Cash and Debt: The company will also share the cash and debt balances as of their valuation date. In the example above, this would mean Meetly has shared their cash and debt balances as of 03/01/2019.",
        "originalText": "Cash and Debt: The company will also share the cash and debt balances as of their valuation date. In the example above, this would mean Meetly has shared their cash and debt balances as of 03/01/2019.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Summary level ownership information: Some cap table information will also be made available, which includes access to share class level information but will not contain any information about share holders. Here's what you'll see as an investor:  carta/public/13/images/5138035882690049120_8-bNs29hzfa03WwKKxqPq8dipA-e1MWI6_E3Rg6Ucx5nZw9ywPqN5yIv7ibw4bp3Y6OHw1-VxD03CUniohjILKvLM6FYxC2uygRqbgesLxhQM3xxjkSJHNZxhFgGWEmxlP-yZvCP",
        "originalText": "Summary level ownership information: Some cap table information will also be made available, which includes access to share class level information but will not contain any information about share holders. Here's what you'll see as an investor:<br> <img height=\"145\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/5138035882690049120_8-bNs29hzfa03WwKKxqPq8dipA-e1MWI6_E3Rg6Ucx5nZw9ywPqN5yIv7ibw4bp3Y6OHw1-VxD03CUniohjILKvLM6FYxC2uygRqbgesLxhQM3xxjkSJHNZxhFgGWEmxlP-yZvCP\" width=\"527\"><br> &nbsp;",
