{
  "id": "-7766476356399308490",
  "subject": {
    "id": "-7766476356399308490",
    "text": {
      "text": "FAQs",
      "originalText": " FAQs"
    },
    "signals": [{
      "valueL": "2"
    }]
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-8378077894431475342",
    "text": {
      "text": "Can I revert sharing settings? Reverting sharing settings is not currently supported. Reach out to Carta Support if data was shared with someone that it should not have been shared with.",
      "originalText": "Can I revert sharing settings?<br>Reverting sharing settings is not currently supported. Reach out to <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/carta-help-center\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Carta Support</u></a> if data was shared with someone that it should not have been shared with.<br>&nbsp;"
    },
    "signals": [{
      "key": "FontBolded",
      "valueB": true
    }]
  }, {
    "id": "3919386057811213028",
    "text": {
      "text": "Can I share with more investors? Yes, you can always go back and share with more investors. To do this, revisit the sharing settings by going toCompliance > 409A and finding the valuation you wish to share. Use the drop down menu to the right of the valuation and selectShare information. carta/public/13/images/5372188204123399122_qIQVghHN3k-FT2_tajvt7I-N6SZ6jYjN2-HImobNGzu1O6NkxbK0dsEZLeHRAyGHTLEOFh8nhFAYpNAtru0IfRM_Oc82NMtZ3rXtNOsoWQy501E1xqaU8vGl5qkVhBi7S5djjb3u",
      "originalText": "Can I share with more investors?<br>Yes, you can always go back and share with more investors. To do this, revisit the sharing settings by going to Compliance &gt; 409A and finding the valuation you wish to share. Use the drop down menu to the right of the valuation and select Share information.<br><img height=\"439\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/5372188204123399122_qIQVghHN3k-FT2_tajvt7I-N6SZ6jYjN2-HImobNGzu1O6NkxbK0dsEZLeHRAyGHTLEOFh8nhFAYpNAtru0IfRM_Oc82NMtZ3rXtNOsoWQy501E1xqaU8vGl5qkVhBi7S5djjb3u\" width=\"486\"><br>&nbsp;",
      "associatedImage": {
        "url": "carta/public/13/images/5372188204123399122_qIQVghHN3k-FT2_tajvt7I-N6SZ6jYjN2-HImobNGzu1O6NkxbK0dsEZLeHRAyGHTLEOFh8nhFAYpNAtru0IfRM_Oc82NMtZ3rXtNOsoWQy501E1xqaU8vGl5qkVhBi7S5djjb3u"
      }
    },
    "signals": [{
      "key": "FontBolded",
      "valueB": true
    }]
  }, {
    "id": "-2757387431748371238",
    "text": {
      "text": "Can I share with investors later? Yes, you do not need to share immediately after approving your 409A valuation and can revisit this setting later.",
      "originalText": "Can I share with investors later?<br>Yes, you do not need to share immediately after approving your 409A valuation and can revisit this setting later.<br>&nbsp;"
    },
    "signals": [{
      "key": "FontBolded",
      "valueB": true
    }]
  }, {
    "id": "-3293523109667530790",
    "text": {
      "text": "Why should I share this with investors? Larger investors will often need to conduct a valuation of your company periodically. This is called an ASC 820 valuation which helps the investor establish the fair value of their holdings in your company. They use this information to put together financial statements and to help them understand how each of their funds are performing from an investment standpoint. In addition to this, sharing information about your company’s financial position can help the investment team understand how they can be most helpful in supporting your company.",
      "originalText": "Why should I share this with investors?<br>Larger investors will often need to conduct a valuation of your company periodically. This is called an ASC 820 valuation which helps the investor establish the fair value of their holdings in your company. They use this information to put together financial statements and to help them understand how each of their funds are performing from an investment standpoint. In addition to this, sharing information about your company’s financial position can help the investment team understand how they can be most helpful in supporting your company.<br>&nbsp;"
    },
    "signals": [{
      "key": "FontBolded",
      "valueB": true
    }]
  }, {
    "id": "4347251904053474765",
    "text": {
      "text": "Can I share only some data and not all? Sharing only some of the data is not supported today. Reach out to Carta Support for requests to share only some of the data.",
      "originalText": "Can I share only some data and not all?<br>Sharing only some of the data is not supported today. Reach out to <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/carta-help-center\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Carta Support</u></a> for requests to share only some of the data."
    },
    "signals": [{
      "key": "FontBolded",
      "valueB": true
    }]
  }]
}

