        "originalText": "Navigate to Compliance &gt; Expense accounting and in the Manage Assumptions tab.<br> <img height=\"168\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/5546808328503086272_Oyq8FHpibL3b4DMRePDn1sKvkIqYhwPrPWnOO-iP9Kmf2RBfZudswxfSjK-PFNuBcmPPPp0KrtV3WE2tnCd5BCILojdR4sNmDgiAxrx9BXBiCGOZH2qw0H863X6hdev1M8j9JO2K\" width=\"444\">",
