        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click the blue Actions button and select Edit expense detail.  carta/public/13/images/8941214850847419791_9LXcitIArV9hdLfGPQ46l8Bhio4fPSZrryS9FSNXfANx_dO4Z3Q6LEf40RkCIO28zjwGpdjTrZoAkIokj9fgAz3b8iouyJHaOJiTy3X2VNIESNw71UUWBddsrIgUKXQ4UEsPlY-4",
