  }, {
    "id": "8687058868544114519",
    "text": {
      "text": "If you need assistance calculating the interest rate and volatility based on your custom term assumption or would like to upload multiple custom assumptions for the awards by using a bulk assumptions importer, submit a case via Carta's Help Center. Learn more about Carta's Help Center.",
