        "originalText": "Click Actions, then Edit plan details.<br> <img height=\"135\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/7980048287691980068_srjkHc_0YsqV-4dnWTk4ifeykoZ8kW87nyq8ryFTIaswrUK2A5SvfM4HGmbTKTZP8HkcYqP1_qi_DV08wokgE0icdVhtly-HlAK9cjMxKNrxvkRv7DjBa9sudBm6-91zp8wUIIID\" width=\"430\">",
