        }
      }, {
        "text": "Scroll to the bottom to update the repurchase period. Changes to these fields will only apply to future issuances.  carta/public/13/images/8567801708021492648_1UZpNwSFr8wiBvkdBsFHXI_Xzx-AyU8-yODB-1UUrLqPviXZBVpfEP7sdlXNYogH2V2gzx-hLq76_j-xeixqPnZBHuw-DOHcyUQrtgLn_xcNDMZG2COiGpKF0Rc-jUOKX2gdpl2A",
