        "originalText": "After you submit your request, the issuing company will approve your exercise. Your company’s approval will then allow you to access wire instructions within Carta via the Wire funds task in app, or through your email.<br> <img height=\"376\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/5918337573135634701_E4-xc9FRS19ASzIPiWAmHrj4VPkb5ddJJdCs_R8EhW07ggzVTUiwh8LnxlGnm-NWyl5R_2k3cNk6GEBckGfUnYbVGlRt3XoPdpFoxLfCRpOnh53XD8YG-NQ3MYHAJk4-krnLEgfL\" width=\"209\"><img height=\"365\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/1938066786867348529_CouKY3aUYwR5hr-mfuSPHXJchgZMl1GdVY_6FPKM9187JoIN-nA-tVVP5-Q0pgY-XYH_zBwmDi4CkpLE6Otf5Ki_WpHToh0_b-VicrOkTs0MullZ_9eAQXWMzzKfL8vpADzwRinb\" width=\"215\"><br> &nbsp;",
