        "originalText": "Click Upload documents &gt; Divide PDF.<br> <img height=\"215\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/1089461170983234731_8sK0Gxn9deZ06mqeDDeQ4xS2kV29eMHlsYMrfngqy8nx5MNYwvVfKfRUfsS5N8Sk3v3NO76Ed94ue0_dQ1r6TnZXrzjxw16cCaDh0DrkE3melidJmFnm2AanMLhuEaiL7leunVag\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"494\">",
