        "text": "Both the Partner and Unique Identifier columns will be pre-populated when you download the template.",
        "originalText": "Both the Partner and Unique Identifier columns will be pre-populated when you download the template."
      }, {
        "text": "The Unique identifier is the text will be looked for when the importer is scanning the document. The exact Partner name in the document is a good unique identifier in most cases.",
