  }, {
    "id": "-6962111207220410082",
    "text": {
      "text": "You can add non-Carta board approved fair market values to the 409a page by following the directions here.",
      "originalText": "You can add non-Carta board approved fair market values to the 409a page by following the directions <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/add-a-fair-market-value\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "1859316071234510095",
    "text": {
      "text": "In addition, you can edit, delete, or add FMV’s specific to expense reporting purposes at anytime, even after reports are generated. All of these changes can be made directly on the fair market values table in yourSettings underCompliance >> Expense reporting.",
      "originalText": "In addition, you can edit, delete, or add FMV’s specific to expense reporting purposes at anytime, even after reports are generated. All of these changes can be made directly on the fair market values table in your Settings&nbsp;under Compliance &gt;&gt; Expense reporting."
