  }, {
    "id": "2014873329969069262",
    "text": {
      "text": "Note that in order to successfully generate the expense report, you will need to make sure that a FMV is listed on this page that covers the date of the earliest issued award. For companies that did not obtain a 409a valuation facilitated by a third-party provider at this early stage, a board approved FMV is sufficient. You can add additional FMV's for expensing purposes here using the green + option or delete FMVs that do not apply.",
      "originalText": "Note that in order to successfully generate the expense report, you will need to make sure that a FMV is listed on this page that covers the date of the earliest issued award. For companies that did not obtain&nbsp;a 409a valuation facilitated by a third-party provider at this early stage, a board approved FMV is sufficient. You can add additional FMV's for expensing purposes here using the green + option or delete FMVs that do not apply."
