        "text": "Support PIN - a 6 digit PIN requested upon calling into Carta Support to verify the user’s identity. This PIN will need to be refreshed while on call with Carta Support as the PIN as it is only valid for five minutes. Click the Refresh button next to the Support PIN to generate a new number. In addition, a new PIN is generated when visiting this help modal.",
        "originalText": "Support PIN - a 6 digit PIN requested upon calling into Carta Support to verify the user’s identity. This PIN will need to be refreshed while on call with Carta Support as the PIN as it is only valid for five minutes. Click the Refresh button next to the Support PIN to generate a new number. In addition, a new PIN is generated when visiting this help modal."
      }, {
        "text": "Access PIN - a 10 key PIN, consisting of randomly generated letters and numbers, requested when Carta Support would like access to the user’s company account, investment firm, or portfolio. The Access PIN may need to be refreshed when first accessed and when requested by Carta Support. Click the Refresh button next to the Access PIN to generate a new PIN.",
        "originalText": "Access PIN - a&nbsp;10 key PIN,&nbsp;consisting of randomly generated letters and numbers, requested when Carta Support would like access to the user’s company account, investment firm, or portfolio. The Access PIN may need to be refreshed when first accessed and when requested by Carta Support. Click the Refresh button next to the Access PIN to generate a new PIN."
