    "text": {
      "text": "Issue Restricted Stock Awards (RSAs)"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "7544735274059311933",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "Navigate to Securities > Equity Awards. In the RSAs tab, click Draft shares. These shares will be deducted from the equity plan.    Note: If you are not able to access the Draft shares button, check the Permissions and Roles page as you will need to have Legal Administrator permissions.  carta/public/13/images/1467852841912320369_qlj18mQglo1wHdf4FbHq_qHGfWAJ1OprsO5n0zmUnO0qSYRilq3Lq5rPi8FJ8IqnfrCDIwUl9KYPYGVaQHn-iNbuRliXs7jsR6xwzMxcett8j-OfkpF1AqFKEkxyjgBWdsKU5L3c",
        "originalText": "Navigate to Securities &gt; Equity Awards. In the RSAs tab, click Draft shares. These shares will be deducted from the equity plan.<br> <br> Note: If you are not able to access the Draft shares&nbsp;button, check the <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/corporate-permissions\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Permissions and Roles</a> page as you will need to have Legal Administrator permissions.<br> <img height=\"123\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/1467852841912320369_qlj18mQglo1wHdf4FbHq_qHGfWAJ1OprsO5n0zmUnO0qSYRilq3Lq5rPi8FJ8IqnfrCDIwUl9KYPYGVaQHn-iNbuRliXs7jsR6xwzMxcett8j-OfkpF1AqFKEkxyjgBWdsKU5L3c\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"436\">",
