        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click on the draft that you would like to edit, or click Add certificate.    NOTE: For shares that have been approved by the board but not purchased yet, choose Board approved under status. These shares will reduce the number of shares under the Equity Plan but will not be added to Shares Outstanding until they are purchased from the ledger once paid for by the holder, as described here.  carta/public/13/images/6052746258657145056_eDIzjKVzBSIx93mjz5nyIKFDcqRMu3k2TB82PkVFXl4lIb41OaE9AKZ5Rzd_tjyfqVHmxQdposQupI-5bjk12HeFIkmeDTAhNx7qWByDf8PQ5ZW26dyPR50-Al7HVSIVwSJ190eY",
        "originalText": "Click on the draft that you would like to edit, or click Add certificate.<br> <br> NOTE: For shares that have been approved by the board but not purchased yet, choose Board approved under status. These shares will reduce the number of shares under the Equity Plan but will not be added to Shares Outstanding until they are purchased from the ledger once paid for by the holder, as described <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/purchase-board-approved-rsas\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.<br> <img height=\"175\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/6052746258657145056_eDIzjKVzBSIx93mjz5nyIKFDcqRMu3k2TB82PkVFXl4lIb41OaE9AKZ5Rzd_tjyfqVHmxQdposQupI-5bjk12HeFIkmeDTAhNx7qWByDf8PQ5ZW26dyPR50-Al7HVSIVwSJ190eY\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"433\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/6052746258657145056_eDIzjKVzBSIx93mjz5nyIKFDcqRMu3k2TB82PkVFXl4lIb41OaE9AKZ5Rzd_tjyfqVHmxQdposQupI-5bjk12HeFIkmeDTAhNx7qWByDf8PQ5ZW26dyPR50-Al7HVSIVwSJ190eY"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "For Board Approved RSAs, click Add to ledger.  carta/public/13/images/4217957884295951257_CGRMWvPR59VVfA-ppdh137l2fpIj96LPHlTfLwTsCfbNt8GplbTNxIMZyMJgtzQCSErI5Gb4U6BfEQ4XIJLB-PB4HFjryvW7edPGZnZVleDpXyGiLdrhftac0DNb7nCenndCn-Gm",
        "originalText": "For Board Approved RSAs, click Add to ledger.<br> <img height=\"103\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/4217957884295951257_CGRMWvPR59VVfA-ppdh137l2fpIj96LPHlTfLwTsCfbNt8GplbTNxIMZyMJgtzQCSErI5Gb4U6BfEQ4XIJLB-PB4HFjryvW7edPGZnZVleDpXyGiLdrhftac0DNb7nCenndCn-Gm\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"426\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/4217957884295951257_CGRMWvPR59VVfA-ppdh137l2fpIj96LPHlTfLwTsCfbNt8GplbTNxIMZyMJgtzQCSErI5Gb4U6BfEQ4XIJLB-PB4HFjryvW7edPGZnZVleDpXyGiLdrhftac0DNb7nCenndCn-Gm"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Review the details and click Add to ledger.    NOTE: If the RSAs are not purchased yet, they are not sent for officers' signature. Purchase the RSAs to send the certificates for officer signature.  carta/public/13/images/8985227251748913921_DaDTQxgMNePGSd34CyYjklyW2EDvs0Htni-YEgqQxqZYYBZuSgoFIbdp7SlHoSKzd-Jur2ZMsC1wMTdC0y5vSiznzYzxSOHfZlwWY846RMTP_KdUdqVIjb1Esto9Da5QPiKv7ikK",
        "originalText": "Review the details and click Add to ledger.<br> <br> NOTE: If the RSAs are not purchased yet, they are not sent for officers' signature. Purchase the RSAs to send the certificates for officer signature.<br> <img height=\"235\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/8985227251748913921_DaDTQxgMNePGSd34CyYjklyW2EDvs0Htni-YEgqQxqZYYBZuSgoFIbdp7SlHoSKzd-Jur2ZMsC1wMTdC0y5vSiznzYzxSOHfZlwWY846RMTP_KdUdqVIjb1Esto9Da5QPiKv7ikK\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"433\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/8985227251748913921_DaDTQxgMNePGSd34CyYjklyW2EDvs0Htni-YEgqQxqZYYBZuSgoFIbdp7SlHoSKzd-Jur2ZMsC1wMTdC0y5vSiznzYzxSOHfZlwWY846RMTP_KdUdqVIjb1Esto9Da5QPiKv7ikK"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "To see how Board Approved RSAs are shown in the cap table, navigate to Capitalization > By share class.  Once purchased, previously Not-purchased RSAs will be counted as Shares Outstanding.  carta/public/13/images/4816210067467986184_J-s7W6pgg1OP6wgtAYsOEZccNFvE4aMjjeSgjzjj3Ks752_kXWC8iV3KvdP2kjSd-t2jX2WAEpxLvO_Gj1NuiO3SohdjDKd3n5XEoLGS55WmfUQ4bG3iDGoKy5MHRT5K4d7f78Jt",
