  "linked": [{
    "id": "266021809775021701",
    "text": {
      "text": "Terminating stakeholders is a common action in Carta that is typically one step. For holders of RSAs, there is an additional step that needs to happen to properly reflect the termination on the capitalization table. While the process of terminating a stakeholder stops all vesting on outstanding securities, this does not return unvested shares to the pool. This article will walk you through terminating stakeholders as well as the process of getting the unvested shares returned to the pool by repurchasing them.",
      "originalText": "Terminating stakeholders is a common action in Carta that is typically one step. For holders of RSAs, there is an additional step that needs to happen to properly reflect the termination on the capitalization table. While the process of terminating a stakeholder stops all vesting on outstanding securities, this does not return unvested shares to the pool. This article will walk you through terminating stakeholders as well as the process of getting the unvested shares returned to the pool by repurchasing them."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "5612820420818744062",
    "text": {
      "text": "To terminate a stakeholder, navigate toStakeholders > All Stakeholders. On the row of the stakeholder to be terminated, click theV drop-down menu and clickTerminate stakeholder. Review the termination procedure here. carta/public/13/images/2389959206532104761_Xmgjf41VPBmWTNYfPCnyp6SSjWPm5Fh2k3AtwbupfIQjGjogKAT18QcnoFbsUriayfDwGwDn9ig_Cnq-YyIOHnKlhS-PS4_zoZbvoZ-knWfPFrgQ4c4GtVyVXOGtF_ekXuCL1Qea",
      "originalText": "To terminate a stakeholder, navigate to Stakeholders &gt; All Stakeholders. On the row of the stakeholder to be terminated, click the V drop-down menu and click Terminate stakeholder. <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/terminate-stakeholders-update\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Review the termination procedure here</a>.<br><img height=\"173\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/2389959206532104761_Xmgjf41VPBmWTNYfPCnyp6SSjWPm5Fh2k3AtwbupfIQjGjogKAT18QcnoFbsUriayfDwGwDn9ig_Cnq-YyIOHnKlhS-PS4_zoZbvoZ-knWfPFrgQ4c4GtVyVXOGtF_ekXuCL1Qea\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"216\">",
