        }
      }, {
        "text": "In the Vesting schedules tab, click Create vesting schedules.  There are a few standard vesting schedule templates readily available to be used, such the common 1/48 monthly, 1 year cliff schedule.  carta/public/13/images/8950373362986835598_A5M8wXDMT_Fscm3PaiVTsPj2RmUvD8R9yMRohDkvc8OFVLdLAngKgeLRl7kPk0tYjldZdsobtIZF8e4Cd_U11VgWj9Jf54q-58MiMCTQh4jpOyqtJAaLLrcQnVMHtJ3v60ZdoVYq",
        "originalText": "In the Vesting schedules tab, click Create vesting schedules.<br> There are a few standard vesting schedule templates readily available to be used, such the common 1/48 monthly, 1 year cliff schedule.<br> <img height=\"116\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/8950373362986835598_A5M8wXDMT_Fscm3PaiVTsPj2RmUvD8R9yMRohDkvc8OFVLdLAngKgeLRl7kPk0tYjldZdsobtIZF8e4Cd_U11VgWj9Jf54q-58MiMCTQh4jpOyqtJAaLLrcQnVMHtJ3v60ZdoVYq\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"431\">",
        "associatedImage": {
