        "text": "Once set, click Create vesting schedule to save.  NOTE: Updating the vesting details will not apply to securities where the template is already applied. The vesting schedule will need to be reapplied to the security to reflect the updated template.",
        "originalText": "Once set, click Create vesting schedule to save.<br> NOTE: Updating the vesting details will not apply to securities where the template is already applied. The vesting schedule will need to be reapplied to the security to reflect the updated template."
      }, {
