      "text": "3921 Form - Copy B Delivery and Download"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "5045395499878951561",
    "text": {
      "text": "Section 6039 of the Internal Revenue Code requires companies to provide Form 3921 Copy B to the employee by January 31 of the year following the year of exercise of an incentive stock option (ISO). Companies can deliver this file electronically to the employee through Carta platform.",
      "originalText": "Section 6039 of the Internal Revenue Code requires companies to provide&nbsp;Form 3921 Copy B to the employee by January 31 of the year following the year of exercise of an incentive stock option (ISO). Companies can deliver this file electronically to the employee through Carta platform.<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "1078521231474003317",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "Navigate to Compliance > Form 3921 and generate your 3921 report ( see how to generate the report here.)  carta/public/13/images/638043282759050144_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Navigate to Compliance &gt; Form 3921 and generate your 3921 report (<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/generating-form-3921-in-carta\" target=\"_blank\">see how to generate the report here.</a>)<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/638043282759050144_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/638043282759050144_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Once the report is generated, click Deliver Copy B.  carta/public/13/images/627865294022707705_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Once the report is generated, click Deliver Copy B.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/627865294022707705_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/627865294022707705_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "This will send an email notifying holders that Copy B has been delivered.  carta/public/13/images/8670257728486353776_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "This will send an email notifying holders that Copy B has been delivered.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/8670257728486353776_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/8670257728486353776_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "ISO holders can download their Copy B here.",
        "originalText": "ISO holders can <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/3921-form-download\" target=\"_blank\"><u>download their Copy B here</u></a>."
      }]
    }
  }]
}

