    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "After the company has received the signed exercise agreement and the payment from the employee, navigate to the appropriate option grant and select Exercise options in the drop-down menu.  carta/public/13/images/6660860576906318702_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "After the company has&nbsp;received the signed exercise agreement and the payment from the employee, navigate to the appropriate option grant and select Exercise options in the drop-down menu.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/6660860576906318702_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/6660860576906318702_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Fill out all pertinent details about the exercise date and the number of options to be exercised. Click Next: Review.  carta/public/13/images/1748581083456277976_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Fill out all pertinent details about the exercise date and the number of options to be exercised. Click Next: Review.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/1748581083456277976_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/1748581083456277976_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Review the exercise details and any tax withholdings. Click Save Off System Transaction.  carta/public/13/images/966812822218994105_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Review the exercise details and any tax withholdings. Click Save Off System Transaction.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/966812822218994105_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/966812822218994105_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "The newly issued certificate now shows up under the common certificate section of the cap table. The number of shares available under the equity plan is reduced by the number of options that were exercised.  carta/public/13/images/5193723459506372421_rtaImage    carta/public/13/images/8262972710639554627_rtaImage",
