      }, {
        "text": "Your seller table is now created. You can export the table to excel and update security minimums and maximums as well as per stakeholder. Your project manager at Carta can help as needed and will upload the new table for you.  NOTE: The format and columns of this table cannot be changed as it will not import properly.  carta/public/13/images/4258944543859540873_BBsX4R6dUlGhSCNTw09VqtiN3PzWn7yd350FmD3xROK6czLB4vCAUK6esM3K-k4ur2M1qzyIlzyG-YO2nakV77_XNhsl3RK_XW1dBA54RKqajUOZhopew8YJpkXdjoNn-1Zo-GbG",
        "originalText": "Your seller table is now created. You can export the table to excel and update security minimums and maximums as well as per stakeholder. Your project manager at Carta can help as needed and will upload the new table for you.<br> NOTE: The format and columns of this table cannot be changed as it will not import properly.<br> <img height=\"215\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/4258944543859540873_BBsX4R6dUlGhSCNTw09VqtiN3PzWn7yd350FmD3xROK6czLB4vCAUK6esM3K-k4ur2M1qzyIlzyG-YO2nakV77_XNhsl3RK_XW1dBA54RKqajUOZhopew8YJpkXdjoNn-1Zo-GbG\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"431\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/4258944543859540873_BBsX4R6dUlGhSCNTw09VqtiN3PzWn7yd350FmD3xROK6czLB4vCAUK6esM3K-k4ur2M1qzyIlzyG-YO2nakV77_XNhsl3RK_XW1dBA54RKqajUOZhopew8YJpkXdjoNn-1Zo-GbG"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Once the documents have been watermarked and the seller table confirmed, you are now ready to invite your participants on launch day. To invite participants, first filter for Not Invited status.  NOTE: Participants will need to accept their security on Carta before you can invite them to the Tender Offer. Once they accept, they will be moved from Not Accepted to Not Invited status. You will then be able to invite them throughout the open offer.  carta/public/13/images/7908411681313371336_bccAVSZsaU0if7VuueA1uMki3h5xAvD8VYewwDcL7fgCBstr2ZCPv6CVki_Bb3TIw3RCjNKJVTdZcnRwJIZcdEsj58zf_KGalgFpNwBhRA__LlhkJh9U_FMUi8t1-r4MumFrjY19",
        "originalText": "Once the documents have been watermarked and the seller table confirmed, you are now ready to invite your participants on launch day. To invite participants, first filter for Not Invited status.<br> NOTE: Participants will need to accept their security on Carta before you can invite them to the Tender Offer. Once they accept, they will be moved from Not Accepted to Not Invited status. You will then be able to invite them throughout the open offer.<br> <img height=\"283\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/7908411681313371336_bccAVSZsaU0if7VuueA1uMki3h5xAvD8VYewwDcL7fgCBstr2ZCPv6CVki_Bb3TIw3RCjNKJVTdZcnRwJIZcdEsj58zf_KGalgFpNwBhRA__LlhkJh9U_FMUi8t1-r4MumFrjY19\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"436\">",
