      "item": [{
        "text": "If you need to bulk update the name or email address connected to the stakeholder, click Manageand select Update properties.  carta/public/13/images/4173216833218962617_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "If you need to bulk update the name or email address connected to the stakeholder, click Manage and select Update properties.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/4173216833218962617_rtaImage\">",
