        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/2861546076037347024_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "The exported template will have a tab for each property. The grey columns are to be left unedited, while the updated properties will be added to Column F and G.  carta/public/13/images/1830473377791757805_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "The exported template will have a tab for each property. The grey columns are to be left unedited, while the updated properties will be added to Column F and G.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/1830473377791757805_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/1830473377791757805_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Once the sheet is complete, upload the sheet to Step 2 of the previous modal, and click Import spreadsheet.  carta/public/13/images/4231573251868414461_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Once the sheet is complete, upload the sheet to Step 2 of the previous modal, and click&nbsp;Import spreadsheet.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/4231573251868414461_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/4231573251868414461_rtaImage"
        }
      }]
    }
  }]
}

{
  "id": "-1306181019620754107",
  "subject": {
    "id": "-1306181019620754107",
    "text": {
      "text": "Uploading Investor Documents"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "2724616629247218248",
    "text": {
      "text": "Note: This feature will send the document to all of the investment firm's Partners. If you would like to send a document to an individual partner, refer to these instructions.",
      "originalText": "Note: This feature will send the document to all of the investment firm's Partners. If you would like to send a document to an individual partner, refer to <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/uploading-multiple-files\" target=\"_blank\">these instructions</a>."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-8921692903735305087",
    "text": {
      "text": "Investment firms that have added their LPs to the investment firm can send documents to their partners.",
      "originalText": "Investment firms that have added their LPs to the investment firm can send documents to their partners."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-6257030285728176579",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "To upload and share investor documents, navigate into the individual fund level, then to Investors > Partner Documents.  carta/public/13/images/8988011779851018402_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "To upload and share investor documents, navigate into the individual fund level, then to Investors &gt; Partner Documents.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/8988011779851018402_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/8988011779851018402_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "To upload additional documents, select Upload documents. You will have the option to upload a single file, multiple files, or divide a PDF.  carta/public/13/images/3798257649000370058_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "To upload additional documents, select Upload documents. You will have the option to upload a single file, multiple files, or divide a PDF.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/3798257649000370058_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/3798257649000370058_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "A. To upload a single file, select a recipient and fill out the document type, name, date and choose a file. The Recipients dropdown will allow you to upload files to multiple investors, all investors, or a single investor. Once the fields have been completed, click Upload.  carta/public/13/images/3004785584041397764_rtaImage    B. To upload multiple files, you will be prompted to download an excel spreadsheet. The spreadsheet will be pre-populated with the names of the investors and their associated fund.  carta/public/13/images/2974201454421888484_rtaImage    The spreadsheet will allow you to select the document type that you wish to upload. The file name should match the name of the document in the file folder.  carta/public/13/images/8491296465172335487_rtaImage    You can also upload multiple files for each investor within the spreadsheet.  carta/public/13/images/6156443757697377873_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "A. To upload a single file, select a recipient and fill out the document type, name, date and choose a file. The Recipients dropdown will allow you to upload files to multiple investors, all investors, or a single investor. Once the fields have been completed,&nbsp;click Upload.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/3004785584041397764_rtaImage\"><br> <br> B. To upload multiple files, you will be prompted to download an excel spreadsheet. The spreadsheet will be pre-populated with the names of the investors and their associated fund.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/2974201454421888484_rtaImage\"><br> <br> The spreadsheet will allow you to select the document type that you wish to upload. The file&nbsp;name should match the name of the document in the file folder.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/8491296465172335487_rtaImage\"><br> <br> You can also upload multiple files for each investor within the spreadsheet.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/6156443757697377873_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/6156443757697377873_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Once the spreadsheet has been completed, it should be uploaded along with a zip file of the physical copies of the investor documents.  carta/public/13/images/5778586406700940122_rtaImageOnce the documents are uploaded, you will be able to view them in the Partner documents view within the individual fund.",
