      }, {
        "text": "After documents have been uploaded, they can be shared and/or deleted. To send documents, check the box associated with the investor to which you want to send the document.  carta/public/13/images/6265790849132897549_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "After documents have been uploaded, they can be shared and/or deleted. To send documents, check the box associated with the investor to which you want to send the document.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/6265790849132897549_rtaImage\">",
