{
  "id": "-5475739640416974296",
  "subject": {
    "id": "-5475739640416974296",
    "text": {
      "text": "Migrating from CapMX to Carta"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "7168399599481850009",
    "text": {
      "text": "Carta can import the full history of a company easily if the company was previously on CapMX.",
      "originalText": "Carta can import the full&nbsp;history of a company easily if the company was previously on CapMX.<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "1531697603779683977",
    "text": {
      "text": "We need several reports exported from CapMX along with a handful of screenshots to begin.",
      "originalText": "We need several reports exported from CapMX along with a handful of screenshots to begin.<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-260046456690292209",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "Authorized Capital (screenshot)  Under Capitalization › Authorized Capital carta/public/13/images/8881808804304443356_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Authorized Capital&nbsp;(screenshot)<br> Under Capitalization&nbsp;› Authorized Capital<img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/8881808804304443356_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/8881808804304443356_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Option Plans (screen shot)  Under Stock/Option Plan › Modify Option Plan carta/public/13/images/7777882011194414980_rtaImage This must include the full history ofShare Allocations for the plans. Include a separate screen shot for each option plan if there is more than one.",
        "originalText": "Option Plans&nbsp;(screen shot)<br> Under Stock/Option Plan&nbsp;› Modify Option Plan <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/7777882011194414980_rtaImage\"> This must include the full history of&nbsp; Share Allocations&nbsp;for the plans. Include a separate screen shot for each option plan if there is more than one. ",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/7777882011194414980_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Option plan terminations (screen shot)  Under Stock/Option Plan › Modify Option Plan › first dated amendment carta/public/13/images/6432378043319412472_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Option plan terminations&nbsp;(screen shot)<br> Under Stock/Option Plan&nbsp;› Modify Option Plan&nbsp;›&nbsp;first dated&nbsp;amendment <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/6432378043319412472_rtaImage\"> ",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/6432378043319412472_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Detailed Capitalization Report  Under Reports › Current Reports › Capitalization › Detailed Capitalization Report carta/public/13/images/5469523816840441021_rtaImage   This must includeOutstanding andAs-Converted Shares (combined) carta/public/13/images/7341764613801074211_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Detailed Capitalization Report<br> Under Reports&nbsp;› Current Reports&nbsp;› Capitalization&nbsp;› Detailed Capitalization Report <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/5469523816840441021_rtaImage\"> <br> This must include&nbsp; Outstanding&nbsp;and&nbsp;As-Converted Shares (combined)<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/7341764613801074211_rtaImage\"> ",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/7341764613801074211_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Option Holder Report (ledger)  Under Reports › Current Reports › Option & Stock Purchase Rights › Option Holder Report (ledger)    It's critical that this is the ledger report, as the other versions lack critical information. When generated, it should have columns A through AE at least. carta/public/13/images/7521991809913757637_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Option Holder Report (ledger)<br> Under Reports&nbsp;› Current Reports&nbsp;› Option &amp; Stock Purchase Rights&nbsp;›&nbsp;Option Holder Report (ledger)<br> <br> It's critical that this is the&nbsp; ledger&nbsp;report, as the other versions lack critical information. When generated, it should have columns A through AE at least. <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/7521991809913757637_rtaImage\"> ",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/7521991809913757637_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Options & SPRs Granted Report (***If you have SPRs in your CapMx account, please see the note below)  Under Reports › Current Reports › Option & Stock Purchase Rights › Options & SPRs Granted (Legal) Report carta/public/13/images/1631019851724835610_rtaImage   When prompted for dates, use01/01/1990 as theFrom Date and today's date as theTo Date. carta/public/13/images/8267411973710683260_rtaImage ***IMPORTANT -- CapMx and Carta represent SPRs and RSAs in different ways. Here's what you can do to make sure the security is properly entered: 1) Determine if it is actually an SPR or an RSA 2) If it is an RSA (Restricted Stock Award), enter them as RSAs issued from an equity plan with the issue date on the SPR as the RSA issue date 3) If it is a true SPR (Stock Purchase Right), please contact the Carta Onboarding Team for support!",
        "originalText": "Options &amp; SPRs Granted Report (***If you have SPRs in your CapMx account, please see the note below)<br> Under Reports&nbsp;› Current Reports&nbsp;› Option &amp; Stock Purchase Rights&nbsp;› Options &amp; SPRs Granted (Legal) Report <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/1631019851724835610_rtaImage\"> <br> When prompted&nbsp;for dates, use&nbsp; 01/01/1990&nbsp;as the&nbsp;From Date&nbsp;and today's date as the&nbsp;To Date.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/8267411973710683260_rtaImage\"> &nbsp; ***IMPORTANT -- CapMx and Carta represent SPRs and RSAs in different ways. Here's what you can do to make sure&nbsp;the security is properly entered: 1)&nbsp;Determine if it is actually an SPR or an RSA 2)&nbsp;If it is an RSA (Restricted Stock Award), enter them as RSAs issued from an equity plan with the issue date on the SPR as the RSA issue date 3)&nbsp;If it is a true SPR (Stock Purchase Right), please contact the Carta Onboarding Team for support! ",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/8267411973710683260_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Stock Ledger  Under Reports › Current Reports › Shareholder › Stock Ledger (legal)    We cannot use other stock reports, such as class-level reports, as they do not contain enough information.  carta/public/13/images/3890264379712185391_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Stock Ledger<br> Under Reports&nbsp;› Current Reports&nbsp;›&nbsp;Shareholder&nbsp;› Stock Ledger (legal)<br> <br> We cannot use other stock reports, such as class-level reports, as they do not contain enough information.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/3890264379712185391_rtaImage\"> &nbsp; ",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/3890264379712185391_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Termination Report  Under Reports › Current Reports › Termination › Termination Report carta/public/13/images/663368153662440086_rtaImage   When prompted for dates, please use01/01/1990 as theFrom Date and today's date as theTo Date.",
        "originalText": "Termination Report<br> Under Reports&nbsp;› Current Reports ›&nbsp;Termination&nbsp;› Termination Report <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/663368153662440086_rtaImage\"> <br> When prompted&nbsp;for dates, please use&nbsp; 01/01/1990&nbsp;as the&nbsp;From Date&nbsp;and today's date as the&nbsp;To Date. ",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/663368153662440086_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Warrant Ledger  Under Reports › Current Reports › Warrant › Warrant Ledger Report (Ledger)    If no warrants have been issued, no report will be generated. This is OK.",
        "originalText": "Warrant Ledger<br> Under Reports&nbsp;› Current Reports ›&nbsp;Warrant&nbsp;› Warrant Ledger Report (Ledger)<br> <br> If no warrants have been issued, no report will be generated. This is OK."
      }, {
        "text": "Convertible Note Ledger  Under Reports › Current Reports › Convertible Promissory Note › CPN Ledger Report (Legal)    If no convertible notes have been issued, no report will be generated. This is OK.",
        "originalText": "Convertible Note Ledger<br> Under Reports&nbsp;› Current Reports ›&nbsp;Convertible&nbsp;Promissory Note&nbsp;›&nbsp;CPN Ledger Report (Legal)<br> <br> If no convertible notes have been issued, no report will be generated.&nbsp;This is OK.<br> &nbsp;"
      }, {
        "text": "Shareholder Report  Under Reports › Current Reports › Shareholder › Shareholder Report",
        "originalText": "Shareholder Report<br> Under Reports&nbsp;› Current Reports&nbsp;› Shareholder&nbsp;› Shareholder Report"
      }]
    }
  }]
}

{
  "id": "1880800946946271044",
  "subject": {
    "id": "1880800946946271044",
    "text": {
      "text": "How to create a board meeting"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-3511643646321289779",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "As a Board admin, navigate to Board > Meetings from the top header.  carta/public/13/images/3140624839073787248_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "As a <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/set-board-admin\" target=\"_blank\">Board admin</a>, navigate to Board &gt; Meetings&nbsp;from the top header.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/3140624839073787248_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/3140624839073787248_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click Create board meeting.  carta/public/13/images/1742927977009942746_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Click Create board meeting.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/1742927977009942746_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/1742927977009942746_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Complete meeting details and click Save.  carta/public/13/images/1308663526498652902_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Complete meeting details and click Save.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/1308663526498652902_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/1308663526498652902_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "The meeting will stay in draft mode, where you can continue to edit the meeting details and add agenda items, until the meeting is published.  carta/public/13/images/4633837393282785693_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "The meeting will stay in draft mode, where you can continue to edit the meeting details and add agenda items, until the meeting is published.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/4633837393282785693_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/4633837393282785693_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "The meeting attendees will only be notified of the meeting and given access to documents once the meeting is published. When the meeting is complete, click manage meeting > archive meeting& to make the contents read-only.  carta/public/13/images/1208673559205932675_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "The meeting attendees will only be notified of the meeting and given access to documents once the meeting is published. When the meeting is complete, click manage meeting &gt; archive meeting&amp; to make the contents read-only.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/1208673559205932675_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/1208673559205932675_rtaImage"
        }
      }]
    }
  }]
}

