        }
      }, {
        "text": "Check the box to the left of the CBU’s row to select the row. You can select multiple CBUs if the modifications are the same for multiple CBUs.  carta/public/13/images/8904882471729295438_uw6OIK7Nc1Fd61VzF7TuBVwDgXZFrDlYhv57W1du-XYfKttSriIkLwoIt7Nhx0MJcUMGLOtaleT3jHF496t8g8Igi1YeHcjEkR7eGgPJWKMl4Y5XqEByaT6LoaUGvUJ8bUjGLItw",
