        }
      }, {
        "text": "Choose the modification type: clerical error or amendment. Add a note for the modification - if the modification sends out a notification to the holder who has accepted the security, this note will be included. Click Next: Modify values.  carta/public/13/images/3782567860993077383_PeTRrL1yABU_Q9TTme1fLC1OyURZiBve6o16iIWQ0fauNpHuLAS646NBB8Fdf1DDMKxUmYpW8Zy3MCzzgmDLTk4XbnIfs70Spjpsbie9VoM-7BiBYQ6WtqfQM349WQq1yA0rZcvZ",
