    "id": "-8023167504537100155",
    "text": {
      "text": "Exercise Option Grant Manually (option holder)"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-5033931695195838829",
    "text": {
      "text": "Exercising manually does not require you to set up your bank account with Carta. If you would like to exercise electronically, click to learn about ACH exercise.",
      "originalText": "Exercising manually does not require you to set up your bank account with Carta. If you would like to exercise electronically, <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/exercising-options-on-carta\" target=\"_blank\">click to learn about ACH exercise</a>.<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "7293066690036243576",
    "text": {
      "text": "Manual exercising requires communication between the option holder and the company. Confirm the process with your company admins to ensure proper forms are filled and form of payment is accepted. You can contact the issuing company from your portfolio.",
      "originalText": "Manual exercising requires communication between the option holder and the company. Confirm the process with your company admins to ensure proper forms are filled and form of payment is accepted. You can <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/contacting-the-issuer\" target=\"_blank\">contact the issuing company</a> from your portfolio."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "8856026973899454113",
    "text": {
      "text": "1. From thePortfolio page, click into theHoldings tab and click on the image or grant ID to open the option grant details. carta/public/13/images/5285339247384761372_rtaImage",
      "originalText": "1. From the Portfolio&nbsp;page, click into the&nbsp;Holdings&nbsp;tab and click on the image or grant ID to open the option grant details.<br><img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/5285339247384761372_rtaImage\">",
      "associatedImage": {
        "url": "carta/public/13/images/5285339247384761372_rtaImage"
      }
    }
  }, {
    "id": "913134786144242303",
    "text": {
      "text": "2. Click onDocuments and notes and click on the file name to download theForm of Exercise Agreement.",
      "originalText": "2. Click on Documents and notes&nbsp;and click on the file name to download the Form of Exercise Agreement."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "3657816502835352590",
    "image": {
      "url": "carta/public/13/images/4177219418445765759_rtaImage"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "3535640231058829323",
    "text": {
      "text": "Here is an example of a Notice of Exercise to complete and send to the issuing company. Forms will differ per company. carta/public/13/images/432478443290580038_rtaImage",
      "originalText": "Here is an example of a Notice of Exercise to complete and send to the issuing company. Forms will differ per company.<br><img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/432478443290580038_rtaImage\">",
      "associatedImage": {
        "url": "carta/public/13/images/432478443290580038_rtaImage"
      }
    }
  }, {
    "id": "5866125007219798215",
    "text": {
      "text": "3. Fill out theForm of Exercise and send the completed form, the payment, and any other information required by the company. Once processed, the company admin will reflect the exercise on the cap table. This will produce a resulting certificate of the exercised shares that will be sent to the officer signatories to sign, then to the holder to accept.",
      "originalText": "3. Fill out the Form of Exercise&nbsp;and send the completed form, the payment, and any other information required by the company. Once processed, the company admin will reflect the exercise on the cap table. This will produce a resulting certificate of the exercised shares that will be sent to the officer signatories to sign, then to the holder to accept."
    }
