{
  "id": "-9182839921837881378",
  "subject": {
    "id": "-9182839921837881378",
    "text": {
      "text": "Generating Form 3921 in Carta"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "6393573303730098190",
    "text": {
      "text": "Section 6039 of the Internal Revenue Code (IRC) requires companies to provide Form 3921 Copy B to the employee by January 31 of the year following the year of exercise of an incentive stock option (ISO). The company must also file Form 3921 with the IRS no later than February 28 if filed on paper, or March 31, if filed electronically. You can review the 3921 workflow and FAQs here.",
      "originalText": "Section 6039 of the Internal Revenue Code (IRC) requires companies to provide&nbsp;Form 3921 Copy B to the employee by January 31 of the year following the year of exercise of an incentive stock option (ISO). The company must also file Form 3921 with the IRS no later than February 28 if filed on paper, or March 31, if filed electronically. <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/form-3921-walkthrough\" target=\"_blank\">You can review the 3921 workflow and FAQs here</a>.<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-7043924292997566215",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "To generate Form 3921, navigate to Compliance > Form 3921. Then click Generate 3921s.  Note: TCC is not required to generate Form 3921 Copy B for employees and Copy C for the company.  carta/public/13/images/7292156518515806092_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "To generate Form 3921, navigate to&nbsp;Compliance &gt; Form 3921. Then click Generate 3921s.<br> Note: TCC is not required to generate Form 3921 Copy B for employees and Copy C for the company.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/7292156518515806092_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/7292156518515806092_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Choose the effective year of the report, and click Next: check data.  carta/public/13/images/963814054144649383_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Choose the effective year of the report, and click Next: check data.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/963814054144649383_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/963814054144649383_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click on the links under the missing data set.  carta/public/13/images/6166503538184063624_rtaImage    If you have any missing company tax data, navigate to Company > Accounts, then to the Profile tab. Enter Tax ID, TCC (optional) and address.  Note: Without a TCC, only forms B and C will be generated. If TCC is obtained after generating 3921, you can enter the code in the company's profile page, then repeat the workflow to generate Copy A for electronic filing to the IRS fire site.  carta/public/13/images/6829569081270153862_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Click on the links under the missing data set.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/6166503538184063624_rtaImage\"><br> <br> If you have any missing company tax data, navigate to Company &gt; Accounts , then to the Profile tab. Enter Tax ID, TCC (optional) and address.<br> Note: Without a TCC, only forms B and C will be generated. If TCC is obtained after generating 3921, you can enter the code in the company's profile page, then repeat the workflow&nbsp;to generate&nbsp;Copy A for electronic filing to the IRS fire site.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/6829569081270153862_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/6829569081270153862_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Return to the Form 3921 page to update any missing stakeholder tax data.  carta/public/13/images/4587954549191899514_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Return to the Form 3921 page to update any missing stakeholder tax data.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/4587954549191899514_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/4587954549191899514_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Update missing data under Stakeholder Details.  carta/public/13/images/2476671123116818420_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Update missing data under Stakeholder Details.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/2476671123116818420_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/2476671123116818420_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Review and update the historical 409A valuation for every tax year in which you will be running Form 3921.  6a. Click Review FMVs.  carta/public/13/images/2981438710546824543_rtaImage    6b. If any historical 409A values are missing, click Add fair market value to enter all historical values.  carta/public/13/images/403431356250760041_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Review and update the historical 409A valuation for every tax year in which you will be running Form 3921.<br> 6a. Click Review FMVs.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/2981438710546824543_rtaImage\"><br> <br> 6b. If any historical 409A values are missing, click Add fair market value to enter all historical values.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/403431356250760041_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/403431356250760041_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Return to Form 3921 page. Once the three data sets are complete and you have checked the box under Confirm company data, click Next: add contact info.  carta/public/13/images/7695471454427407071_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Return to Form 3921 page. Once the three data sets are complete and you have checked the box under Confirm company data, click Next: add contact info.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/7695471454427407071_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/7695471454427407071_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Company contact is formatted into the electronic Copy A .txt file that will be uploaded to the IRS site:  carta/public/13/images/5976090329015201689_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Company contact is formatted into the electronic Copy A .txt file that will be uploaded to the <a href=\"https://www.irs.gov/tax-professionals/e-file-providers-partners/filing-information-returns-electronically-fire\" target=\"_blank\">IRS site</a>:<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/5976090329015201689_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/5976090329015201689_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "The form will take a few minutes to generate depending on the number of ISO exercises in that tax year. Refresh the page after some time or navigate away and return later.  carta/public/13/images/5917276793056133346_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "The form will take a few minutes to generate depending on the number of ISO exercises in that tax year. Refresh the page after some time&nbsp;or navigate away and return later.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/5917276793056133346_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/5917276793056133346_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Once generated, Carta will download a file to your computer that contains all necessary data to electronically file Copy A and distribute Copy B and Copy C:  carta/public/13/images/8805074730953946859_rtaImage    The proper documents will be broken out into three appropriate files:  carta/public/13/images/9203680865854031355_rtaImageCopy A will be a specially formatted electronic .txt file.Note: Do not edit this file. Only download and upload to the IRS fire site. Instructions can be found here. If any data needs to be updated, it should be done in Carta. To regenerate, follow the instructions here. carta/public/13/images/3653694012430332792_rtaImageCopy B should be delivered to all exercising employees by the January 31st deadline and can be delivered electronically on Carta. Click onDeliver Copy B. To see how employees can access their copy B, click here. carta/public/13/images/3494494082575119776_rtaImageCopy C is kept for company records. carta/public/13/images/774610952310803014_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Once generated, Carta will download a file to your computer that contains all necessary data to electronically file Copy A and distribute Copy B and Copy C:<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/8805074730953946859_rtaImage\"><br> <br> The proper documents will be broken out into three appropriate files:<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/9203680865854031355_rtaImage\">  Copy A will be a specially formatted electronic .txt file.<br> Note: Do not edit this file. Only download and upload to the IRS fire site. Instructions can be found <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/uploading-3921\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>. If any data needs to be updated, it should be done in Carta. To regenerate, follow the instructions <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/how-to-regenerate-form-3921\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/3653694012430332792_rtaImage\"> Copy B should be delivered to all exercising employees by the January 31st deadline and can be delivered electronically on Carta. Click on Deliver Copy B. To see how employees can access their copy B, click <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/3921-form-download\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/3494494082575119776_rtaImage\"> Copy C is kept for company records.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/774610952310803014_rtaImage\">  ",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/774610952310803014_rtaImage"
        }
      }]
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-5758552650416238277",
    "text": {
      "text": "You can review the rest of the 3921 workflow and common FAQs here.",
      "originalText": "<br><a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/form-3921-walkthrough\" target=\"_blank\">You can review the rest of the 3921 workflow and common FAQs here</a>."
    }
  }]
}

