      "originalText": "Once the securities have been issued, the share class or note block will appear in your Library. Click Edit&nbsp;enter the closing date, document name, and upload the documents. All investors on Carta who have participated in that round will receive an email notification from Carta that these documents have been uploaded and will be granted access to securely view and download.<br><img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/7941625902683380269_rtaImage\">",
