    "id": "-6300771611406770553",
    "text": {
      "text": "Two-factor authentication (Company Admin setting)"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "8772507840518491307",
    "text": {
      "text": "Two-factor authentication adds an additional layer of security and prevents users listed on the Company'sPermissions and Roles page from accessing or using your account, even if they have your password. Company administrators can require users from theCompany > Permissions and Roles page to set up two-factor authentication on their Carta account for extra security. This setting does not apply to stakeholders of the company.",
      "originalText": "Two-factor authentication adds an additional layer of security and prevents users listed on the Company's Permissions and Roles&nbsp;page from accessing or using&nbsp;your account, even if they have your password. Company administrators can require users from the&nbsp;Company&nbsp;&gt; Permissions and Roles&nbsp;page to set up two-factor authentication on their Carta account&nbsp;for extra security. This setting does not apply to stakeholders of the company.<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "5038029226863389391",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "Navigate to Company > Settings.  carta/public/13/images/2255945856817615720_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Navigate to Company &gt; Settings.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/2255945856817615720_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/2255945856817615720_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Then toggle on Require two-factor authentication.  carta/public/13/images/1708824774481890491_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Then toggle on Require two-factor authentication.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/1708824774481890491_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/1708824774481890491_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Once enabled, users from the company's Permissions and Roles page may see this screen and will be required to enable two-factor authentication before accessing the company account.  carta/public/13/images/5816411637673851754_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "Once enabled, users from the company's Permissions and Roles&nbsp;page may see this screen and will be required to enable two-factor authentication before accessing the company account.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/5816411637673851754_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/5816411637673851754_rtaImage"
        }
      }]
    }
  }, {
