    "id": "683408555289063779",
    "text": {
      "text": "Investor Calibration Tool"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-6829805167501628275",
    "text": {
      "text": "TheCalibrationtool on the Carta platform is a fast and efficient way to determine whether any of your investments should be reassessed given current market conditions and portfolio company performance. Whether your current holdings value was based on a market multiples analysis or the most recent round of financing, the CartaCalibrationtool can provide a high-level picture of how current market conditions may have impacted your portfolio.",
      "originalText": "The Calibration tool on the Carta platform is a fast and efficient way to determine whether any of your investments should be reassessed given current market conditions and portfolio company performance. Whether your current holdings value was based on a market multiples analysis or the most recent round of financing, the Carta Calibration tool can provide a high-level picture of how current market conditions may have impacted your portfolio."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "3098332037997693015",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "You can access the Calibrationtool in the Reports and Documentssection of your fund dashboard.  carta/public/13/images/7734729705410831653_DQScgRX_AHhndXvvjBx_Tkfo3htEDNT_OgYXWEzjmcK0RSFY3fCFBQxz5BYlL-ig36u3ehO7umnAEaQ9m7s_uh-6YTU988umA4WrCtJdSoA62rWLV6Ra-C1HT716GmxMWACFG4yg",
        "originalText": "You can access the Calibration tool in the Reports and Documents section of your fund dashboard.<br> <img height=\"381\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/7734729705410831653_DQScgRX_AHhndXvvjBx_Tkfo3htEDNT_OgYXWEzjmcK0RSFY3fCFBQxz5BYlL-ig36u3ehO7umnAEaQ9m7s_uh-6YTU988umA4WrCtJdSoA62rWLV6Ra-C1HT716GmxMWACFG4yg\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"471\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/7734729705410831653_DQScgRX_AHhndXvvjBx_Tkfo3htEDNT_OgYXWEzjmcK0RSFY3fCFBQxz5BYlL-ig36u3ehO7umnAEaQ9m7s_uh-6YTU988umA4WrCtJdSoA62rWLV6Ra-C1HT716GmxMWACFG4yg"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click Create report to launch the Calibrationtool.  carta/public/13/images/2659734923649161715_NHXbYgGSZSdLeU3Kdd666Dk5ibBZ66zTYY1JbyMbkFCuCpRMmcGCskHBqvIxtt8maMyc1JYTgFGnMqpcsVpVqGSt6lqgAe8dCsu8NO9Xl9Q9XrGNU1ZXxchfDyXK9v687xYUUc9h",
        "originalText": "Click Create report to launch the Calibration tool.<br> <img height=\"177\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/2659734923649161715_NHXbYgGSZSdLeU3Kdd666Dk5ibBZ66zTYY1JbyMbkFCuCpRMmcGCskHBqvIxtt8maMyc1JYTgFGnMqpcsVpVqGSt6lqgAe8dCsu8NO9Xl9Q9XrGNU1ZXxchfDyXK9v687xYUUc9h\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"425\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/2659734923649161715_NHXbYgGSZSdLeU3Kdd666Dk5ibBZ66zTYY1JbyMbkFCuCpRMmcGCskHBqvIxtt8maMyc1JYTgFGnMqpcsVpVqGSt6lqgAe8dCsu8NO9Xl9Q9XrGNU1ZXxchfDyXK9v687xYUUc9h"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Name the report, select the desired calibration date, and select the companies you would like to include in the report. You can add any portfolio companies, not currently included in your Company Investments page, manually you within the tool. To proceed, click Continue. carta/public/13/images/6679766977335889935_Rau4JZxWy4bkAXOY-IKg2Ep1fyn9woWjyXo6cc1G3UrvmSL2SkJsl_2H4vyIpivronaYsfA5Tt7RRHSwWk5jKwGoV3GgbHE89SuKIkTAD62NtvXCFh2w8fdzLa9ywQ3GXjcRKy9a",
        "originalText": "Name the report, select the desired calibration date, and select the companies you would like to include in the report. You can add any portfolio companies, not currently included in your Company Investments page, manually you within the tool. To proceed, click Continue.<br> <img height=\"328\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/6679766977335889935_Rau4JZxWy4bkAXOY-IKg2Ep1fyn9woWjyXo6cc1G3UrvmSL2SkJsl_2H4vyIpivronaYsfA5Tt7RRHSwWk5jKwGoV3GgbHE89SuKIkTAD62NtvXCFh2w8fdzLa9ywQ3GXjcRKy9a\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"427\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/6679766977335889935_Rau4JZxWy4bkAXOY-IKg2Ep1fyn9woWjyXo6cc1G3UrvmSL2SkJsl_2H4vyIpivronaYsfA5Tt7RRHSwWk5jKwGoV3GgbHE89SuKIkTAD62NtvXCFh2w8fdzLa9ywQ3GXjcRKy9a"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Any companies that have a finalized ASC 820 valuation on Carta will populate with the industry, valuation date, company value, and LTM Revenue from the most recent finalized valuation. For all other companies, you will need to enter this information. In the Comparables column, select the industry that most closely aligns with the portfolio company. The Benchmark Date can be the date of the last valuation performed on the company (for example, 12/31/2019) or the date of the last financing depending on how you arrived at your current holdings value. Benchmark Company Value, Holdings Value, and LTM Revenue should all be as of the selected Benchmark Date.    To incorporate any companies not currently included on the Company Investments page of your Carta account, simply press the green + symbol to add a row where you can incorporate the details for that company.",
        "originalText": "Any companies that have a finalized ASC 820 valuation on Carta will populate with the industry, valuation date, company value, and LTM Revenue from the most recent finalized valuation. For all other companies, you will need to enter this information. In the Comparables column, select the industry that most closely aligns with the portfolio company. The Benchmark Date can be the date of the last valuation performed on the company (for example, 12/31/2019) or the date of the last financing depending on how you arrived at your current holdings value. Benchmark Company Value, Holdings Value, and LTM Revenue should all be as of the selected Benchmark Date.<br> <br> To incorporate any companies not currently included on the Company Investments page of your Carta account, simply press the green + symbol to add a row where you can incorporate the details for that company."
      }, {
        "text": "After entering the Benchmark details for each investment, the final step is to complete the Calibration columns. Company performance selection should be based on overall performance since the Benchmark Date. This selection will determine if the multiple selected in the Calibration Report should be adjusted up or down the range relative to the multiple implied as of the Benchmark Date.",
        "originalText": "After entering the Benchmark details for each investment, the final step is to complete the Calibration columns. Company performance selection should be based on overall performance since the Benchmark Date. This selection will determine if the multiple selected in the Calibration Report should be adjusted up or down the range relative to the multiple implied as of the Benchmark Date."
      }, {
        "text": "Once you have made a performance selection and entered the LTM revenue as of the Calibration date for each company, click Run Report.  carta/public/13/images/3699271034482648825_1E_iyMgJ-xEkBssDJn1WNu-lx0-jUSANyw-ineiO0BZfsmXTxZgVQzgQiecAPzc0frOIebKsuOxEEL-rLaBk6n5o3Uy3d-8q8NuOQiVZPXIY77MB7qx6QQWrbnNj6692sIFiGipe",
        "originalText": "Once you have made a performance selection and entered the LTM revenue as of the Calibration date for each company, click Run Report.<br> <img height=\"209\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/3699271034482648825_1E_iyMgJ-xEkBssDJn1WNu-lx0-jUSANyw-ineiO0BZfsmXTxZgVQzgQiecAPzc0frOIebKsuOxEEL-rLaBk6n5o3Uy3d-8q8NuOQiVZPXIY77MB7qx6QQWrbnNj6692sIFiGipe\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"431\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/3699271034482648825_1E_iyMgJ-xEkBssDJn1WNu-lx0-jUSANyw-ineiO0BZfsmXTxZgVQzgQiecAPzc0frOIebKsuOxEEL-rLaBk6n5o3Uy3d-8q8NuOQiVZPXIY77MB7qx6QQWrbnNj6692sIFiGipe"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "The Calibration Report will display the change in value for each company, clicking on the name of a company will open a page that details the metrics that were used to arrive at the calibrated value.  carta/public/13/images/4283448905179935779_NsUt2xwuLNWF1c8WLq15BKif3WTTiJaAaz9rQ-_iOHVoRuPNOODJ1YhJPYo204o_YY_pafd0D3lQpizeNTXVZTWHooY8LcUBKrG8FmLHTqefeviO-HCxopdFAlEZ-NYsaFwwVJ4v",
        "originalText": "The Calibration Report will display the change in value for each company, clicking on the name of a company will open a page that details the metrics that were used to arrive at the calibrated value.<br> <img height=\"253\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/4283448905179935779_NsUt2xwuLNWF1c8WLq15BKif3WTTiJaAaz9rQ-_iOHVoRuPNOODJ1YhJPYo204o_YY_pafd0D3lQpizeNTXVZTWHooY8LcUBKrG8FmLHTqefeviO-HCxopdFAlEZ-NYsaFwwVJ4v\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"430\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/4283448905179935779_NsUt2xwuLNWF1c8WLq15BKif3WTTiJaAaz9rQ-_iOHVoRuPNOODJ1YhJPYo204o_YY_pafd0D3lQpizeNTXVZTWHooY8LcUBKrG8FmLHTqefeviO-HCxopdFAlEZ-NYsaFwwVJ4v"
        }
      }]
    }
  }, {
    "id": "8186186778248489759",
