  "linked": [{
    "id": "6697533435833560420",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "When a company invites you to participate in their Employee Stock Purchase Plan (ESPP), you will receive an email inviting you to enroll through Carta.  carta/public/13/images/5008570719447159191_rtaImage",
        "originalText": "When a company invites you to participate in their <a href=\"https://carta.com/espp/\" target=\"_blank\">Employee Stock Purchase Plan (ESPP)</a>, you will receive an email inviting you to enroll through Carta.<br> <img alt=\"\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/5008570719447159191_rtaImage\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/5008570719447159191_rtaImage"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "After opening the email, click Log in. If you already have an active Carta account, you can skip to log in and review tasks by following this link.  carta/public/13/images/6949740162964644885_dFFkMODdgzorE_-YFacVhKij4iddzn9m4aVxhKslSlQmzQStV7fFpDZOSn4gvOrj_vgBNno97xjQ4ice51r73q6-JsOYRzCYbIBoCINX7AsipgwlPa9IsizlT83Q1obMjJX5Oo-U    If you do not have a Carta account, proceed with registering an account and activating it using the activation email that is sent to you on registration.  carta/public/13/images/8631971659588803311_66XKQgMK4UjfqqjLK0amw2EUQrMHXChp7gO0E-ubAnh7hJn8v5svsWDe6Hog15eqkEUBwHLdKVOowefz4d6RxmL3NNUnCYBhRGpm5WzrUS4c1UzTf8LRO9r_Be2AkSjo3mWQDe2A",
        "originalText": "After opening the email, click Log in. If you already have an active Carta account, you can skip to log in and review tasks by following <a href=\"https://carta.com/accounts/login\" target=\"_blank\">this link</a>.<br> <img height=\"279\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/6949740162964644885_dFFkMODdgzorE_-YFacVhKij4iddzn9m4aVxhKslSlQmzQStV7fFpDZOSn4gvOrj_vgBNno97xjQ4ice51r73q6-JsOYRzCYbIBoCINX7AsipgwlPa9IsizlT83Q1obMjJX5Oo-U\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"483\"><br> <br> If you do not have a Carta account, proceed with registering an account and activating it using the activation email that is sent to you on registration.<br> <img height=\"355\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/8631971659588803311_66XKQgMK4UjfqqjLK0amw2EUQrMHXChp7gO0E-ubAnh7hJn8v5svsWDe6Hog15eqkEUBwHLdKVOowefz4d6RxmL3NNUnCYBhRGpm5WzrUS4c1UzTf8LRO9r_Be2AkSjo3mWQDe2A\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"382\">",
