        }
      }, {
        "text": "The next page allows you to review a summary of the current plan and offering period, and set your payroll contribution rate. You can also download and review the relevant plan documents. Once you set your contribution rate, click Sign and enroll.  https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/dRh9plG-59T0bB59cnX9W-tqESHim79F2hXd_i6R1xRQSfufp6QM4geLNki_hdENvo_lW2HLR-PfZ_RH5E32HPTw4nwjLwOkQTWQidI4UUgUFHMtA4DYWlxXtm4TkMlyYZNoA-CL",
        "originalText": "The next page allows you to review a summary of the current plan and offering period, and set your payroll contribution rate. You can also download and review the relevant plan documents. Once you set your contribution rate, click Sign and enroll.<br> <img alt=\"\" height=\"794\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/dRh9plG-59T0bB59cnX9W-tqESHim79F2hXd_i6R1xRQSfufp6QM4geLNki_hdENvo_lW2HLR-PfZ_RH5E32HPTw4nwjLwOkQTWQidI4UUgUFHMtA4DYWlxXtm4TkMlyYZNoA-CL\" style=\"display: block;\" width=\"485\">",
