        "text": "You will then be prompted to confirm your enrollment by checking off all boxes next to the relevant plan documents and then typing your signature before clicking Enroll.  https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/omEOnHiHMkIuMmsNiukxLS60TkgeKJyVpeMfrPc1DDmdCC3kq9YX3yYIhGUrooXl_k6ilkMz1Pc6EAeeDg6JVii8uvSYDW14x47XRorLYUKmlp9bN0TPkfCpQtBWHPcewMN8845h",
