  "linked": [{
    "id": "-1086780347863720980",
    "text": {
      "text": "Selecting Initiate an advance on theLine of Credit Summary orAccount Summary page will access the form to submit an advance request. Operators and Signers can view the calculation of available credit based on current fund data such ascallable capital andcalled to date. Note the available credit calculation may differ from borrower to borrower because it is defined by the LSA specific to each borrower.  An Operator can fill out the advance form and submit for signature. A Signer can sign submitted forms or fill one out and sign directly.  All signed requests received before 12PM PT will be processed on the same day and after this time, the next business day. There may be delays in processing due to federal holidays or non-operational business days such as President’s Day and the day after Thanksgiving. carta/public/13/images/6783421396110618705_5lFvsuVoQSAjOT8vcGvEJnzHynGUQsbO5s3b3tCH5DsZLdNlxblDSH3t-C5361d9Ejv35oCH5XPA5Vqo8khEff9JXYuoWqWqAdUkSxAILiG_JBohWc0nZ2l-Ue9aDsRquZBmbyiF",
      "originalText": "Selecting Initiate an advance on the Line of Credit Summary or Account Summary page will access the form to submit an advance request. Operators and Signers can view the calculation of available credit based on current fund data such as callable capital and called to date. Note the available credit calculation may differ from borrower to borrower because it is defined by the LSA specific to each borrower.<br><br>An Operator can fill out the advance form and submit for signature. A Signer can sign submitted forms or fill one out and sign directly.<br><br>All signed requests received before 12PM PT will be processed on the same day and after this time, the next business day. There may be delays in processing due to federal holidays or non-operational business days such as President’s Day and the day after Thanksgiving.<br><img height=\"287\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/6783421396110618705_5lFvsuVoQSAjOT8vcGvEJnzHynGUQsbO5s3b3tCH5DsZLdNlxblDSH3t-C5361d9Ejv35oCH5XPA5Vqo8khEff9JXYuoWqWqAdUkSxAILiG_JBohWc0nZ2l-Ue9aDsRquZBmbyiF\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"481\">",
