    "text": {
      "text": "To view a document, click on theView documentbutton of each document line item, which will open up the document in a separate window. carta/public/13/images/3933925365048361624_hKAKTqqYfKvllWxlEb2FSdPDreKo_P26sGxaJSMEApFzmA4SgU9Rbr3CoQBxoj4hJ4C8nDvVfYMCLpQMeZCBK0Fc3uapEaf3Ail09SzrHFzRwZdNBJmNBV_76KD0jva1zhp74MBn",
