    "id": "-5039788616975793482",
    "text": {
      "text": "How to use the Exercise Simulator in your Carta portfolio"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "7059425759865110915",
    "text": {
      "text": "In your Carta portfolio, it is possible to simulate and customize an exercise request before actually performing it. By changing the date of exercise, the tool will adjust the scenario based on the current vesting schedule and exercise quantity. The exercise simulator provides an estimate for your exercise cost and tax calculations. Consult your tax advisor before making decisions that may affect your business or interests.",
      "originalText": "In your Carta portfolio, it is possible to simulate and customize an exercise request before actually performing it. By changing the date of exercise, the tool will adjust the scenario based on the current vesting schedule and exercise quantity.<br>The exercise simulator provides an estimate for your exercise cost and tax calculations. Consult your tax advisor before making decisions that may affect your business or interests.<br>&nbsp;"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-515191393456734588",
    "text": {
