      "originalText": "Under Portfolio, select the desired company and click on Exercise Simulator.<br><img height=\"265\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/9038734668737298657_ekCyvDfyrnaxJ9C5EBqm0OupsGxv5Kr6q0FUxP6gAv1nihFaPTPb7EgVguOHeOo-RkLJ6Ekgc2ym0P3qtkJSfW1Q4JkNo2EgVmoME-3XKIOzFs-Zp3CekdH-hzqxDeF4nnipFMnk\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" width=\"624\">",
