    "id": "5672202168662646345",
    "text": {
      "text": "The “Option value” column utilizes the formula for the Black-Scholes OPM. These option values decrease as the effective strike prices (e.g., the values in the “To” column) increase.",
      "originalText": "The “Option value” column utilizes the formula for the Black-Scholes OPM. These option values decrease as the effective strike prices (e.g., the values in the “To” column) increase.&nbsp;"
