  }, {
    "id": "-1704391656582676202",
    "text": {
      "text": "Within the OPM, holding all other items constant, an increase in volatility will increase the value of the common stock. The more volatile the underlying asset, the more likely a high value exit occurs; the more likely a high value exit occurs, the larger the potential payout to common stock.",
      "originalText": "Within the OPM, holding all other items constant, an increase in volatility will increase the value of the common stock. The more volatile the underlying asset, the more likely a high value exit occurs; the more likely a high value exit occurs, the larger the potential payout to common stock."
