      "text": "=IF(ISBLANK(B6),\"\",IFERROR(LN(B6/B5),IFERROR(LN(B6/B4),IFERROR(LN(B6/B3),IFERROR(LN(B6/B2),IFERROR(LN(B6/B1),\"\"))))))",
      "textFormat": "HTML",
      "originalText": "<pre class=\"ckeditor_codeblock\">=IF(ISBLANK(B6),\"\",IFERROR(LN(B6/B5),IFERROR(LN(B6/B4),IFERROR(LN(B6/B3),IFERROR(LN(B6/B2),IFERROR(LN(B6/B1),\"\")))))) </pre>"
