  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-8621733183513850088",
    "text": {
      "text": "You can copy and paste the text and images from this article into an email. Send it to your security holders that will be invited to participate in the tender offer.",
      "originalText": "You can copy and paste the text and images from this article into an email. Send it to your security&nbsp;holders that will be invited to participate in the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://blog.carta.com/tender-offer-faq/\" style=\"color: blue;text-decoration: underline;\" target=\"_blank\">tender offer</a>."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "-7695914172907136670",
    "text": {
      "text": "Hi,  I wanted to give you a heads up that we are launching a tender offer through Carta. During this time, you will be able to sell your holdings at a fixed price during a time frame specified in the transaction documents in Carta.  Very shortly, you will receive an email from Carta notifying you of this tender offer. For information on how to participate in the tender, refer to the tender participation instructions.  The email will look like the following:  carta/public/13/images/2817696731326035105_rtaImage  After providing the required information and submitting your order to sell, you will receive a confirmation email from Carta. Please note that the tax form provided must be properly completed and a valid government ID (e.g. Driver's License or passport) must be uploaded, otherwise your order will be considered invalid.  The tender offer will close on<date> at<time> and orders will not be accepted for any reason after that time. On or around the settlement date, your net proceeds will be sent via ACH or wire to the bank account you specify in Carta, provided you have submitted all documents and information correctly.  Thank you!",
      "originalText": "<br><br>Hi,<br><br>I wanted to give you a heads up that we are launching a tender offer through Carta. During this time, you will be able to sell your holdings at a fixed price during a time frame specified in the transaction documents in Carta.<br><br>Very shortly, you will receive an email from <a href=\"http://www.carta.com/\" style=\"color: blue;text-decoration: underline;\" target=\"_blank\">Carta</a> notifying you of this tender offer.&nbsp;For information on how to participate in the tender, refer to the <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/participate-tender-offer\" style=\"color: blue;text-decoration: underline;\" target=\"_blank\">tender participation instructions</a>.<br><br>The email will look like the following:<br><br><img alt=\"A screenshot of a cell phone  Description automatically generated\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/2817696731326035105_rtaImage\" style=\"width: 301px;height: 560px;\"><br><br>After providing the required information and submitting your order to sell, you will receive a confirmation email from Carta. Please note that the tax form provided must be properly completed and a valid government ID (e.g. Driver's License or passport) must be uploaded, otherwise your order will be considered invalid.<br><br>The tender offer will close on &lt;date&gt; at &lt;time&gt; and orders will not be accepted for any reason after that time. On or around the settlement date, your net proceeds will be sent via ACH or wire to the bank account you specify in Carta, provided you have submitted all documents and information correctly.<br><br>Thank you!<br><br><br>&nbsp;",
      "associatedImage": {
        "url": "carta/public/13/images/2817696731326035105_rtaImage"
      }
    }
  }]
}

