    "id": "-5539739994212840484",
    "text": {
      "text": "For wire exercises, is it possible to submit two wire transfers? My bank has a transfer limit. Yes, multiple wires can be submitted for a single exercise. Upon Carta receiving the first wire of funds, the holder will get an email that their exercise is underfunded and more wires can be sent to complete the funds transfer of the total exercise cost. As long as the holder is within the 30 days deadline (starting when exercise is submitted), the exercise will complete. If the funds transfer falls out of the 30 day deadline, the exercise will automatically cancel and the holder can resubmit the exercise.",
