  "linked": [{
    "id": "-695088554931880806",
    "text": {
      "text": "After you’ve set up your closing on Carta and are ready to start inviting LPs to complete subscription documents, you can easily add LPs in bulk or one at a time.",
      "originalText": "After you’ve set up your closing on Carta and are ready to start inviting LPs to complete subscription documents, you can easily add LPs in bulk or one at a time."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "4797373390622192767",
    "text": {
      "text": "To add prospective LPs:",
      "originalText": "To add prospective LPs:"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "8164132308629540229",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "In the “Closings” tab of your entity click “Add new prospective partners” and then “Bulk add partners” carta/public/13/images/3685003595587168253_uLT6j0LqJUdvh9TE0SQkiG1secvMjRMoThZy6t7sAHA5rjsEpfUxPEUWJaIqBy7D4gmJ078xt9-WVMvSgimzoiUco-5c8RkmXkSqEioPZxnbV-43YeH4JSKXa70BynD2qoEoPlrH=s0",
        "originalText": "In the “Closings” tab of your entity click “Add new prospective partners” and then “Bulk add partners” <img height=\"312\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/3685003595587168253_uLT6j0LqJUdvh9TE0SQkiG1secvMjRMoThZy6t7sAHA5rjsEpfUxPEUWJaIqBy7D4gmJ078xt9-WVMvSgimzoiUco-5c8RkmXkSqEioPZxnbV-43YeH4JSKXa70BynD2qoEoPlrH=s0\" width=\"373\"> ",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/3685003595587168253_uLT6j0LqJUdvh9TE0SQkiG1secvMjRMoThZy6t7sAHA5rjsEpfUxPEUWJaIqBy7D4gmJ078xt9-WVMvSgimzoiUco-5c8RkmXkSqEioPZxnbV-43YeH4JSKXa70BynD2qoEoPlrH=s0"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "A spreadsheet will open on the page. On this spreadsheet you can enter in the following:Partner name: The name of the individual or entity that is subscribingFirst and Last Name: This will be the name of the primary contact for the LPs commitment. The LP can always update this and add additional contacts when they’re filling out subscription documentsEmail: The email address of the individual who will be filling out subscription documents for the partnerCommitment amount: The amount the LP will be committing to the fund or SPV. You must enter a commitment amount but this can be updated at any point prior to the LP signing.   You can also paste this information in from a spreadsheet.  carta/public/13/images/561655511986094246__oCSUIWh-gcoACF4teqcJ9TD_iyx67HDR8LrpKQ7LOt-hSEJm6631HHDANbVNLD8ZIpVuqME4J4r9l3seunnfyV8PnfFPIPQBzRK6kHvN1muqWXjHo16IZvC-okDZpsrOYcwKU5v=s0",
        "originalText": "A spreadsheet will open on the page. On this spreadsheet you can enter in the following:  Partner name: The name of the individual or entity that is subscribing First and Last Name: This will be the name of the primary contact for the LPs commitment. The LP can always update this and add additional contacts when they’re filling out subscription documents Email: The email address of the individual who will be filling out subscription documents for the partner Commitment amount: The amount the LP will be committing to the fund or SPV. You must enter a commitment amount but this can be updated at any point prior to the LP signing.  <br> You can also paste this information in from a spreadsheet.<br> <img height=\"206\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/561655511986094246__oCSUIWh-gcoACF4teqcJ9TD_iyx67HDR8LrpKQ7LOt-hSEJm6631HHDANbVNLD8ZIpVuqME4J4r9l3seunnfyV8PnfFPIPQBzRK6kHvN1muqWXjHo16IZvC-okDZpsrOYcwKU5v=s0\" width=\"564\">",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/561655511986094246__oCSUIWh-gcoACF4teqcJ9TD_iyx67HDR8LrpKQ7LOt-hSEJm6631HHDANbVNLD8ZIpVuqME4J4r9l3seunnfyV8PnfFPIPQBzRK6kHvN1muqWXjHo16IZvC-okDZpsrOYcwKU5v=s0"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Click “Save” in the top right of the spreadsheet. You will be alerted to resolve any errors in the information you uploaded.",
        "originalText": "Click “Save” in the top right of the spreadsheet. You will be alerted to resolve any errors in the information you uploaded."
      }, {
        "text": "The full list of partners will now be populated as prospects on the closings tab.",
        "originalText": "The full list of partners will now be populated as prospects on the closings tab."
      }, {
        "text": "At this point, the LPs have not yet been invited to complete subscription documents. When you’re ready to send invitations, select the LPs you’d like to invite and then click “Send Invite”. Their status will change to “Invited\"",
