    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-2955712874402947426",
    "text": {
      "text": "With theRule 701 Disclosure feature, Admins can send the disclosure to equity award holders through Carta. The holders can accept and review the documents in their Carta account.  Admins will need to work with Carta Support to upload and send the document. After completing the following three steps, submit a case to Carta’s Help Center and Carta Support can assist.  NOTE: It is recommended to issue the equity awards ( Option grants or RSUs) to the cap table prior to starting the 701 distribution process to ensure new equity award holders are included in the recipient spreadsheet. After the 701 disclosure is distributed, the equity award signatories can sign the securities and send them to the holders for acceptance.",
      "originalText": "With the Rule 701 Disclosure feature, Admins can send the disclosure to equity award holders through Carta. The holders can accept and review the documents in their Carta account.<br><br>Admins will need to work with Carta Support to upload and send the document. After completing the following three steps, submit a case to <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/carta-help-center\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Carta’s Help Center</u></a> and Carta Support can assist.<br><br>NOTE: It is recommended to issue the equity awards (<a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/issue-option-grants\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><u>Option grants</u></a> or <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/issue-rsus\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><u>RSUs</u></a>) to the cap table prior to starting the 701 distribution process to ensure new equity award holders are included in the recipient spreadsheet. After the 701 disclosure is distributed, the equity award signatories can sign the securities and send them to the holders for acceptance."
    }
  }, {
