        "text": "Download the backup codes in case you lose access to the device with two-factor authentication setup. Carta strongly recommends downloading and keeping backup codes in a secure place in your home, office or other location. Having the backup code enables easy access to your account without going through the entire two-factor authentication reset process.  carta/public/13/images/2436958925428736768_KRPv3FxuM3R-7NZkuUkIaKAZq8tjKP-dixCqI9-P6lZ2grCGc5mlwT3HXoRbIa4TxXUlDLju1MAgsUbaMu4P0QvmpWDK5Z9SUzIXhww_AQ0IUdxrlXoTEBbM1xcweDvTHkQWTEZ-",
