    "id": "4558407851557289420",
    "text": {
      "text": "How to manually send email reminders about securities"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "241204890311240054",
    "text": {
      "text": "Users with Legal Administrator,Company Editor, orCompany Viewer permissions will be able to manually resend reminder emails to signatories to sign securities and holders to accept securities. Email reminders are automatically sent at the 5, 10, 20, 30, and 90 day mark if a security remains unsigned or unaccepted. Learn more about notifications sent to users.",
      "originalText": "Users with Legal Administrator, Company Editor, or Company Viewer permissions will be able to manually resend reminder emails to signatories to sign securities and holders to accept securities. Email reminders are automatically sent at the 5, 10, 20, 30, and 90 day mark if a security remains unsigned or unaccepted. <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/send-company-admin-holders\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more about notifications sent to users.</a>"
    }
  }, {
    "id": "3318819318767619251",
    "text": {
      "text": "Emails can be sent from all security ledgers on the company’s cap table. Securities with an orange flag implies that the security is still “awaiting officer signature”, while securities with a green flag implies that the security is still “awaiting holder signature” to be accepted into their portfolio. Learn more from the securities ledger glossary. carta/public/13/images/4572778341596948276_PxtAtHACSxC9aL7CjNj1--epZU5HvT2rBOf8WCPSFq45Cmxz44MvwFXHq_Hzw97kK-t-caBLSTQqP9VxaKukc4UwfMfYd391pdLnIP5x7XpDrOIFEGfNfUhK__8vP6y-MazOkVnE carta/public/13/images/451411836772611510_v8FkhsPSswwLQsoAWBSwaFUp4xeiQaXAK5yN2qTQblpnCm6SRQrMf7CtdkSr_gTjm5iv6WilWcNgbh5rq6AUoQu3s38hTbK6A5f30ssCyeaWCkmAaQ79ZQb5VFOuAtwIk8X1UIBO",
      "originalText": "Emails can be sent from all security ledgers on the company’s cap table. Securities with an orange flag implies that the security is still “awaiting officer signature”, while securities with a green flag implies that the security is still “awaiting holder signature” to be accepted into their portfolio. <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/securities-ledgers-guide\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more from the securities ledger glossary.</a><br><img height=\"69\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/4572778341596948276_PxtAtHACSxC9aL7CjNj1--epZU5HvT2rBOf8WCPSFq45Cmxz44MvwFXHq_Hzw97kK-t-caBLSTQqP9VxaKukc4UwfMfYd391pdLnIP5x7XpDrOIFEGfNfUhK__8vP6y-MazOkVnE\" width=\"268\"><br><img height=\"71\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/451411836772611510_v8FkhsPSswwLQsoAWBSwaFUp4xeiQaXAK5yN2qTQblpnCm6SRQrMf7CtdkSr_gTjm5iv6WilWcNgbh5rq6AUoQu3s38hTbK6A5f30ssCyeaWCkmAaQ79ZQb5VFOuAtwIk8X1UIBO\" width=\"270\">",
