  "subject": {
    "id": "-2591262032498768114",
    "text": {
      "text": "How to Request a 2FA Reset"
    }
  },
  "linked": [{
    "id": "-1984027052409465360",
    "text": {
      "text": "If you have lost access to your two-factor authentication (2FA) device or are facing difficulties receiving the 2FA code, you can still use your backup codes to log in. Backup codes are provided to you when you set up two factor authentication. If you have downloaded the codes, it is saved on your local drive as carta-backup-codes.txt.   If you do not have your backup codes, this article will direct you to raise a 2FA reset request with Carta Support team.",
      "originalText": "If you have lost access to your two-factor authentication (2FA) device or are facing difficulties receiving the 2FA code, you can still use your backup codes to log in.&nbsp;Backup codes are provided to you when you set up two factor authentication. If you have downloaded the codes, it is&nbsp;saved on your local drive as carta-backup-codes.txt.<br><br><br>If you do not have your backup codes, this article will direct you to raise a 2FA reset request with Carta Support team."
    }
  }, {
    "id": "8712279905289893600",
    "list": {
      "isOrdered": true,
      "item": [{
        "text": "Navigate to carta.com/accounts/login and log in using your credentials.  carta/public/13/images/5741204783233242108_AXISRIUCtc_RtMh6onMdtIs2o0QuYUykzV12LNEsJr0P-BZeH-4GeRTunghv7iYpDROudsUMs-bKLDcbVwNqF95rJulsz9LbGhN8Ig7AYWAfx7lb4nvS1wRw6RAiUr-4O9ndoe79",
        "originalText": "Navigate to <a href=\"http://carta.com/accounts/login\" target=\"_blank\">carta.com/accounts/login</a> and log in using your credentials.<br> <img height=\"563\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/5741204783233242108_AXISRIUCtc_RtMh6onMdtIs2o0QuYUykzV12LNEsJr0P-BZeH-4GeRTunghv7iYpDROudsUMs-bKLDcbVwNqF95rJulsz9LbGhN8Ig7AYWAfx7lb4nvS1wRw6RAiUr-4O9ndoe79\" style=\"border: 1pt solid #000000;\" width=\"446\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
