        "originalText": "Click Recovery options from the Authentication code page, which will have a slightly different view depending on the authentication type used.<br> <img height=\"478\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/2860794056120917195_kBnX6zoq93T0_LT-QR_3-ST-Y4IFgqLv2VreuzD1fVxixN6SG2fvrChpK7gYc4ff6gBjOy7DMsqYNjSO_XZHgF2BIOrfC_YcV_gtR37feaOhvSOcdo_a3JUjfQAFYbbDx2haZyfQ\" style=\"border: 1pt solid #000000;\" width=\"478\"><br> <br> <img height=\"502\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/5474663823588446013_zeTMQZ5_-xeaHHLbDVOJtHmEsTvxTaMNZskws3fV8kcsJXvpUJR_5n8-wqCmfEXeKvQph2cAnpLXG1OtBz1SYkgCnQC346t5X9MWZ6_LFArYGftR2DI1q41Qy4GK7pYjDPn61cYv\" style=\"border: 1pt solid #000000;\" width=\"477\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
