        }
      }, {
        "text": "If you have your backup codes, enter one of them on the following screen. If you do not, click Request 2FA reset to raise a request with Carta Support to disable 2FA on your account.  carta/public/13/images/7035951239105292864_qBVWlOH-2ZhxtOKPXjbqOJ5420yB3iJGeyzvgFXiCyPWfGpUSk5tARsAF2Owm4TG3YKOmocotBxPLV32guxlhfQThW3qEdHkMqw0rqQ2qZqeHoijLcQi5Y9PO9Rw9vao3kxFlxRA",
        "originalText": "If you have your backup codes, enter one of them on the following screen. If you do not, click Request 2FA reset to raise a request with Carta Support to disable&nbsp;2FA on your account.<br> <img height=\"452\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/7035951239105292864_qBVWlOH-2ZhxtOKPXjbqOJ5420yB3iJGeyzvgFXiCyPWfGpUSk5tARsAF2Owm4TG3YKOmocotBxPLV32guxlhfQThW3qEdHkMqw0rqQ2qZqeHoijLcQi5Y9PO9Rw9vao3kxFlxRA\" style=\"border: 1pt solid #000000;\" width=\"476\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/7035951239105292864_qBVWlOH-2ZhxtOKPXjbqOJ5420yB3iJGeyzvgFXiCyPWfGpUSk5tARsAF2Owm4TG3YKOmocotBxPLV32guxlhfQThW3qEdHkMqw0rqQ2qZqeHoijLcQi5Y9PO9Rw9vao3kxFlxRA"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Fill out the request form with the required information. A photo of yourself holding your government ID and a note displaying today's date is required. Click here to review good and bad examples of photos.  carta/public/13/images/1686351603249332463_p9dIJqmIamkgmCo9NNe7ZTW5rnfroasy817twQI-Ellh4czjw0TMxH1mK-DivcAE6HA_1GSPFRPGNWO2vCQZuTC6V0G9k98-eJdbWe-8pD2Qf7U1MmELsG8qKfvjuaLqOJJsNmSi",
        "originalText": "Fill out the request form with the required information. A photo of yourself holding your government ID and a note displaying today's date is required. <a href=\"https://support.carta.com/s/article/how-to-request-a-2fa-reset#photo-examples\"><u>Click here to review good and bad examples of photos</u></a>.<br> <img height=\"679\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/1686351603249332463_p9dIJqmIamkgmCo9NNe7ZTW5rnfroasy817twQI-Ellh4czjw0TMxH1mK-DivcAE6HA_1GSPFRPGNWO2vCQZuTC6V0G9k98-eJdbWe-8pD2Qf7U1MmELsG8qKfvjuaLqOJJsNmSi\" style=\"border: 1pt solid #000000;\" width=\"332\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/1686351603249332463_p9dIJqmIamkgmCo9NNe7ZTW5rnfroasy817twQI-Ellh4czjw0TMxH1mK-DivcAE6HA_1GSPFRPGNWO2vCQZuTC6V0G9k98-eJdbWe-8pD2Qf7U1MmELsG8qKfvjuaLqOJJsNmSi"
        }
      }, {
        "text": "Check your email and click Complete reset request to confirm the request.  carta/public/13/images/1598755163167213242_-YhE1M4G9crQAL0ahefPU6kDubEiYluuerkQseGC1NdAHD8uiL9wPlRlRPw2-_woaa6m-QcwcBrGYezQ_6oOKB58v9LiN9Gw2l9mpNu8kxjc-V2bk_LlEzxo3rDdJqz9aAypUUKq=s0",
        "originalText": "Check your email and click Complete reset request to confirm the request.<br> <img height=\"388\" src=\"carta/public/13/images/1598755163167213242_-YhE1M4G9crQAL0ahefPU6kDubEiYluuerkQseGC1NdAHD8uiL9wPlRlRPw2-_woaa6m-QcwcBrGYezQ_6oOKB58v9LiN9Gw2l9mpNu8kxjc-V2bk_LlEzxo3rDdJqz9aAypUUKq=s0\" style=\"border: 1pt solid #000000;\" width=\"391\"><br> &nbsp;",
        "associatedImage": {
          "url": "carta/public/13/images/1598755163167213242_-YhE1M4G9crQAL0ahefPU6kDubEiYluuerkQseGC1NdAHD8uiL9wPlRlRPw2-_woaa6m-QcwcBrGYezQ_6oOKB58v9LiN9Gw2l9mpNu8kxjc-V2bk_LlEzxo3rDdJqz9aAypUUKq=s0"
